\id LUK - Zyphe
\h LUKA
\toc1 LUKA A CIAPAW THAWNGCHAWBIA
\toc2 LUKA
\toc3 Luk
\mt1 LUKA
\mt2 A CIAPAW THAWNGCHAWBIA
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Mehchaw cai a cangpaw Theofila, mehlupui tah kaa hrawng letei hming a va tlung ciapaw kong khah cia a pachia cy he ka,
\v 2 cia a pachiapaw he cawh mehkho ceingei tei a hmuh tawpaw sahlo le phung a reilaipaw sahlo he tei aa ma chingpaw hrakhei a cang.
\v 3 Macawtaco kama zong tah a hrangthonah taitah zezong a raering teitah ka khiahle khy taitah a pazui naning tei hratah na cawtah ciapah heh a chah thly a tatah ka rawh.
\v 4 Aa ca cawngpah pawhe vytei khah biahmuisui a cang tahpaw na hni khy nápawtah.
\s1 Baptisma a peitu Johan a pinah kong reihlangnah
\p 
\v 5 Herod cawh Judia raang letah siangpahrang a cangning takhei Zakaria aa tahpaw tlangbui pakheh ung ka, ama cawh tlangbui Abija phu leteipaw a cang. A nupui Elizabet zong cawh tlangbui Aron hring a cang.
\v 6 Aa pahning tah Khazing hme letah a dingkong teitah khua a sahpaw cang he ka, suise a kawh ly tei Abuipaw biapeh le a phung le lang vytei khah a zuipaw a cang he.
\v 7 Canghrasala Elizabet cawh cing ka, sawteisah bei he. Aa pahning co, aa kung a macang ngetei myca he.
\p 
\v 8 Uikhehpaw cawh Zakaria phu khah aa raihre nápaw cai cawh va chuh ka, Zakaria cawh Khazing hmekaw leco tlangbui rai cawh hre ka,
\v 9 tlangbui cangnah rai a rainah phung tei hratah basung phe he ka, ama cawh Abuipaw behnah ing chung letei ringthopaw me tei ropaw rai khah a ting.
\v 10 Ringthopaw me ronah cai a va chua tihtah Khazing beh rua pawtei a pahmopaw zawpui sahlo cawh khungthing lang lekhei thlaw aa chang.
\p 
\v 11 Mataico, Abuipaw vaiming cawh ama khatah a va paly ka, ringthopaw ronah siasang cacang lang lekhei a daw thlang.
\v 12 Zakaria tah ama cawh a hmuh tihtah a pahly ka, a ci ngetei.
\v 13 Canghrasala vaiming taco, “Zakaria ci kheh, Khazing tah na thlawchangnah khah a ca thui pah. Na nupui Elizabet tah sawcapaw a ca sah pah a. A ming cawh Johan na sá a.
\v 14 Na thawchahnah le na lung a tlingnah ngetei a cang a. A pinah cawtah ming hlupui khah aa lung a lawng a.
\v 15 Abuipaw mehmuh letah mehlai a cang a. Zu le ahringpaw rui khy a cangpaw zong khah ding hrahring a be. A no chung taitah Thlawpaw Pathai tah a chih ciapaw a cang a.
\v 16 Israel cawngsaw mehlupui khah Abuipaw aa Khazing khatah a va chui kaw he a.
\v 17 Taico, Elija a hmingtuakhynah le a thlawpaw tah Abuipaw hmelang tah a sei a. Paw sahlo lungthing cawh aa sawtei sahlo lang letah le bia a nge lypaw sahlo cawh singnah a cangpaw dingnah lang letah a hui sá he a. Cawngsaw vytei khah Abuipaw cawtah a maipacia rua pawtah a pachia a paning he a,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 18 Zakaria tah vaiming hai letaco, “Ma cawh zehratamaw a cang khy a? Kama zong mehtaa cang myca neh ka, ka nupui zong kung macang pui a cang myca?” a tah.
\p 
\v 19 Vaiming taco, “Kama Gabriel cawh, Khazing hmekaw letah a dawpaw ka cang. Ma kong thawngchawbia heh nama ching rua tah tawpaw ka cang.
\v 20 Mataico nama cawh ma hming vytei heh a va tlung thlu hlai vytei na rei thlaw khy khaw bei ceh. Zecawtamaw tatah ma cai a tling tih tei, a va tlung lepaw ka reipaw bia khah na zing lynah cawtah,” a tah.
\p 
\v 21 Ma chung cawh zawpui vytei tah ama cawh heh thlang he ka, zecawtamaw behnah ing chung letah ma tlua co a ry zia tatah aa khuarawh a haa thlu.
\v 22 A ka piathlah tihtah aaning sahlo khah bia a ching khy khawh bei he. Behnah ing chung lekhei apalynah a hmuh tahpaw khah aa hni. Zemaw tahpaw co, a kihtua khei bia khah a ching he ka, a rei cawh thlaw khy hlui be.
\p 
\v 23 Mataico a raihrenah cai cawh a chang tihtah ing lang khah a dih.
\v 24 Ma khy taico a nupui Elizabet cawh sawtei pho ka, thlah pangaw chung a nawh.
\v 25 Elizabet taco, “Ma heh Abuipaw tah ka cawtah a tuapaw a cang, atoning cai lehei a dukhuinah cawh palangsah ka, ming vytei hrong letei ka ningzawnah khah a pa lahpah hly myca,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Zisu a pinah kong reihlangnah
\p 
\v 26 Taico, a thlahruhnah leco, Khazing tah vaiming Gabriel cawh Galili raang Nazaret khua lang khah taw ka,
\v 27 David teisaw a cangpaw Josef tah chui ruapaw tei a pahapaw laisaw pathai khakhei a taw. Ma laisaw pathai a ming cawh Mari a cang.
\v 28 Vaiming cawh ama khaco va sei ka, “Na kih ka ca tle, nama cawh dukhuinah a sangpui a cypaw na cang. Abuipaw cawh nama khatah a ung,” a tah.
\p 
\v 29 Mari cawh ma bia rawng taco a lung hna a hnawh ngetei ka, ma heh zehapaw kihtlenah maw a cang sialia, tatah a khuarawh a haa thlang.
\v 30 Canghrasala vaiming taco a hai letah, “Mari, ci kheh, Khazing dukhuinah na hmuh myca.
\v 31 Sawtei pho ceh ka, sawcapaw na sá a. A ming tah Zisu tatah na tah a.
\v 32 Ama cawh mehlai cang a ka, Cungnungcai Khazing Sawcapaw tatah y a cang a. Abuipaw Khazing tah a pathlahtu paw David abui dyching khah a pae a.
\v 33 Jakob mingphing sahlo cung letah bia a hnui paria a. A painah raang cawh changnah hnui be,” a tah.
\p 
\v 34 Mari taco, “Zekhatamaw ma hming heh a cang thai a? Kama cawh laisaw pathai pui ka cang caw!” tah ka,
\v 35 vaiming taco, “Thlawpaw Pathai cawh na cung letah tlung ka, Cungnungcai Khazing hmingtuakhynah tah a ca bakhu a. Macawtaco, mehpathai a va pi lepaw cawh Khazing Sawcapaw tatah y a cang a.
\v 36 Na sawny no Elizabet tahmai a tá khy tah sawtei a sá a. A cing tatei aa tah teipaw khah atoheh cawh a thlahruhnah a cang myca.
\v 37 Khazing khaco a cang khy lypaw zehmai ung be,” tatah a palei.
\p 
\v 38 Mari taco, “Kama cawh Abuipaw a saecanu ka cang, na reipaw hratah ka cung letah tlung ky seh,” tatah a tah. Mataico, vaiming tah ama cawh a seisai.
\s1 Mari tah Elizabet a tlong
\p 
\v 39 Ma ningcai leco Mari cawh a pachia ka, Judia raang tlaang cung letei a ungpaw khua lang khah rairang tah a sei.
\v 40 Zakaria ing leco a nae ka, Elizabet cawh a kih a tle.
\v 41 Mari tei bia a chingpaw khah Elizabet tah a thui tihtah a chung letei a ungpaw ny cawh a pathlo ka, Elizabet cawh Thlawpaw Pathai tah a chih.
\v 42 A thangpui tah y ka, “Canu vytei letah bonghnang a ting cai no cang ceh ka, na sah lepaw ny zong bonghnang a tingpaw a cang!
\v 43 Canghrasala zecawtamaw ma tlua hei dukhuinah ka ting tu tlong! Ka Buipaw a no, kama khatah na vong thlangpaw heh!
\v 44 Na kih tlenah o khah ka naw tah a thui cangkaw tei leh ka chi chung letei a ungpaw ny cawh a lawng ka, a pathlo.
\v 45 Abuipaw tah ama khatei bia a reipaw, a va tlung ceingei a, tatei a zing no cawh bonghnang song tah ung ky seh,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Mari hlaw
\p 
\v 46 Taico Mari taco,
\q1 “Ka hringnah tahei Abuipaw cawh reithai ka,
\q2 
\v 47 ka thlawpaw cawh Khazing, a pa Pachahtu cung letah a lawng.
\q1 
\v 48 A saecanu a ny pahnai zia cawh
\q2 monghly be ca ka,
\q1 atoning ri taihei co, chai a va chuh lepaw letei cawngsaw vytei tah
\q2 bonghnang a ting no aa pa tah a.
\q1 
\v 49 Meh thawtlungpaw taco, ka cawtah hming rungnawpaw a tua myca,
\q2 a ming cawh a pathai.
\q1 
\v 50 Chaikheh hning chaikheh
\q2 Ama a cizawpaw sahlo he cung letah a ningdonah a palang.
\q1 
\v 51 A kiá tah hming rungnawpaw sahlo cawh tua ka,
\q2 aa lungchung tei a palai a patuinah a hnuipaw sahlo khah a papaipatlaw thlu he.
\q1 
\v 52 Uhtu bui sahlo khah aa buidyching taitah dawh thlah he ka,
\q2 canghrasala nytawpaw sahlo cawh a cuicaling he.
\q1 
\v 53 A ngaidipaw sahlo cawh hming chawpaw tah aa rivawsah he ka,
\q2 canghrasala mehrung sahlo cawh aa kih longpaw tah a kawsah he.
\q1 
\v 54 A sae Israel cawh bawkhang ka,
\q2 Abraham le a pathlah sahlo
\q1 
\v 55 letei a zaangsawnah cawh chaizaw tah a thui paria thlang ka,
\q2 kaa mapaw sahlo letei a reipaw zong tai khah,”
\m a tah.
\p 
\v 56 Mari cawh Elizabet khaco thlah thung hrawng a ung khy taitah ing lang a tlung kaw.
\s1 Baptisma peitu Johan a pinah
\p 
\v 57 Elizabet cawh ny a hnuinah ning le thlaw cawh va tling ka, sawcapaw a sah.
\v 58 A ingpaw le a sawny sahlo tah Abuipaw tah a cung letah a zaangsawnah alaipui tah a langsah tahpaw aa thui tihtah a lawng khui ngetei he.
\p 
\v 59 Ningreh ning taco nysai cawh a cingpatai rua pawtah va sei he ka, a ming cawh a paw ming Zakaria sah kaw pawtah aa tah.
\v 60 Canghrasala a no tei a tahpaw cawh, “Cang be, Johan tatah ypaw a cang,” a tah.
\p 
\v 61 Aaning sahlo taco, “Naa sawny hrong letah ma hapaw ming a phopaw cawh aa ung tlung be,” aa tah.
\p 
\v 62 Taico a paw cawh kihtua tah nypaw ming heh aho tah paseh la maw na du tatah aa hae.
\v 63 Ama taco, “Ca cianah calung pa pei law,” tatah a kih tuapah he ka, “A ming cawh Johan a cang,” tatah cia ka, cawngsaw vytei cawh aa khuarawh a haa thlang.
\v 64 Ma khy cangkaw leco, a lui cawh a catlai ka, a hmo a ka caw ka, bia ka reichua ka, Khazing khah a reithai.
\v 65 Ingpaw sahlo vytei cawh ningang tah ung he ka, tlaang raang a cangpaw Judia raang cawngsaw vytei taco, ma kong longtei khah aa rei.
\v 66 Ma aa thuipaw maikaw cawh aa khuarawh haa ka, “Ma nypaw heh zemaw a ka lo tae tu a?” tatah aa tah tlungmang. Abuipaw hmingtuakhynah kih cawh a cung letah a ungnah cawtah a cang.
\s1 Zakaria hlaw
\p 
\v 67 A paw Zakaria cawh Thlawpaw Pathai tah chih ka, bia phy ka,
\q1 
\v 68 “Abuipaw, Israel Khazing cawh reithai tah ung ky seh.
\q2 Zemaw tah pawco, Ama cawh a vong ka, a cawngsaw sahlo cawh a tlang myca he.
\q1 
\v 69 A sae David pathlah taikhei pachahnah ki cawh
\q2 kaa cawtah a patung myca.
\q1 
\v 70 Abuipaw tah khuahlai ning taitei Khazing khuavang mehpathai sahlo hmang tei
\q2 bia a ma taipaw cawh,
\q1 
\v 71 kaa carae sahlo le a ma huapaw sahlo taitah
\q2 pachah rua pawtah a cang.
\q1 
\v 72 Khazing tah kaa mapaw sahlo cung letah zawnge a neh ka,
\q2 ka biahrai pathaipaw cawh ka cingkai a, a tah.
\q1 
\v 73 Kaa mapaw Abraham khatah
\q2 ma biatainah a tuapaw cawh
\q1 
\v 74 kaaning khah kaa carae kih chung taitah pachah chua pawtah le
\q2 ciphang lytah le pathainah le ding ná tah,
\q1 
\v 75 kaa hring chung vytei a hmekung letah
\q2 a rai kaa hre khy nápaw cawtah a cang.
\q1 
\v 76 Ka sawtei, nama cawh Cungnungcai Khazing khuavang tatah y na cang a;
\q2 zecawtamaw tatah Abuipaw langpui parai pawtah a hme letah na sei lai a.
\q1 
\v 77 A cawngsaw sahlo khah naa suanah ngethai a cangnah thongtah
\q2 pachahnah naa hmuh a, tatah na ching he a.
\q1 
\v 78 Zecawtamaw tatah kaa Khazing cawh ningdo a thaipaw le a ningnaipaw a cang,
\q2 pachahnah khainah cawh avai taitah kaa cung letah khaisah ka,
\q1 
\v 79 thihnah ningpahli le muinah chung letah a ungpaw sahlo cung letah
\q2 khai sá pawtah le kaaning khah denah langpui lang chuithlah rua pawtah a cang,”
\m tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 80 Taico nysai cawh ka changchy ka, thlawpaw lang letah thawzaang ka hnui longmang ka, Israel mingphing sahlo letei a va phyhlang hlai vytei cawh raangcaa lekhei khua a sah.
\c 2
\s1 Zisu a pinah
\r (Mt 1:18-25)
\p 
\v 1 Ma ningcai leco Sizar Augusta tah Rom painah raang chung letei a ungpaw vytei mehlu rei rua pawtah bia a chua.
\v 2 Ma hming heh Kuirinia cawh Siria raang letah raang uhbui a hrening letei mehlu reinah a ung taw caipaw a cang.
\v 3 Cawngsaw vytei cawh aaning aa thokehnah khua cacy lang khah ming cia rua pawtah a sei he.
\p 
\v 4 Josef zong Galili raang Nazaret khua taitah Judia raang David khua Bethlehem lang cawh sei rua pawtah a tho. Ama cawh David hring le a pathlah taitei a chuhpaw a cangnah cawtah.
\v 5 Chui ruapaw tei a pahapaw Mari, ny a chai daimangpaw khaco ming cia rua pawtah a sei.
\v 6 Ma letei aa ungning taco ny a hnui nápaw ning le thlaw cawh va tling ka,
\v 7 taico sa-uthui cawh sah ka, sawcapaw a cang. Pai tah pahlong he ka, sahring lawhkong letah aa isah, zecawtamaw tatah khuabuh letah aa tlung nápaw hminghmaw ung khawh be.
\s1 Tuukingtu sahlo le vaiming sahlo
\p 
\v 8 Taico ma kaekang phong leco tuukingtu sahlo ung he ka, zai tah aa tuu sahlo cawh aa mingkai he.
\v 9 Abuipaw a vaiming cawh a za paly ka, Abuipaw rungnawnah taco aa kaekang vytei cawh khaisah thlu ka, tuuking sahlo cawh aa ci ngetei.
\v 10 Canghrasala Abuipaw a vaiming taco, “Ci khe o, cawngsaw vytei caw pawtah thawngchawbia a lawng a chuipaw ka va ca tlungkhui pah he hi.
\v 11 Atoning heh naa cawtah David khua letah Pachahtu a pi, Ama cawh Khri\f + \fr 2:11 \ft Khri (Grik rei), le Mesiah (Hebru rei) aa silang cawh, \fq Sathy thupaw,\ft tahnah a cang.\f* le Abuipaw a cang.
\v 12 Ma heh naa cawtah paching pakhanah a cang a. Nysai pai tei pahlongpaw, sahring lawhkong letei aa isah thlangpaw cawh naa hmuh a,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 13 Ma cangkawleh cawh sung sungkheh tah vaiming rungpui cawh Khazing reithai hmo khei vaiming khaco a za paly he ka,
\q1 
\v 14 “Cungnungcai Khazing cawh reithai tah ung ky seh,
\q2 a dukhuinah aa cung letah a ungpaw aluicung cawngsaw sahlo khaco
\q2 denah ung paria thlang seh,”
\m aa tah.
\p 
\v 15 Vaiming sahlo vaicung lang aa sei kaw taico, tuuking sahlo taco, “Atoheh a tho he peh seh la, Bethlehem khua lang cawh sei he peh. Abuipaw tei a ma chingpaw hming a va tlungpaw cawh ming rua pawtah sei he peh,” aa tah he.
\p 
\v 16 Taico rairang tah sei he ka, Mari le Josef le sahring lawhkong letei aa isah thlangpaw nysai khah aa va hmuh.
\v 17 Aa va hmuh khy taico, ma nysai konglang vytei, vaiming tei a chingpaw he hratah aa va hmuhpaw kong khah aa reilai longmang.
\v 18 A thuipaw vytei sahlo taco, tuukingtu sahlo tei bia aa reipaw khah aa khuarawh a haa ngetei thlu.
\v 19 Canghrasala Mari duitei taco ma hming vytei cawh a lungthing tah pacang ka, a cingkai.
\v 20 Aa thuipaw hming vytei le aa hmuhpaw maikaw cawh aa chingpaw he hratah a cangnah cawtah tuukingtu sahlo tah Khazing cawh rungnawnah le reithainah hlai he ka aa ungnah lang a kaw kaw he.
\s1 Behnah ing letah Zisu aa chuakhui
\p 
\v 21 Ningreh a va tling ning leco, a cingpa cawh tai he ka, a ming tah Zisu aa sah. Ma ming cawh sawtei a pho hlai tah vaiming tei a peh si ciapaw ming khah a cang.
\p 
\v 22 Moses phungbia hratah a pathaisahnah cai cawh a tling tihtah Josef le Mari taco Abuipaw letah hlai rua pawtah Zisu cawh Jerusalem lang aa seikhui.
\v 23 Abuipaw phungbia letah, “Capaw sa-uthui maikaw cawh Abuipaw cawtah patliapaw a cang he,”\x + \xo 2:23 \xt Piachua 13:2,12\x* tatah ciapaw hratah.
\v 24 Taico Abuipaw phungbia tei a reipaw zui nápaw athuihlainah caw pawtah thury bokheh a cang ly leh lelai a nypaw tei punghning tah aa hlai pawtah aa va seipaw a cang hrah.
\p 
\v 25 Ma ningcai leco Jerusalem letah cawngsaw pakheh Simeon aa tahpaw, mehding le mehse ngeteipaw a ung. Israel mingphing cung letei thlaw palungtu a va tlung lepaw cawh heh thlang ka, Thlawpaw Pathai cawh a cung letah a ung.
\v 26 Thlawpaw Pathai tah Abuipaw Khri a hmuh hlai vytei cawh thi balang bei ceh tatah a thuisah ciapaw a cang.
\v 27 Thlawpaw chuithlah ná tah behnah ingdung chunglang cawh a nae ka. Moses phungbia naning tei hratah a cung letah tua ruapaw cawtah nysai Zisu cawh a no le a paw tah aa va chuakhui.
\v 28 Simeon taco nysai cawh pawng ka, Khazing cawh ma hrahei a reithai,
\q1 
\v 29 “Vy, Cungnungcai Abuipaw nama tei bia na pa pataipaw hrakhei
\q2 atoheh na sae cawh thlawlung teitah na pa thihsah myca a.
\q1 
\v 30 Ka mehkho tah na pachahnah cawh a hmuh myca,
\q2 
\v 31 ming vytei mehmuh letei na pachia ciapaw khah le,
\q1 
\v 32 Gental cawngsaw sahlo cawtah khainah cawh palangsah pawtah le
\q2 na cawngsaw Israel cawngsaw sahlo rungnawnah ruapaw cawtah,”
\m a tah.
\p 
\v 33 A no le a paw cawh nysai konglang a reipaw bia cawh aa khuarawh a haa ngetei.
\v 34 Taico Simeon taco aaning cawh bonghnang song he ka, a no Mari khah ma hrahei a tah, “Ma nysai heh Israel cawngsaw mehlupui a posahly rua pawtah le mehlupui a padawchy tu cawtah rawhpaw a cang. Ama cawh Khazing taitah a va chuhpaw paching pakhanah cawngsaw hlupui tei aa cakhae lepaw cawh a cang a.
\v 35 Ma taikhei cawngsaw hlupui aa khuarawnah khah palang a cang tae a. Taico nama na thinglung zong zyzi tah a ca thipahleh tae a,” a tah.
\p 
\v 36 Khazing khuavangno pakheh, Asher phing leteipaw, Fanuel a sawcanu Ana ung hrah ka, ama cawh a taa ngetei myca. Ama cawh dongcang ka, a pasae khatah kung sarih ung hrui he ka,
\v 37 ma khy taico kung songreh le kung pali tai lahmeno a cang. Behnah ing seisai bang lytah ching le zai batui cahe hmotah thlawchang katei Khazing a beh teipaw a cang.
\v 38 Ma ningcing taco aaning lang a vong ka, Khazing khatah alawngnah bia a hlai. Jerusalem pachahnah a heh paw sahlo maikaw hai leco ma nysai kong heh a ching he.
\p 
\v 39 Josef le Mari tah Abuipaw phungbia tei a hia a tahpaw maikaw aa tua panging thlu khy taikhei Galili raang aa ungnah khua Nazaret lang cawh aa paleh kaw.
\v 40 Taico nysai cawh ka lai vy longmang, a thaw ka tlung vy longmang ka, singná tah chih ka, Khazing dukhuinah cawh a cung letah a ung.
\s1 Behnah ing chung letah nyhehpaw Zisu
\p 
\v 41 Kung tating tah Zisu a no le a paw cawh Khungsai Panawnah hmang rua pawtah Jerusalem lang a sei tei he.
\v 42 Zisu cawh kung hrawhluihning va tling ka, a phunglang tei hratah Panawnah lang cawh aa sei.
\v 43 Panawnah a chang khy taico a no le a paw cawh ing lang aa va kaw kaw ning tah nyhehpaw Zisu cawh Jerusalem lekhei ung patle ka, canghrasala aaning taco hnih bei he.
\v 44 Aa hrong letah a ung thlang rua tah he ka, ning kheh chung a sei he. Mataico a vesaw sahlo le a sawny hrong letah aa huilai.
\v 45 Ama cawh aa hmuh khawh ly tih taco, Jerusalem khuapui lang khah hui rua pawtah aa paleh kaw he.
\v 46 Ningthung a tling khy tah behnah ingdung chung lekhei, aa va hmuh kaw. Cawngpahtu macang sahlo khakhei a za ty thlang ka, aa bia khah nge he, hae hri he, a za tah leimei.
\v 47 A chaipaw he bia le a hnithai zia, aa thuipaw maikaw cawh aa ning a ang ngetei.
\v 48 A no le a paw tah Ama cawh aa hmuh tihtah aa khuarawh a haa thlang. A no taco, “Ka sawcapaw, zecawtamaw ma hrahei na ma tua? Na paw khatah thlawzawng hmotah pui kaa ca huilai leimei kata caw!” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 49 Zisu taco, “Zecawtamaw naa pa hui? Ka Paw ing letah ka ung ruapaw a cang tahpaw heh hnih bei he ceh maw?” a tah he.
\v 50 Canghrasala, aa hai letei bia a reipaw cawh a silang hnih bei he.
\p 
\v 51 Mataico, aaning khatah Nazaret khua lang cawh sei ka, aa reingé tah a ung. Canghrasala a no taco ma hming vytei heh a lungchung letah a pacung thlang.
\v 52 Taico Zisu cawh kachang vy lai, ka sing vy lai longmang ka, Khazing le cawngsaw dukhuinah a tong.
\c 3
\s1 Baptisma peitu Johan tah langpui a parai
\r (Mt 3:1-12; Mk 1:1-8; Jh 1:19-28)
\p 
\v 1 Tiberias Sizar abuinah kung hrawhluipangaw a tling kung, Pontia Pilat cawh Judia raang uhtu a cangning takhei Herod cawh Galili raang uhbui cang ka, a unypaw Filip cawh Ituria le Trakoniti raang uhbui cang ka, Lusinia cawh Abilen raang uhbui cang ka,
\v 2 Anas le Kaiafa tlangbui alaicaipaw aa cangning takhei, raangcaa letei a ungpaw Zakaria a sawcapaw Johan cung lekhei Khazing bia cawh a va tlung.
\v 3 Jordan tuivaw kaekang raang vytei lang cawh seilai ka, sua ngethainah cawtah angepachihnah baptisma kong phung a rei lai.
\v 4 Khazing khuavang Isaiah cabu letei,
\q1 “Raangcaa letei a y leimeipaw o taco,
\q1 ‘Abuipaw a cawtah langpui parai la,
\q2 a cawtah langpui pading pah my lo.
\q1 
\v 5 Saiho maikaw cawh nai la,
\q2 tlaang le tlangby maikaw cawh panai my lo.
\q1 Lang a kuikalehpaw cawh pading la,
\q2 a bykhi a bylypaw cawh pamai my lo.
\q1 
\v 6 Taico, cawngsaw maikaw tah Khazing a pachahnah cawh aa hmuh a,’ tatah a tah,”\x + \xo 3:6 \xt Isai 40:3-5\x*
\m tatah ciapaw hrakhei.
\p 
\v 7 Johan tah ama khatah baptisma cang ruapaw tei a va chuhpaw zawpui sahlo he cawh, “Naaning pari cangmai pathlah sahlo, Khazing thingaenah a va chuh leimeipaw heh saisai rua pawtah aho tamaw a ca ching he?
\v 8 Na ngepachihnah he ceh cawh a thuipa tah palang my lo. ‘Abraham pathlah sahlo kaa cang peh,’ tatah tah leimei khe o. Ka ca ching he hi, Khazing taco ma alung sahlo heh Abraham sawtei sahlo tah a tua khy thlang he hi.
\v 9 Thinghrang maikaw letah ahrui aa chia thlu thah. Thui chaw a thui lypaw thingkung maikaw cawh hyhly tah me lang bo a cang he a,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 10 Zawpuipaw tah, “A cang caco zemaw kaa tua a?” tatah aa hae.
\p 
\v 11 Johan taco, “Angki zing hning a hnuipaw tah a hnui lypaw khah chaichy seh la, e ruapaw a hnuipaw tah a hnui lypaw cawh pei hrah seh,” tatah a chai he.
\p 
\v 12 Ngungkhui a kheipaw sahlo zong cawh baptisma cang hrá pawtah a vong he ka, “Cawngpahtu, zemaw kaa tua a?” tatah aa hae.
\p 
\v 13 “Khei ruapaw navy tah a hlu vy tah va khei lai khe o,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 14 Mataico raekeh thaikhehpaw sahlo tah, “Kaaning saw zemaw kaa tua a?” tatah aa hae.
\p “Male tangka chu lai khe la, ahmang lypaw tah cawngsaw luithae lai khe o, naa hlo letah naa lungtling thlang seh,” tatah a tah he.
\p 
\v 15 Zawpui taco a ngete ly ngetei tah heh thlang he ka, aa dawngkasawny co, Johan heh Khri a cang thlang thly a, tatah aa rawh.
\v 16 Johan tah aa dawngkasawny hai leco, “Kama taco tui tah baptisma ka ca cangsah he. Canghrasala kama navy tah a rungnaw vypaw a va chuh a. Kama cawh a phepakong rui a thlang tlangpaw hmai cang bei neh. Ama taco Thlawpaw Pathai le me tah baptisma a ca cangsá he a.
\v 17 Saze zeinah cawh a kiá tah tle ka, phuhri letah saze cawh a zei a, achang khah apaang letah rai a ka, asi khah a thi thai lypaw me lang a bo a,” tatah a tah he.
\v 18 Taico Johan tah zawpui vytei cawh a phingphing tah pasynah bia ching he ka, aaning cawh thawngchawbia a cawngpah he.
\p 
\v 19 Canghrasala, Johan tah abui Herod cawh a nytei nupui Herodi a chunah kong letah le ahringpaw chahlynah hming a tuapaw vytei kong letah a mochia tihtah,
\v 20 Herod tah ma vytei cung letah a chahchipaw cawh Johan khah thong-ing chung letah a hrai.
\s1 Zisu baptisma a cangnah le a thokehnah
\r (Mt 1:1-17; 3:13-17; Mk 1:9-11)
\p 
\v 21 Ming vytei baptisma aa cang tlungmang ning takhei, Zisu zong cawh baptisma a cang hrah. Taico thlaw a chang leimei ning taco avai cawh a hong.
\v 22 Thlawpaw Pathai cawh thury hratah a cung letah a za cung. Taico avai taitah o za ring ka, “Nama cawh ka dopaw Ka Sawcapaw na cang, na cung letah ka lung a lawng ngetei,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 23 Zisu cawh phungrei a patho ning tahei kung songthung hrawng a tah. Ama cawh Josef sawtei aa tah.
\q1 Josef cawh Heli a sawtei,
\q1 
\v 24 Heli cawh Mathat a sawtei,
\q1 Mathat cawh Levi a sawtei,
\q1 Levi cawh Melkhi a sawtei,
\q1 Melkhi cawh Janai a sawtei,
\q1 Janai cawh Josef a sawtei,
\q1 
\v 25 Josef cawh Matathia a sawtei,
\q1 Mathathia cawh Amos a sawtei,
\q1 Amos cawh Nahum a sawtei,
\q1 Nahum cawh Esli a sawtei,
\q1 Esli cawh Nakai a sawtei,
\q1 
\v 26 Nakai cawh Matha a sawtei,
\q1 Matha cawh Matathia a sawtei,
\q1 Matathia cawh Semein a sawtei,
\q1 Semein cawh Josek a sawtei,
\q1 Josek cawh Joda a sawtei,
\q1 
\v 27 Joda cawh Joanan a sawtei,
\q1 Joanan cawh Rhesa a sawtei,
\q1 Rhesa cawh Zerubabel a sawtei,
\q1 Zerubabel cawh Shealtia a sawtei,
\q1 Shealtia cawh Neri a sawtei,
\q1 
\v 28 Neri cawh Melkhi a sawtei,
\q1 Melkhi cawh Adi a sawtei,
\q1 Adi cawh Kosam a sawtei,
\q1 Kosam cawh Elmadam a sawtei,
\q1 Elmadam cawh Er a sawtei,
\q1 
\v 29 Er cawh Josua a sawtei,
\q1 Josua cawh Eliezer a sawtei,
\q1 Eliezer cawh Jorim a sawtei,
\q1 Jorim cawh Mathat a sawtei,
\q1 Mathat cawh Levi a sawtei,
\q1 
\v 30 Levi cawh Simeon a sawtei,
\q1 Simeon cawh Judah a sawtei,
\q1 Judah cawh Josef a sawtei,
\q1 Josef cawh Jonam a sawtei,
\q1 Jonam cawh Eliakim a sawtei,
\p 
\v 31 Eliakim cawh Melea a sawtei,
\q1 Melea cawh Mena a sawtei,
\q1 Mena cawh Matatha a sawtei,
\q1 Matatha cawh Nathan a sawtei,
\q1 Nathan cawh David a sawtei,
\q1 
\v 32 David cawh Jesi a sawtei,
\q1 Jesi cawh Obed a sawtei,
\q1 Obed cawh Boaz a sawtei,
\q1 Boaz cawh Salmon a sawtei,
\q1 Salmon cawh Nashon a sawtei,
\p 
\v 33 Nashon cawh Aminada a sawtei,
\q1 Aminada cawh Ram a sawtei,
\q1 Ram cawh Hezron a sawtei,
\q1 Hezron cawh Perez a sawtei,
\q1 Perez cawh Judah a sawtei,
\q1 
\v 34 Judah cawh Jakob a sawtei,
\q1 Jakob cawh Isak a sawtei,
\q1 Isak cawh Abraham a sawtei,
\q1 Abraham cawh Tera a sawtei,
\q1 Tera cawh Nahor a sawtei,
\q1 
\v 35 Nahor cawh Seruk a sawtei,
\q1 Seruk cawh Reu a sawtei,
\q1 Reu cawh Pelek a sawtei,
\q1 Pelek cawh Eba a sawtei,
\q1 Eba cawh Shelah a sawtei,
\q1 
\v 36 Shelah cawh Kainan a sawtei,
\q1 Kainan cawh Arpaksa a sawtei,
\q1 Arpaksa cawh Shem a sawtei,
\q1 Shem cawh Noah a sawtei,
\q1 Noah cawh Lamek a sawtei,
\q1 
\v 37 Lamek cawh Methusela a sawtei,
\q1 Methusela cawh Enok a sawtei,
\q1 Enok cawh Jared a sawtei,
\q1 Jared cawh Mahalale a sawtei,
\q1 Mahalale cawh Kenan a sawtei,
\q1 
\v 38 Kenan cawh Eno a sawtei,
\q1 Eno cawh Seth a sawtei,
\q1 Seth cawh Adam a sawtei,
\q1 Adam cawh Khazing a sawtei a cang.
\c 4
\s1 Setan tah Zisu a tuhso
\r (Mt 4:1-11; Mk 1:12-13)
\p 
\v 1 Zisu cawh Thlawpaw Pathai tah chih ka, Jordan tuivaw taitah va kaw kaw ka, Thlawpaw taco raangcaa lang a seikhui.
\v 2 Ma leco Setan tah ning songli chung tuhso ka, ma chung vytei cawh zehmai a e lynah cawtah a hning taco a ngai a di.
\p 
\v 3 Setan taco, “Khazing Sawcapaw na cang caco, ma alung heh very tah cang law tah ca!” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 4 Zisu taco, “Khazing bia letah ma hrahei ciapaw a cang, ‘Cawngsaw heh very suipaw tah aa hring tlung be!’ ”\x + \xo 4:4 \xt Biary 8:3\x* tatah a chai.
\p 
\v 5 Setan taco Zisu cawh tlaang sangpaw lang kekhui ka, khazaw painah raang vytei khah sungkheh tah hmuhsah ka,
\v 6 taico a hai letah, “Ma vytei nawhnuinah le a rungnawnah heh ka ca pae a, zecawtamaw tatah ma heh kama letah pehpaw cang thah he ka, ka dupaw maikaw cawh ka peh khy he.
\v 7 Macawtaco, na pa beh caco, ma vytei heh na tei a cang a,” a tah.
\p 
\v 8 Zisu taco, “Capathai letah ma hrahei cia a cang, ‘Abuipaw na Khazing khah beh la, Ama a rai suipaw hre my lo,’\x + \xo 4:8 \xt Biary 6:13\x* tah a cang,” tatah a palei.
\p 
\v 9 Setan tah Zisu cawh Jerusalem khuapui lang seikhui ka, behnah ing a sangcainah ing cung lekhei a dawsah ka, “Khazing Sawcapaw na cang caco, ma taihei a zythlah tua.
\v 10 Zecawtamaw tatah ma hrahei cia a cang,
\q1 ‘Nama na kong lehei Khazing tah
\q2 a vaiming sahlo khah naw pei a he ka,
\q1 
\v 11 na phe cawh alung letah
\q2 na khong ly nápawtah aa kiá tah aa ca caling a,’\x + \xo 4:11 \xt Hlaw 91:11-12\x* a tah,”
\m tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 12 Zisu tah, “Abuipaw na Khazing cawh hnehsah kheh, tahpaw a cang,”\x + \xo 4:12 \xt Biary 6:16\x* tatah a chai.
\p 
\v 13 Setan tah Zisu cawh ma vytei hrahei a tuhso khy taitah hmelang cai a raicangpaw cawtah a seisai.
\s1 Nazaret letah Zisu du bei he
\r (Mt 4:12-17; 13:53-58; Mk 1:14-15; 6:1-6)
\p 
\v 14 Thlawpaw Pathai thawtlungnah khatah Zisu cawh Galili raang lang a paleh kaw ka, a konglang cawh khuapui kaekang vytei letah a thang.
\v 15 Aa synagog\f + \fr 4:15 \ft Synagog cawh, \fq Juda sahlo behnah ing,\ft a cang.\f* sahlo letah cawngpah he ka, ming vytei tah Ama cawh aa reithai.
\p 
\v 16 A changchynah khua Nazaret khua lang cawh sei ka, Sabat\f + \fr 4:16 \ft Sabat cawh, \fq Juda cawngsaw sahlo a hianah ning,\ft a cang.\f* ning taco a tua teipaw phung hratah synagog lang kha a nae. Taico capathai rei pawtah a daw.
\v 17 Khazing khuavang Isaiah bia, sapho lingpaw cabu cawh a kih letah aa hlai. Ma cabu cawh pathlang ka, ma hratei ciapaw khah a hmuh,
\q1 
\v 18 “Abuipaw Thlawpaw cawh ka cung letah a ung,
\q1 zecawtamaw tatah mehsisah sahlo hai letah
\q2 thawngchawbia rei rua pawtah kama cawh sathy thu tah a pa thing.
\q1 Thong letei a tangpaw sahlo he piachuanah ruapaw tlang y pawtah pa taw ka,
\q2 a mehcopaw sahlo mehvang sápaw le tlaihnawh a cangpaw sahlo thochua rua pawtah le,
\q1 
\v 19 Abuipaw dukhuipaw kung kong y khui rua pawtah,”\x + \xo 4:19 \xt Isai 61:1-2\x*
\m tahpaw heh.
\p 
\v 20 Mataico sapho lingpaw cabu cawh ling kaw ka, a kaitu khah pei ka, a ty. Synagog chung letei ming vytei taco a cung letah aa meh aa chia thlu thlang.
\v 21 Aa hai leco, “Atoning letah ma Capathai heh naa thuipaw tei hrahei a tling myca,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 22 Ming maikaw tah a kong chaw rei he ka, a kaw taitei ningdonah bia a chuhpaw cung leco aa ningang ngetei thlu ka, “Ma heh Josef a sawcapaw khah cang bei maw?” aa tah.
\p 
\v 23 Zisu tah aa hai leco, “Ma phungthluh bia heh naa pa reiso hrahring tae hi, ‘Sibuipaw, nama le nama a dangsah tua, Kapernaum khua letei na tuapaw kaa thuipaw khah ma na changchynah khua lehei tua hrah!’ tahpaw heh.
\p 
\v 24 Biahmuisui ka ca ching he, Khazing khuavang cawh ama a pinah khua leco cyhlang bei he.
\v 25 Khazing khuavang Elija chai lekhei, Israel raang chung letah lahme hlupui a ung he. Kung thung le a chy khua kaang ka, raang pungpaluh letah cakaang a thaw tah a tlung.
\v 26 Canghrasala Elija cawh Israel raang lahme maikaw khatah taw cang hlui be. Sidon raang, Zarefat khua letei a ungpaw lahme khatah suipaw taw a cang.
\v 27 Mataico, Khazing khuavang Elisha chaining zong takhei, Israel raang chung letah mehthinghmui hlupui a ung he. Canghrasala Siria cawngsaw Naaman tah cy ly co ahohmai a dangsah tlung bei he,” tatah a tah he.
\p 
\v 28 Synagog letei a ungpaw ming vytei tah aa thui tihtah aa thing aa ae ngetei.
\v 29 Tho he ka, Ama cawh khua lailang papia he ka, aa khuathui tlaang, lungkang lang nang thlah pawtah aa seikhui.
\v 30 Canghrasala zawpui hrong taikhei a zuh thlah ka, a seihly.
\s1 Zisu tah thlawpaw pialuipaw a tingchua
\r (Mk 1:21-28)
\p 
\v 31 Ma khy taico Galili raang, Kapernaum khua lang cawh cungthlah ka, Sabat ning tah zawpui khah a cawngpah he.
\v 32 A bia cawh nawhnuinah chi tah a cangnah cawtah a cawngpahnah cawh aa khuarawh a haa thlang.
\p 
\v 33 Synagog leco, thlawpaw pialuipaw tei a tlepaw cawngsaw pakheh ung ka, a thangpui tah y ka,
\v 34 “Vy, Nazaret Zisu, kaaning khahei zemaw na du? Kaaning hlyde ruapaw tamaw na vong? Nama cawh ahomaw na cang tahpaw ka hni, Khazing Mehpathai na cang,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 35 Zisu tah, “De teitah ung! A chung taikhei ka pia,” tatah a hrangso. Ma khy taico thlawpaw pialuipaw tah ma cawngsawpaw cawh ming vytei mehmuh leco phongchai ka, hmaw phosah lytah a piathlah.
\p 
\v 36 Cawngsaw vytei cawh aa ningang thlang ka, pakheh le pakheh khah, “Zehapaw cawngpahnah maw a cang he? Naw hnuinah le hmingtuakhynah khatah thlawpaw pialuipaw zong naw pei he katei, aa pia thlangpaw heh!” tatah aa tah he.
\v 37 Taico Zisu kong thongpang cawh ma raang kaekang vytei cawh a thang thlu.
\s1 Zisu tah mehlupui a dangsah he
\r (Mt 8:14-17; Mk 1:29-34)
\p 
\v 38 Zisu cawh synagog taitah piathlah ka, Simon ing lang a nae. Simon a nupuino a no cawh asaw tah a sahpui tah nang ka, Zisu cawh bawnah aa haepah.
\v 39 Zisu tah a bung hno ka, a sawnah khah raw ka, a sawnah taco a thlaw. Sungkheh tah ka tho ka, aaning sahlo cawh a tangtui he.
\p 
\v 40 Ning a va tlah lang leco asawnah phingphing a hnuipaw vytei khah Zisu khatah va chua khui he ka, aa cung letah a kih pahnia cy ka, aaning sahlo cawh a dangsah he.
\v 41 Ma hlui co, mehlupui chung taitah khachia sahlo khah pia he ka, “Nama cawh Khazing Sawcapaw na cang,” tatah a y he. Canghrasala aaning cawh Zisu tah raw he ka, Khri a cang tahpaw aa hni cawtah khei aa rei thlawpaw khah sai bei he.
\p 
\v 42 Mong khua va dui ka, Zisu cawh a kingdangnah lang khah sei ka, zawpui tah Ama khah aa hui. Taico a ungnah aa va phah tihtah aaning khah seisai khawh ly rua pawtah tle a pachia he.
\v 43 Canghrasala Zisu tah, “Khua hring lang zong letah Khazing painah raang thawngchawbia ka rei hrah ruapaw a cang, ma ruapaw taco tawpaw cang tlung neh ka,” a tah he.
\v 44 Taico Judia raang synagog sahlo letah a cawngpah lai longmang he.
\c 5
\s1 A hmetawcai a hningzuitu sahlo ynah
\r (Mt 4:18-22; Mk 1:16-20)
\p 
\v 1 Ningkhehpaw cawh Zisu cawh Genesaret tuiping ngaekang leco a daw thlang. Cawngsaw zawpui taco a pungso thlang he ka, Khazing bia cawh aa nge.
\v 2 Ngaw a tlepaw sahlo tei aa so aa suh kaa letei aa seisaipaw tuilawng sanghning khah ngaekang letah a hmuh.
\v 3 Simon a tei a cangpaw tuilawng chunglang cawh a nae ka, “Ngaekang taitah tui le chung vy lang hrui vy bang law,” tatah Simon cawh a tah. Taico a ty ka, zawpui cawh tuilawng taico a cawngpah he.
\p 
\v 4 Bia a reipaw a pachang taico Simon hai letah, “Tui a thunah vypaw lang pange la, ma leco na so khah va tua,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 5 Simon taco, “Hruitupaw, zaikhuadui reithui ngetei tah va he peh ka, sangkheh hmai tle bei peh. Canghrasala, nama na bia tei hratah ka va thlang tua a,” tatah a palei.
\p 
\v 6 Ma hraco tua he ka, ngaw a hlupui a o cawtah aa so sahlo zong a kychy pai thlu.
\v 7 Mataico, tuilawng ahringpaw letei a ungpaw sahlo khah va ma baw law tatah aa kiá tah aa kui he. Mataico a vong he ka, tuilawng sanghning tah ngaw cawh dui he ka, a chi tu cawtah tuilawng cawh tui lang a phungpai daimang he.
\p 
\v 8 Simon Piter tah ma hming vytei cawh a hmuh tihtah Zisu phehrang letah a bawh ka, a hai leco, “Mehsua ka cang, Abuipaw, pa seisai thlang law,” a tah.
\v 9 Ama le a vesaw sahlo cawh ngaw hlupui aa tlenah cawtah khei aa khuarawh haa ngetei ka,
\v 10 Simon a vesaw sahlo a cangpaw Zebedi sawcapaw leh Jeims le Johan cawh aa khuarawh aa haa ngetei hrah.
\p Mataico Zisu tah Simon hai letah, “Ci kheh, atohei co cawngsaw na tle myca he a,” tatah a tah.
\v 11 Macawtaco tuilawng sahlo khah ngaekang lang piakhui he ka, zezongpui seisai tah Zisu cawh aa zui.
\s1 Thinghmuihri a ingpaw
\r (Mt 8:1-4; Mk 1:40-45)
\p 
\v 12 Zisu cawh khuapui hrawng letei khua kheh letah a ungning taco, thinghmuihri tei a pahlong thlangpaw cawngsawpaw pakheh Ama khatah a vong ka, Zisu a hmuh cangkawleh alui letah a khuh panai ka, ma hrahei naw ka, “Abuipaw na du caco na pa dangsah khy,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 13 Zisu taco a kiá tah va pazah ka, ama cawh va tong ka, “Na dang cawh du neh ka, dang myca,” tatah a tah. Ma cangkaw leco, a thinghmuihri vytei cawh a pathai.
\p 
\v 14 Taico, Zisu tah ma hrahei bia patai ka, “Ahohmai ching khe lo, ma duitei cawh va sei la, tlangbui a va ming sah la, Moses phungbia hrakhei thuihlainah va tua, mapaw suico dangsah na cangpaw khah ming maikaw tah aa ca hni a,” a tah.
\p 
\v 15 Canghmaisala, Zisu a konglang cawh a thang vy lo leimei ka, mehlupui tah a bia nge pawtah le aa sawnah pawhe dangsah rua pawtah Ama cawh aa va pange.
\v 16 Canghrasala Zisu cawh a kingdangnah lang sei tah thlawchang pawtah a piathlah tei.
\s1 Zisu tah a songbepaw a dangsah
\r (Mt 9:1-8; Mk 2:1-12)
\p 
\v 17 Ningkheh cawh Zisu tah a cawngpah leimeining he tah Farasi le phungbia cawngpahtu sahlo, Galili raang khua ting taitah le Judia raang khua ting taitah le Jerusalem khuapui taitei a va chuhpaw sahlo cawh a ty thlang hrah he ka, a sahpaw sahlo he dangsah rua pawtah Abuipaw thawtlungnah cawh a cung letah a ung.
\v 18 Mehthaikheh tah a songbepaw pakheh a iphaw khatah a ka song lai he ka, ing chunglang a nae khui tah Zisu kung tlungkhui pawtah a pachia he.
\v 19 Cawngsaw aa hlutunah cawtah a kung phahkhuinah lang hmuh be ca he ka, ingcung lang aa kekhui. Ing aa daepaw lungphae khah hneihly he ka, cawngsawpaw cawh iphaw chitah zawpui hrawng lekhei Zisu hme lalei leco aa za thlah.
\p 
\v 20 Zisu tah aa zingnah khah a hmuh tihtah a songbepaw hai leco, “Ka dua, na suanah vytei cawh ngethai a cang,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 21 Farasi le phungbia cawngpahtu sahlo taco, “Ma cawngsaw heh ahomaw a cang? Khazing reipachianah bia a rei hi! Khazing tah ly co ahomaw suanah a ngethai khy?” tatah aa lungchung tah aa pacang.
\p 
\v 22 Zisu tah aa lungchung rawhnah cawh hnih ka, “Zecawtamaw ma hrahei naa lungchung tah naa pacang?
\v 23 ‘Na suanah sahlo cawh ngethai a cang,’ tahpaw maw a neh vy maw? ‘Tho la, sei,’ tahpaw maw a neh vy?
\v 24 Canghrasala, Cawngsaw Sawcapaw heh aluicung lehei sua ngethai khynah naw a hnui taheh ka ca hmuh sá he a,” tah ka, a songbepaw hai letaco, “Tho la, na iphaw a lah la, ing lang a dih,” tatah a tah.
\v 25 Sung sungkheh tah aa hmekaw leco a daw ka, a iphaw cawh law ka, Khazing reithai hmotah ing lang cawh a dih.
\v 26 Ming maikaw cawh aa ningang ngetei ka, Khazing khah reithai he ka, “Atoning heh hming khuarawha chuipaw kaa hmuh hi,” aa tah tlungmang.
\s1 Levi ynah
\r (Mt 9:9-13; Mk 2:13-17)
\p 
\v 27 Ma khy taico Zisu cawh piathlah ka, ngungkhui a kheipaw Levi aa tahpaw cawh ngungkhui kheinah hming letah a tythlangpaw khah hmuh ka, “Va pa zui,” tatah a tah.
\v 28 Taico Levi cawh tho ka, zezongpui seisai tah Zisu cawh a zui.
\p 
\v 29 Mataico Levi tah Zisu cawtah a ing letah lawhdangnah rungnaw ngeteipaw a tuapah. Ngungkhui a kheipaw mehlupui le ahringpaw mehlupui khah aaning khatah batui aa e hrah.
\v 30 Canghrasala Farasi le aa phu a cangpaw phungbia cawngpahtu sahlo taco, Zisu hningzuitu sahlo hai leco, “Zecawtamaw ngungkhui a kheitu sahlo le ahringpaw mehsua sahlo khatah naa e naa ding lai?” tatah aa mochia he.
\p 
\v 31 Zisu tah aa hai leco, “A dang thlangpaw tah sibui aa hia tlung be, a dang lypaw tah pui aa hia!
\v 32 Mehding y rua pawtah ka vong tlung be, mehsua sahlo khah aa suanah a ngepachihsah rua pawtah ka vong hri hi,” tatah a chai he.
\s1 Batui cahenah kong Zisu aa hae
\r (Mt 9:14-17; Mk 2:18-22)
\p 
\v 33 Aaning sahlo taco Zisu hai letah, “Baptisma peitu Johan a hningzuitu sahlo cawh batui cahe tah thlawchang tei he ka, Farasi phunglang aa zuipaw sahlo zong tah ma hraco aa tua tei hrah. Canghrasala nama na hningzuitu sahlo heh e le ding tah aa ung thlang,” tatah aa tah.
\p 
\v 34 Zisu taco, “Songpaw sahlo cawh nupui a chuipaw satlepaw khatah aa ung chung taco batui a cahe tei he maw?
\v 35 Canghrasala nupui a chuipaw khah aa hrong taitei aa seikhuinah cai khah a phah tae a. Ma taico aa cahe tae thlang a,” tatah a palei he.
\p 
\v 36 Ma tawchingnah bia zong heh Zisu taco a ching he, “Ahotahmai paithang a thapaw khah hriachy tah chaichi a paringpaw khah a beithlah bang bei he. Ma hratei aa tua caco a thapaw khah a rawhrang a ka, a paringpaw letei a thapaw aa baipaw zong khah a tlah hrá be.
\v 37 Mataico ahotahmai misurhang a hringtui khah sapho tuithei a paringpaw letah rai bang bei he. Aa rai caco, misurhang a hring taco sapho tuithei cawh tingchy a ka, taico misurhang khah zuh thlu a ka, sapho tuithei zong a rawh thlu a.
\v 38 Ma navy co, misurhang a hringtui cawh sapho tuithei a thapaw letah rai hripaw a cang.
\v 39 Cawngsaw maikaw tah misurhang ahlungpaw aa ding khy taitah a thapaw ding du khawh bei he. ‘A hlungpaw a chah vy,’ aa tah,” tatah aa tah.
\c 6
\s1 Sabat Buipaw
\r (Mt 12:1-14; Mk 2:23—3:6)
\p 
\v 1 Zisu tah Sabat ningkhehpaw cawh saze lui cahrong ka, a hningzuitu sahlo taco saangsu cawh pahrih he ka, aa kih letah rua he ka, aa e lai.
\v 2 Farasi cawngsaw thaikheh tah Zisu cawh, “Sabat ning letah tua phung a cang lypaw zecawtamaw naa tua?” tatah aa tah he.
\p 
\v 3 Zisu taco, “David tei a vesaw sahlo khatah aa ngaidi ning tei a tuapaw khah rei bang bei he ceh maw?
\v 4 Khazing behnah ing lang a nae ka, tlangbui sahlo tah ly co ahotahmai e phung a cang lypaw, Khazing aa dangnah very khah a e! Taico a chy khah a vesaw sahlo zong a peh hrah he kho!” tatah a palei he.
\v 5 Taico Zisu tah aa hai letah, “Cawngsaw Sawcapaw heh Sabat Buipaw a cang,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 6 Sabat ning vypaw leco Zisu cawh synagog lang a nae ka, a cawngpah he. Ma leco cawngsawpaw pakheh a cacang lang kih a songpaw a ung.
\v 7 Farasi le phungbia cawngpahtu sahlo taco Zisu cawh sua aa pu khy nápawtah a bo he ka, Sabat ning tah ma cawngsawpaw cawh a dangsah maw dangsah ly takhah aa ngia thlang.
\v 8 Canghrasala, Zisu tah aa lungchung tei aa pacangpaw khah hnih thlang ka, a kih a songpaw hai leco, “Ming vytei hme lehei tho la, a daw,” tatah a tah. Taico tho ka, a daw.
\p 
\v 9 Ma khy taico Zisu tah aa hai letah, “Sabat ning tahei chahnah tua maw a phung a cang, chahlynah maw? Hringnah pachah heh maw a phung a cang, thaw heh maw?” tatah a hae he.
\p 
\v 10 A kaekang leteipaw sahlo cawh ming he ka, ma cawngsawpaw hai leco, “Na kih pathlang,” tatah a tah. Taico a kih cawh pathlang ka, a dang.
\v 11 Canghrasala, Farasi le phungbia cawngpahtu sahlo cawh aa thingae ngetei ka, Zisu cawh zekhatamaw tua he peh seh la, a cha a, tahpaw khah pakheh le pakheh aa reisia.
\s1 Apostol pahrawhluihning
\r (Mt 10:1-4; Mk 3:13-19)
\p 
\v 12 Ma cai leco Zisu cawh thlawchang rua pawtah tlaang cung lang ke ka, a zing zaikhuadui Khazing khatah thlaw a chang.
\v 13 Mong khua va dui ka, a hningzuitu sahlo cawh y he ka, pahrawhluihning khah thing he ka, aaning sahlo cawh apostol rai a khing he.
\v 14 Simon (Piter tatei ming sahpaw) a unypaw Andru, Jeims, Johan, Filip, Barthalomeo,
\v 15 Mathai, Thomas, Alfas sawcapaw Jeims, ci le phing a dawkhuipaw Simon,
\v 16 Jeims a sawcapaw Juda le Zisu a luitu paw Judas Iskariot a cang he.
\s1 Bonghnang le cingpingnah
\r (Mt 4:23—5:12)
\p 
\v 17 Zisu cawh aaning sahlo khaco seithlah ka, bai arainah letah a ung. Ama a hning a zuipaw he mehlupui le Judia raang le Jerusalem khuapui, Tair le Sidon khua rili ngaekang raang sahlo taitah mehlupui a va chuh he.
\v 18 A bia khah nawthlia rua pawtah le a sawnah pawhe zong dangsah rua pawtah aa va chua. Thlawpaw pialuipaw tei a tlepaw sahlo zong he tah dangnah aa hmuh.
\v 19 Mehlupui tah Ama khah tong khy cy a zong he. Zecawtamaw tatah Ama taikhei hmingtuakhynah khah pia ka, aaning vytei cawh a dangsah he.
\p 
\v 20 A hningzuitu sahlo cawh ming he ka,
\q1 “Naaning sisahpaw sahlo bonghnang naa ting,
\q2 Khazing painah raang cawh naa cawtah a cang.
\q1 
\v 21 Ato letei a ngai a dipaw sahlo bonghnang naa ting,
\q2 naa ri a vaw tae a.
\q1 Ato letei a cah leimeipaw sahlo bonghnang naa ting,
\q2 na hnui tae he ceh.
\q1 
\v 22 Cawngsaw sahlo tah aa ca hua tih he tah bonghnang naa ting,
\q2 Cawngsaw Sawcapaw a cawngsaw naa cangnah rawng tah ca patlia a he ka,
\q2 naa zy ca lang a he ka, naa ming aa ca pachia tih he tah bonghnang naa ting.
\p 
\v 23 Ma ning taco naa thawchah seh la, lunglawng thawchah tah a pathlo my lo, zecawtamaw tatah vaicung letah naa longmai rungnaw ngeteipaw a ung. Ma hrahei aaning aa pathlahtu sahlo he takhei Khazing khuavang sahlo khah aa za tua tei he.
\q1 
\v 24 Canghrasala naaning mehrung sahlo naa cing a ping,
\q2 zecawtamaw tatah a nawngnah cawh naa hmuh thlu thah.
\q1 
\v 25 Ato letei naaning a ri a vawpaw sahlo naa cing a ping,
\q2 zecawtamaw tatah naa ngai a di tae a.
\q1 Naaning ato letei a hnui leimeipaw sahlo naa cing a ping,
\q2 naa ngechia a ka, na cah tae he ceh.
\q1 
\v 26 Cawngsaw maikaw tah aa ca pachaw tih he tah naa cing a ping.
\q2 Ma hrahei aaning a pathlahtu sahlo tah khuavang pakheipaw sahlo khah aa za tua tei he.
\s1 Caraepaw zong donah
\r (Mt 5:38-48)
\p 
\v 27 Canghrasala, ka bia naw a thliapaw sahlo, ka ca ching he hi, naa carae sahlo cawh va do la, a ca huapaw sahlo cung leco chahnah va tua my lo.
\v 28 Chia a ca reipahpaw he sahlo cawh bonghnang song my lo, a ca zongtepaw sahlo cawh thlawchangpah my lo.
\v 29 Pakheh kheh tah na bai rakheh lang a ca cabai caco, a rakheh lang zong khah cong pah vy thlang. Pakheh kheh tah na pai a ca lah pah caco, na angkilai lah zong ei kheh.
\v 30 A ca haepaw maikaw cawh pei la, na hnuipaw a ca lah pahpaw he cawh hae kaw khawh khe lo.
\v 31 Na cung letah tua he seh tah na dupaw hrakhei male cung letah va tua my lo.
\p 
\v 32 Naaning a ca dopaw suipaw naa do caco he zemaw amia naa hmuh a? Mehsua zong tah ma hapaw cawh aa tua thlang hrah.
\v 33 Naa cung letah a chahpaw cawngsaw cung letah naa chahpaw takhei zemaw amia naa hmuh? Mehsua zong tah ma hapaw cawh aa tua thlang hrah.
\v 34 A ca pei kaw khypaw he hming naa hleipaw he takhei zemaw amia naa hmuh? Mehsua sahlo zong tahmai a ialia tah hmuh kaw rua taco aaning le aaning a hlei thlang hrah he.
\v 35 Canghrasala naa carae sahlo khah va do la, aa cung letah chahnah va tua my lo. Hmuh kaw hrah du tah male hming va hlei khe lo. Mataico longmai rungnawpaw hmuh a he ceh ka, Cungnungcai Khazing sawtei sahlo naa cang a he ceh. Zecawtamaw tatah Ama cawh mehsua le mehchawly cung letah a vei a sy.
\v 36 Naa Paw vaicung leteipaw tah zaangsawnah a ca hnuipaw he hratah zaang a saw cy my lo.
\s1 Male biacepah
\r (Mt 7:1-5)
\p 
\v 37 Male bia cepah khe la, naaning zong biace pah cang hrá bei ceh. Ahohmai thaily va cangsah khe o, naaning zong thaily ca cangsah hrá bei he. Ngethai la, naaning zong ngethai na cang hrá he ceh.
\v 38 Pei la, peh na cang hrá he ceh. Achaw teitah neh pá tah, baichai tah, carawh pai tah a chihluinah tai peh naa cang he ceh. Na hmangpaw nehnah pawtei khei aa ca neh pah kaw hrá a,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 39 Ma tawchingnah bia zong heh a chingpai he, “Mehco tah mehco cawh lang a chui khy a maw? Aa pahning tah khobatlung lang tla bei he maw?
\v 40 A cawngpaw cawh a cawngpahtu cung letah ung be. Canghrasala, a tlungtlianah tai a cawng khy taitah a cawngpahtu hratah a cang hrah a.
\p 
\v 41 Nama na mehkho letei thingphae khah pacang taw lytah na unypaw mehkho letei thingpatlaw khah zecawtamaw na mingpah?
\v 42 Nama na mehkho chung letei thingphae khah a hmuh tlung lytah zekhatamaw na unypaw cawh, ‘Na mehbang khah ca tho pá neh,’ na tah khy? Naaning cungmai raipha sahlo naaning naa mehkho letei thingphae khah thohly taw la, taico naa unypaw a mehkho letei mehbang cawh tho pá pawtah a se pawtah na hmuh khy a.
\s1 Thingkungpaw le a thui
\r (Mt 7:17-20; 12:34-35)
\p 
\v 43 Thingkung cawh a kung a chah caco, a thui a chah, a kung a chiahru caco thui chia a thui.
\v 44 Thingkung maikaw cawh aa thui tah hni a cang he. Thuiku cawh ahling kung taitah lo bang bei he. A cang ly leh misur thui cawh ahling kung taitah lo bang hrah bei he.
\v 45 Mehchaw taco a lungchung letei a pacungpaw a chawpaw taikhei hmingchaw chuasah ka, mehchawly taco a lungchung letei achaw lypaw a pacungpaw taikhei hming chahly a chuasah. A kaw taitei a reichuapaw cawh a lungchung letei a chihluipaw khah a cang.
\s1 Ing a sahpaw mehsing le mehruh kong
\r (Mt 7:24-27)
\p 
\v 46 Ka reipaw tua tlung lytah zecawtamaw, ‘Abuipaw, Abuipaw,’ tatah naa pa y?
\v 47 Kama kha a vong katei, ka bia khah thui tah a zuipaw cawh zekhamaw a lo tahpaw ka ca ming sá he a.
\v 48 Ma hapaw cawngsaw cawh ing a sahpaw, a thuh pui tah atung kho co katei, alung puino cung letei a bingpaw khatah a lo he. Khua a rupui tah va so ka, tuisai tah ing cawh nang ka, canghrasala a calawh be, achaw teitah sahpaw a cangnah cawtah.
\v 49 Canghrasala, kama khatah a vong katei, ka bia khah thuí tah a zui tlung lypaw cawh alui cakhawngpaw letei a tung padawpaw a cy lypaw ing khatah a lo. Khua a rupui tah va so ka, ing cawh a nang tihtah pohly palang ka, a dawngkasawny tah a rawh cehceh,” a tah he.
\c 7
\s1 Raekeh buipaw a zingnah
\r (Mt 8:5-13; Jh 4:43-54)
\p 
\v 1 Taico Zisu tah ma bia vytei cawh zawpui thuí tah a rei khy taitah Kapernaum khua lang a sei.
\v 2 Ma leco raebuipaw a saecapaw, a buipaw tei a do ngeteipaw cawh a sah ka, a thi daimang tei.
\v 3 Ma raebuipaw taco Zisu kong cawh a thui tihtah Juda macang thaikheh cawh taw he ka, Zisu cawh a vong seh la, a saecapaw heh va dangsah ky seh tatah va naw law a tah he.
\v 4 Zisu kung aa va tlung tihtah hmuisui teitah naw he ka, “Ma cawngsaw heh bong tlang a tlahpaw a cang.
\v 5 Kaa mingphing a dopaw cang ka, kaa synagog zong heh Ama tah a sahpaw a cang,” tatah aa tah.
\v 6 Macawtaco Zisu cawh aaning khaco a sei.
\p Ing a va phah daimang letah raebuipaw taco a vesaw sahlo cawh taw he ka, ma hrahei a va chingsah he. “Abuipaw, reithui a lah du kheh, ka ing heh nama na naenah tlangpaw cang be.
\v 7 Macawtaco kama zong nama kha a vong tlangpaw tah a rawh hrah bei neh. Canghrasala bia kaw kheh teitah na rei caco, ka saecapaw cawh a dang thlang a.
\v 8 Kama zong nawhnuinah rai letah a ungpaw cang neh ka, ka rai letah raekeh sahlo a ung hrah he. Pakheh cawh, ‘Sei,’ tah neh ka, sei ka, pakheh cawh, ‘A vong,’ tah neh ka, a vong. Ka saecapaw cawh, ‘Ma heh tua,’ tah neh ka, a tua thlang,” tatah a chingsah he.
\p 
\v 9 Zisu tah ma bia cawh a thui tihtah a ningang ngetei ka, a va zuipaw he zawpui lang cawh a hui ka, “Biahmuisui ka ca ching he, Israel mingphing chung letah hmai ma tluh zingnah heh hmuh bang bei neh,” a tah he.
\v 10 Mataico raebuipaw tei a tawpaw sahlo he khah ing aa va phah kaw tihtah a saecapaw khah a dang thahpaw khah aa hmuh.
\s1 Zisu tah lahmeno sawtei a patho kaw
\p 
\v 11 Ma khy cangkaw tei leco, Zisu cawh Nain aa tahpaw khua lang khah a sei. A hningzuitu sahlo le zawpuipaw cawh Ama khatah a sei hrah he.
\v 12 Khuapui a naenah hawkaw aa phah daimang ning taco mehthi rawh a ka songlai he ka, mehthi cawh lahmeno a hnuitlakangpaw sawcapaw a cang. Khuachung cawngsaw zawpui zong a no khatah a ka seilai hrah he.
\v 13 Abuipaw tah lahmeno cawh a hmuh tihtah ningdo ngetei ka, “Cah kheh,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 14 Taico ka ke thlah ka, rawh kong cawh va tong ka, rawh kong a pupaw sahlo cawh a daw thlang he. “Satle, tho law, ka ca tah,” tatah a tah.
\v 15 Mehthi cawh a ty ka, bia a ka rei. Taico Zisu tah a no cawh a peh kaw.
\p 
\v 16 Aa dawngkasawny tah ci he ka, aa ningang pai tah ka, Khazing khah aa reithai. “Kaa hrawng letah Khazing khuavang rungnawpaw a va paly hi, Khazing cawh a cawngsaw sahlo bong rua pawtah a vong myca hi!” aa tah.
\v 17 Ma Zisu kong heh Judia raang pungpaluh le a kaekang raang lekhei a thang thlu.
\s1 Zisu le Baptisma peitu Johan
\r (Mt 11:1-19)
\p 
\v 18 Johan hningzuitu sahlo taco ma konglang vytei khah Johan cawh aa ching. Johan tah a hningzuitu pahning khah y he ka,
\v 19 Abuipaw khatah ma bia heh hae rua pawtah a taw he. “Nama heh a vong lepaw cawh na cang maw? A cang ly leh ahringpaw maw kaa haw a?” tatah a va tahsah he.
\p 
\v 20 Ma cawngsaw sahlo cawh Zisu kung aa va tlung tihtah a hai leco, “Baptisma peitu Johan tah, ‘Nama heh a vong lepaw cawh na cang maw? A cang ly leh ahringpaw maw kaa haw a?’ tatah nama hae rua pawtah a ma sia,” tatah aa tah.
\p 
\v 21 Ma ningcai ceingei leco Zisu tah a sahpaw le a dang lypaw mehlupui le thlawpaw pialuipaw tei a tlepaw sahlo he cawh dangsah he ka, a mehcopaw zong khah khua a hmuhsah kaw he.
\v 22 Zisu tah Johan tei a va tawpaw he sahlo hai leco, “Va sei kaw la, naa hmuhpaw le naa thuipaw heh Johan cawh va ching my lo. Mehco sahlo tah khua aa hmuh, a songbepaw zong lang a sei he, thinghmuihri a ingpaw sahlo zong dang he ka, a naw a pangpaw sahlo tah khua aa thui. A thipaw zong tho kaw he ka, mehsisah zong tah thawngchawbia aa thui myca.
\v 23 Kama ka kong letei lung langlo tah a ung lypaw cawngsaw cawh bonghnang a ting,” tatah a palei he.
\p 
\v 24 Johan tei a tawpaw sahlo aa sei khy taico Zisu tah zawpui sahlo hai leco Johan konglang khah a ching he. “Ze ming ruapaw tamaw raangcaa lang naa sei? Thli tei a taikalypaw tuiphi kung ming ruapaw tamaw?
\v 25 Ma hratei a cang ly caco, ze ming ruapaw tamaw naa sei? Chaichi chaw a tuapaw cawngsaw ming ruapaw tamaw? Cang tlung be, chaichi amai a rupaw a tua katei, hmingchaw sangsaw a hnuipaw he cawh siangpahrang ing letah pui aa ung ky caw!
\v 26 A cang caco, ze ming ruapaw tamaw naa sei? Khazing khuavang ming ruapaw tamaw? A cang, Khazing khuavang navy tah a lai vypaw kong ka ca ching he.
\v 27 Ma heh Khazing bia letei ciapaw Ama a kong cawh a cang,
\q1 ‘Ka tlang ypaw cawh na hmelang ka taw a,
\q2 na hme letei na langpui a parai ruapaw tah!’\x + \xo 7:27 \xt Mala 3:1\x*
\m 
\v 28 Ka ca ching he hi, canu tei sahpaw saw leco Johan navy tah alai vypaw ahohmai ung bei he, canghrasala Khazing painah raang letei a chia caipaw hmai heh Johan navy tah alai vy,” a tah.
\p 
\v 29 Cawngsaw vytei ngungkhui a kheipaw sahlo takhei hmai, Zisu bia cawh aa thui tihtah Khazing langpui a ding tahpaw khah aa lung a tling. Zemaw tah pawco, aaning sahlo cawh Johan tei baptisma a peh ciapaw sahlo aa cangnah cawtah a cang.
\v 30 Canghrasala, Farasi le phungbia a thai ngeteipaw sahlo he taco Khazing tei aa cawtah khua a khang pahpaw he khah aa ei. Zecawtamaw tatah aaning sahlo cawh Johan baptisma hmai a cang balang bei he.
\p 
\v 31 Zisu tah, “Atochai cawngsaw heh zekhatamaw ka tawching he a? Zekhamaw a lo he?
\v 32 Aaning sahlo cawh chodo tlang letei a ty thlangpaw nyheh sahlo khatah a lo he.
\q1 ‘Phipahli ca tungpah he peh ka,
\q2 naa lang tlung be.
\q1 Mehthi hlawsah he peh ka,
\q2 naa caw tlung be,’
\m tatah aaning leh aaning a tahpaw nyheh sahlo khatah a lo he.
\v 33 Zecawtamaw tatah baptisma peitu Johan cawh va chuh ka, very e lytah le misurhang ding lytah ung ka, ‘Khachia tah a pahrang,’ tatah naa tah.
\v 34 Cawngsaw Sawcapaw a vong ka, e ka, ding ka, ‘Ding le e suipaw a pacang, mehsua sahlo le ngungkhui a kheitu sahlo vesaw,’ naa tah.
\v 35 Canghrasala, singnah cawh a hming tuapaw sahlo takhei ahmang takhah a palang,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Mehsua no tah Zisu sathy a thu
\p 
\v 36 Farasipaw a cangpaw pakheh tah Zisu cawh zaibatui e pawtah a hrui. Macawtaco, Farasipaw ing lang cawh a vaw ka, e pawtah a ty.
\v 37 Canu pakheh mehsua ngetei no, ma khua letei a ung hrahpaw taco Zisu cawh Farasipaw ing letah zaibatui a e leimei tahpaw khah a thui. Sathy ringthopaw cawh lungrang tuithei khei a va tle.
\v 38 Taico a hninglang tah a phe hrang leco a daw ka, cah ka, a phe cawh a mehthli tah pacingsah thlu ka, ma khy taico a sang tah hruh ka, a phepazaw cawh hnang ka, ringthopaw cawh a bia.
\p 
\v 39 Zisu zaibatui e a hruipaw Farasipaw taco, ma cawh a hmuh tihtah a lungchung tah, “Ma cawngsaw heh Khazing khuavang a cang caco, a phe a hre leimeipaw heh ahomaw a cang, zehapaw canu maw a cang tahpaw heh a hni ruapaw a cang, mehsua no cang tlung ka,” tatah a pacang.
\p 
\v 40 Zisu taco, “Simon, bia ka ca ching dupaw a ung,” a tah.
\p Farasipaw Simon taco, “Cawngpahtu, pa ching tua,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 41 Zisu tah, “Cawngsaw pahning tah khalui hnui he ka, pakhehpaw tah ngung tangka 500, pakhehpaw tah ngung tangka songngaw tatah lui aa bah he.
\v 42 Aa pahning taco aa khalui cawh chang khy va vei lytah aa ung. Macawtaco tangka a hnuitupaw taco a ngethai va vei he. A cang caco, aaning pahning lekhei aho tamaw a do vy a, tatah na rawh?” a tah.
\p 
\v 43 Simon taco, “A hlu vy a ngethaipaw khah a cang thly a, tatah ka rawh,” tatah a chai.
\p Zisu tah, “Na rawhpaw a hmang ngetei,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 44 Mataico Zisu cawh cawngsawno lang cawh a hui ka, Simon hai leco, “Ma no heh na hmuh maw? Na ing chunglang ka za naening tah phe sinah ruapaw tui pa pei bei ceh. Canghrasala ma cawngsawno tahei co ka phe heh a mehthli tah si ka, a sang tah a hru.
\v 45 Nama taco pa hnang bei ceh, canghrasala ma no tahei co ka za naenah taikhei ka phe hnang khah tai be.
\v 46 Nama taco ka lu letah zong sathy pa thu bei ceh, canghrasala ma no tahei co ka phe letah ringthopaw a bia.
\v 47 Ma rawng tahei ka ca ching, a suanah a hlu ngeteipaw cawh ngethai a cang myca, macawtaco cawngsawno takhei a do ngetei. Canghrasala, a cawngtei ngethai a cangpaw taco a cawngtei tah a do hrah,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 48 Mataico Zisu tah cawngsawno cawh, “Na suanah cawh ngethai a cang thah,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 49 Aa hrong letei a ung hrahpaw khuachai sahlo taco, “Suanah hmai a ngethaipaw heh ahomaw a cang?” tatah aaning le aaning khah aa tah he.
\p 
\v 50 Zisu tah cawngsawno cawh, “Na zingnah tah a ca pachah thah, thlawlung teitah va sei my lo,” tatah a tah.
\c 8
\s1 Thleci a vapaw tawchingnah
\r (Mt 13:1-23; Mk 4:1-20)
\p 
\v 1 Ma khy taico Zisu cawh khuapui le khuatei tlawnglai longmang ka, Khazing painah raang kong thawngchawbia cawh a y khui lai. A hningzuitu pahrawhluihning khah Ama khatah a sei hrah he.
\v 2 Canu thaikheh, a sawnah taitah a dangsahpaw sahlo le thlawpaw pialuipaw a papia pahpaw he sahlo zong Ama khatah a ung he. Ma canu sahlo hrong leco thlawpaw pialuipaw sangsarih a papia pahpaw Mari (Makdalin aa tahpaw) le,
\v 3 Herod cho a mingkaitu Kuza a nupuino Joana le Susana le ahringpaw sahlo a cang he. Ma sahlo cawh aaning aa hnuicho teitah Zisu le a hningzuitu sahlo a bawkhangpaw a cang he.
\p 
\v 4 Khua keh ná tah mehnung hlupui Zisu khatah a vong he ka, a pahmo ning he takhei ma tawchingnah bia heh a ching he.
\v 5 “Ly a tuapaw pakheh cawh thleci va pawtah ly lang a sei. Thleci a va leimeining takhei a chy cawh lang kae letah tlah ka, cawngsaw tah aa phe tah ci he ka, pavaw sahlo tah aa khi thlu thah he.
\v 6 A chy cawh lungda letah tlah he ka, aa ka cy tihtah aa thahrang aa thlah nápaw alui a pacingpaw a ung lynah cawtah a ro kaw palang thah he.
\v 7 A chy cawh ahling hrong letah tlah he ka, ahling khaco cyhrui he ka, ahling taco a diseh thah he.
\v 8 A chy cawh alui chahnah letah tlah ka, ka cy ka, a thuisu tua ka, a vapaw navy tah a leh zakheh tah a hlu vy a chuh.”
\p Ma bia heh a thangpui tah rei ka, “Thuinah nawkho a hnuipaw taco ma bia heh thui he seh,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 9 A hningzuitu sahlo taco ma tawchingnah bia silang cawh aa hae hri.
\v 10 Zisu tah aa hai leco, “Khazing painah raang biaparuh hni khynah cawh peh na cang thah he ceh. Canghrasala, ming hringpaw hai leco tawchingnah bia tah ka rei. Macawtaco,
\q1 ‘Ming thlang he ka, hmuh a bei he,
\q2 thui thlang he ka, hnih thai a bei he.’\x + \xo 8:10 \xt Isai 6:9\x*
\p 
\v 11 Tawchingnah bia silang cawh ma heh a cang. Thleci cawh Khazing bia heh a cang.
\v 12 Langpui letei a tlahpaw sahlo cawh bia cawh thui he ka, Setan khah a vong ka, zing tah pachah aa cang ly nápawtah bia cawh aa lungchung taitah a lah pah he.
\v 13 Lungda cung letei a tlahpaw sahlo cawh Khazing bia cawh thui he ka, lunglawng teitah aa cyhlang. Canghrasala, thahrang hnui bei he. Aa zingnah cawh sungkheh tei cai caw longlong cang ka, ruhanah a chua tihtah a pohly palang he.
\v 14 Ahling hrong letei a tlahpaw thleci sahlo asilang cawh Khazing bia cawh thui he ka, canghrasala tungtuh khuasahnah lungreithuinah le rungnah le anawngnah tah diseh kaw thlu he katei, aa pui a tling thai lypaw cawngsaw sahlo khah a cang he.
\v 15 Canghrasala, alui a chahnah letei a tlahpaw sahlo cawh lung hmuisui teitah Khazing bia cawh thui he ka, a tle he ka, a thuisu a tuanah tai teria teitah aa zuipaw cawngsaw sahlo khah a cang he,” a tah.
\s1 Me-ing chianah tung leteipaw
\r (Mk 4:21-25)
\p 
\v 16 Zisu taco, “Ahotahmai tah me-ing a vang tihtah lakhing rai letah maw abai rai letah maw chia bang be. Ing chung lang a naepaw maikaw tah a khaipaw aa hmuh khy nápawtah me-ing tung letah aa chia tei.
\v 17 Palang ly rua pawtah nopaw hming zehmai ung be. Taico hni ly rua pawtah paphipaw zehmai ung be, palangsah thlu a cang a.
\v 18 Macawtaco naa nawthliapaw khah achaw teitah pacang my lo. A hnuipaw cawh peh vy cang a he ka, a hnui lypaw cawh a hnuitlakangpaw tatei a rawhpaw hmai khah lah pah a cang a,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Zisu no le a uny sahlo
\r (Mt 12:46-50; Mk 3:31-35)
\p 
\v 19 Taico, Zisu a no le a uny sahlo cawh Ama khah a tong rua pawtah a vong he. Canghrasala, cawngsaw aa hlutunah cawtah a va nae khy bei he.
\v 20 Cawngsaw pakheh tah Zisu cawh, “Na no le na uny sahlo tah a tong ca du he ka, khunglai letah a daw thlang he,” tatah a ching.
\p 
\v 21 Zisu taco, “Khazing bia thui ka, a zuipaw sahlo heh ka no le ka uny sahlo cawh a cang he,” tatah a palei.
\s1 Zisu tah thlichia a desah
\r (Mt 8:23-27; Mk 4:35-41)
\p 
\v 22 Ningkheh cawh Zisu tah a hningzuitu sahlo cawh, “Galili tuiping raechai lang sei he pei,” a tah he. Macawtaco tuilawng chunglang cawh a nae he ka, aa sei.
\v 23 Tuilawng tah aa seilai leimeining taco Zisu cawh a ihning. Tuiping leco thlichia a va hrang ka, aa lawng cawh tui lang a nong thlu daimangnah cawtah ciphang ngetei tah a ung he.
\p 
\v 24 A hningzuitu sahlo tah Ama cawh va patho he ka, “Hruitupaw, Hruitupaw, tui lang kaa tlah thlu he peh hi,” tatah aa tah.
\p Zisu cawh ka tho ka, thli le tuileh cawh a hrangso he ka, thli cawh de ka, tui cawh a cali he.
\v 25 “Naa zingnah cawh zeletamaw a ung thlu?” tatah a hningzuitu sahlo cawh a tah he.
\p Ci le ningang hmotah, “Ma heh zehapaw cawngsaw maw a cang? Thli le tuileh zong tah a bia aa nge thlangpaw heh,” tatah pakheh le pakheh a tah tlungmang he.
\s1 Khachia tei a tlepaw dangsahnah
\r (Mt 8:28-34; Mk 5:1-20)
\p 
\v 26 Galili tuiping raechai lang letei a ungpaw he Gerasin raang cawngsaw sahlo aa ungnah cawh aa va phah.
\v 27 Zisu cawh ngaekang lang a cungthlah cangkawleh ma khua letei a ungpaw khachia tei a tlepaw cawngsawpaw taco a va tong. Ma cawngsawpaw heh a thlekalong tei a ungpaw, ing letah zong a ung lypaw, thlaikung letah a ungteipaw a cang.
\v 28 Zisu a hmuh cangkawleh sang ka, a phehrang leco a bawh ka, a thangpui tah a y. “Cungnungcai Khazing Sawcapaw, Zisu, kama khatah zemaw na dupaw a ung? Pa hreh haitei kheh tatah ka ca naw,” a tah.
\v 29 A chung letei thlawpaw pialuipaw khah ka pia tatah Zisu tah bia a peh cawtah khei a cang. Ma paw cawh uihlupui khachia taco, a hraipakingnah cawtah a kih le a phe letah bahrairui tah khi he ka, aa vai. Bahrairui tah aa hrai naná teitah chehchung thlu ka, khachia taco lyraangpaw lang a tingchua tei.
\p 
\v 30 Zisu tah, “Na ming ahomaw?” tatah a hae.
\p “Ka ming cawh Thongzakheh a cang,” tatah a palei. Khachia a hlupui tah aa pahrangnah cawtah.
\v 31 Taico khachia sahlo taco, Zisu cawh a ping thai lypaw khobatlung lang ma thlah haitei kheh tatah aa naw canei leimei thlang.
\p 
\v 32 Aa kae tlangpa lekhei lawh a e leimeipaw voh rungpui ung he ka, khachia sahlo taco Zisu cawh ma voh rung sahlo aa chunglang kheh a ma naesah thlang, tatah naw he ka, Zisu tah a naesah he.
\v 33 Khachia sahlo cawh ma cawngsawpaw chung taico piathlah he ka, voh chunglang cawh a nae he. Voh rungpui sahlo cawh tuiping lang a zythlah he ka, a thi thlu he.
\p 
\v 34 Voh rungpui a mingkaitu sahlo taco ma hming vytei cawh aa hmuh tihtah sai tlamang he ka, khuapui chung le khuatei lekhei aa rei lai.
\v 35 Taico zawpui sahlo cawh piathlah he ka, zehratamaw a cang tahpaw khah ming rua pawtah a sei he. Zisu kung aa va tlung tihtah khachia sahlo tei, aa piasaipaw cawngsawpaw khah aa va hmuh. Lungsing teitah caise a tua katei, Zisu kae letah a za tythlangpaw khah aa hmuh. Macawtaco aa ci ngetei.
\v 36 A hmuhpaw cawngsaw sahlo taco, khachia sahlo tei aa tlepaw cawngsawpaw a dangnah kong khah cawngsaw hringpaw aa ching lai he.
\v 37 Mataico Gerasin raang letei a ungpaw cawngsaw vytei taco aa ci tunah cawtah Zisu khah aa raang taitah piathlah a pawtah aa naw. Macawtaco tuilawng chunglang cawh a nae ka, a sei.
\p 
\v 38 Khachia sahlo tei aa piasaipaw cawngsawpaw taco, “Nama khatah ka seilai hrá a,” tatah naw ka, canghrasala, Zisu taco kawsah kaw ka, a hai leco,
\v 39 “Ing lang a dih la, Khazing tah zetlua tamaw na cawtah hming a ca tuapah tahpaw khah va ching hri law,” a tah. Mataico cawngsawpaw cawh piathlah ka, Zisu tah zetlua tamaw a cawtah hming a tuapah tahpaw khah khua cawngsaw vytei cawh a ching he.
\s1 Canu nyheh a thipaw le mehdang ly macang no
\r (Mt 9:18-26; Mk 5:21-43)
\p 
\v 40 Zisu cawh a va kaw kaw tihtah cawngsaw hlupui tah dai he ka, aaning sahlo cawh a va tlungpaw a heh thlangpaw a cang he.
\v 41 Taico Jaira aa tahpaw synagog a uhtu cawh a vong. Zisu a phehrang leco a bawh ka, a ing lang a vong rua pawtah a naw.
\v 42 A sawcanu hnuitlakangpaw, kung hrawhluihning a tah no cawh a thih daimangnah cawtah a cang.
\p Zisu a seilai ning taco zawpui tah buh thlang he ka, aa nanghly pai lai leimei he.
\v 43 Ma leco canu pakheh kung hrawhluihning chung a thi a chuh no ung ka, a hnuicho vytei sibui letah pachang thlu thah ka, ahotahmai dangsah khy bei he.
\v 44 Zisu a hninglang tah a vong ka, a pai dong cawh tong ka, ma cangkaw leco, a thi cawh a kih.
\p 
\v 45 “Ahomaw a pa tong?” tatah Zisu tah hae he ka, aa dawngkasawny teitah ca tong bei peh aa tah.
\p Piter taco, “Hruitupaw, zawpui tah ca buh thlang he ka, aa ca nangpaipaw a cang,” a tah.
\p 
\v 46 Canghrasala, Zisu tah, “Pakheh kheh tah a pa tong, ka chung taitah hmingtuakhynah a pia, ma rawng taco ka hni,” a tah.
\p 
\v 47 Mataico canuno taco Zisu tah a pa hni myca tahpaw a hni tihtah a thlawzawng ka, a phehrang leco a bawh ka, zawpui hme leco a cangnah silang le sung sungkheh tah a dangnah kong khah a ching.
\v 48 Mataico Zisu tah a hai leco, “Ka sawcanu, na zingnah tah a ca dangsah, de teitah va seí my lo,” a tah.
\p 
\v 49 Zisu tah bia a rei leimei ning taco, synagog a uhtu Jaira ing taico cawngsaw pakheh a vong ka, “Na sawcanu cawh a thi thah, cawngpahtu heh hnahnawh du khawh kheh,” a tah.
\p 
\v 50 Ma bia cawh Zisu tah thui ka, Jaira hai letaco, “Na thlawzawng kheh seh, zing la, na sawcanu cawh a dang a,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 51 Jaira ing cawh a va phah tihtah Piter le Johan le Jeims le nyno a no le a paw tah cy ly co ahohmai ing chunglang a naesah bei he.
\v 52 Ma chung vytei cawh cawngsaw hringpaw taco nyno cawh ngechia tah aa cawkhui leimei. Zisu tah, “Cah tua khe o, nyno heh a thih tlung be, a ihning hi!” tatah a tah he.
\p 
\v 53 A thi tahpaw aa hni thlangnah cawtah khei Zisu cawh aa hnuiso.
\v 54 Canghrasala, Zisu tah nyno cawh a kiá tah tle ka, “Ka sawcanu, tho law,” a tah.
\v 55 A thlawpaw cawh va kaw kaw ka, ma cangkaw leco, nyno cawh a ka dawchua. Taico Zisu tah aaning sahlo cawh nyno heh e ruapaw sangkheh kheh pei my lo, tatah a ching he.
\v 56 A no le a paw cawh aa khuarawha thlang ka, canghrasala, Zisu tah aaning cawh hming ungzia khah ahohmai ching khe lo, tatah a tah he.
\c 9
\s1 Zisu tah apostol pahrawhluihning a taw he
\r (Mt 10:5-15; Mk 6:7-13)
\p 
\v 1 Zisu tah apostol hluihning cawh Ama khatah a y he. Khachia vytei papia lai pawtah le asawnah vytei zong dangsah lai pawtah nawhnuinah le hmingtuakhynah pei he ka,
\v 2 aaning cawh Khazing painah raang kong reilai rua pawtah le a dang lypaw sahlo zong dangsah lai rua pawtah a taw he.
\v 3 Aa hai leco, “Khua tlawngnah caw pawtah cungcahrei, sahre, chingco, tangka le cai le se a hluipaw zehmai a cakai khe o.
\v 4 Naa naenah pawhe ceh ing leco ma khua taitei naa seithlah kaw hlai vytei cawh ung thlang my lo.
\v 5 Ma khua cawngsaw taco aa ca cyhlang du ly caco he aaning sahlo raering pehnah tah ma khua taico naa piathlah tihtah naa phe letei luipadih khah cathingthlah si my lo,” a tah he.
\v 6 Taico aaning sahlo cawh piathlah he ka, khua kheh hning khua khé co sei lai he ka, aa seilainah maikaw leco, thawngchawbia rei lai he ka, a dang lypaw sahlo zong aa dangsah lai he.
\p 
\v 7 Abui Herod taco hming ungzia vytei cawh a thui tihtah a lung hna a hnawh ngetei. Zecawtamaw tatah baptisma peitu Johan khah thihnah taitah a tho kaw tatah mehthaikheh tah aa tah.
\v 8 Thaikhehpaw sahlo taco Elija a paly tatah aa tah. Mehthaikheh huipaw taco khuahlaining tei Khazing khuavang letei pakhehkheh khah a hring kaw aa tah.
\v 9 Canghrasala Herod taco, “Johan cawh a lu ka tai thah tlung, ma hratei a kong ka thuipaw heh ahomaw a cang!” a tah. Ma cawngsaw cawh hmuh a pachia.
\s1 Zisu tah mehnung 5000 lawh a dang he
\r (Mt 14:13-21; Mk 6:30-44; Jh 6:1-14)
\p 
\v 10 Apostol sahlo cawh aa va tlung kaw tihtah aa tuapaw hming kong khah Zisu cawh aa ching. Taico aaning sahlo cawh a chui he ka, Bethsaida aa tahpaw khua lang cawh aaning teitah aa sei.
\v 11 Canghrasala zawpui taco ma cawh hnih he ka, Ama cawh aa zuilai. Zisu tah zawpui vytei cawh achaw teitah mingkai he ka, Khazing painah raang kong khah ching he ka, dangnah a hiapaw sahlo khah a dangsah he.
\p 
\v 12 Zailang ning a tlah cai letah apostol hluihning cawh Ama khatah a vong he ka, “Ma lehei ung nápaw le e ruapaw zong ung be. Macawtaco zawpui vytei heh na disah pawhe a cang. Kaa kaekang khua le ly sahlo lehei ungnah le e ruapaw a va hui he seh, zecawtamaw tatah kaa ungnah heh raang kingdang cang tlung ka,” aa tah.
\p 
\v 13 Zisu taco, “Naaning tah e ruapaw cawh pei o,” a tah he.
\p Aaning taco, “Ma vytei cawngsaw e ruapaw tahei kaa va cawh seh tah lypaw co, kaaning khaco very tlangpangaw le ngaw sanghning long kaa hnui!” aa tah.
\v 14 Capaw puitling longtei tah 5000 hrawng a tah he.
\p Canghrasala Zisu tah a hningzuitu sahlo cawh, “Zawpui khah songngaw phu longmang tah a tysah o,” a tah he.
\v 15 A reipaw hratah hningzuitu sahlo taco tua he ka, ming vytei cawh a ty he.
\v 16 Very tlangpangaw le ngaw sanghning cawh law ka, avai lang a y ka, Khazing khatah lawngbia hlai ka, very tlang sahlo cawh a kychy. Mataico a hningzuitu sahlo cawh zawpui cawh rai pawtah a peh he.
\v 17 Aa zongmingtei co e he ka, aa ri a vaw thlu. Taico a hningzuitu sahlo taco aa ebangpaw cawh pakhong he ka, baihraw hluihning chih ky tah aa dui.
\s1 Piter tah Khri na cang a tah
\r (Mt 16:13-28; Mk 8:27—9:1)
\p 
\v 18 Uikheh cawh Zisu cawh Ama teitah thlaw a chang leimeining takhei a hningzuitu sahlo cawh Ama khatah a ung thlang he. Zisu tah a hningzuitu sahlo cawh, “Zawpuipaw tah aho aa pa tah maw?” tatah a hae he.
\p 
\v 19 Aaning sahlo taco, “Thaikhehpaw tah baptisma peitu Johan aa ca tah, thaikhehpaw tah Elija a cang ca tah he ka, ahringpaw taco khuahlai tei Khazing khuavang sahlo letah pakheh kheh khah a va hring kaw aa ca tah,” tatah aa palei.
\p 
\v 20 Zisu tah, “Naaning tah saw aho a cang naa pa tah maw?” tatah hae he ka, Piter tah, “Nama cawh Khazing taitei a vongpaw Khri na cang,” tatah a chai.
\p 
\v 21 Zisu tah aaning sahlo cawh ma kong heh ahohmai ching ly rua pawtah araeringnah a peh he.
\v 22 Taico Zisu tah, “Cawngsaw Sawcapaw heh taithuinah a hlupui ing ka, macang sahlo le tlangbui macang sahlo le phungbia cawngpahtu sahlo tah hlawh a he ka, aa thaw a. Canghrasala, a ningthungnah letah hringnah letah thosah kaw a cang a,” tatah a tah he.
\p 
\v 23 Mataico aa zongmingtei hai leco, “Ahohmai zui a pa dupaw cawh ama a dunah khah seisai seh la, a khraws cawh ning tating tah a puh seh la, pazui seh.
\v 24 A hringnah pachah a dupaw taco sung a ka, canghrasala Kama ka cawtah a hringnah a sungpaw taco a hringnah a pachah a.
\v 25 Cawngsaw pakheh tah khazaw heh a pungpaluh tah hnui seh la, a hringnah a hly caco a cawtah zemaw a chahnai a?
\v 26 Ahohmai Kama le ka cawngpahnah bia a zawkhuipaw maikaw cawh Cawngsaw Sawcapaw heh vaicung letei vaiming pathai sahlo khatah a rungnawnah le Paw rungnawnah kha a za cung tihtah ma cawngsaw cawh a zawkhui hrá a.
\v 27 Biahmuisui ka ca ching he, ma lehei a daw thlangpaw sahlo hrong lehei mehthaikheh cawh Khazing painah raang aa hmuh hlai taco thi balang bei he,” a tah.
\s1 A mehme a thlainah
\r (Mt 17:1-8; Mk 9:2-8)
\p 
\v 28 Zisu tah ma bia a rei khy taitah ningreh hrawng lekhei Piter, Johan le Jeims cawh Ama kha a chui he ka, thlawchang rua pawtah tlaang cung lang a kekhui he.
\v 29 Thlaw a chang leimeining tah a mehme pho zia cawh a thlai ka, a caise sahlo cawh lailaw a ky ning tei, akhaipaw tluá khei a khai.
\v 30 Cawngsaw pahning Moses le Elija cawh,
\v 31 vaicung rungnawnah khatah a za lang he ka, Zisu khatah bia aa rei. Jerusalem khuapui letah a thihnah thongtah Khazing a tingaipaw a patling nápaw kong khah aa rei.
\v 32 Piter le a vesaw sahlo cawh a ihning he ka, canghrasala a ka hraw tih he tah a rungnawnah le cawngsaw pahning Ama khatah a daw thlangpaw he khah aa hmuh.
\v 33 Cawngsaw tlaw tah Zisu cawh aa seisai leimeining tah Piter taco a hai letah, “Hruitupaw, ma lehei ung heh kaa cawtah a chah ngetei. Thlangda nama na cawtah sangkheh, Moses a cawtah sangkheh, Elija a cawtah sangkheh tatah sangthung sah a he peh,” a tah. (Piter cawh zemaw ka rei tahpaw hmai hnih be.)
\p 
\v 34 A rei leimeining taco meding va thang ka, aaning cawh pahlong he ka, meding chung letah aa ungnah cawtah aa ci ngetei.
\v 35 Meding chung taico o va ring ka, “Ma heh ka Sawtei, ka thingpaw cawh a cang. Ama a bia cawh nge my lo,” tatah o a za ring.
\v 36 O tah ma hratei a rei khy taico Zisu cawh Ama longtei a cangpaw khah aa hmuh. A hningzuitu sahlo tah ma cawh aa chung letah a cingkai thlang he ka, aa hmuhpaw kong khah ma ning taco ahohmai ching bei he.
\s1 Thlawpaw pialuipaw tei a tlepaw nyhehpaw dangsahnah
\r (Mt 17:14-18, 22-23; Mk 9:14-27, 30-32)
\p 
\v 37 A ningthlamongpaw tlaang cung taitah aa za cung chuh ning takhei cawngsaw rungpui taco Zisu cawh a va tong he.
\v 38 Zawpui chung taico pakhehpaw cawh ka ychua ka, “Cawngpahtu, ka sawtei pa mingpah tua tatah ka ca naw, Ama heh ka sawtei hnuitlakangpaw a cang.
\v 39 Thlawpaw pialuipaw tah tua ka, sung sungkheh tah sangsah ka, hruipakingsah ka, a ci tatabu zong a pia thlu tei. Cai cuitei suipaw piasai ka, a hlyde daimang tei.
\v 40 Ma cawh papia rua pawtah na hningzuitu sahlo naw he neh ka, canghrasala papia khy bei he,” a tah.
\p 
\v 41 Zisu taco, “Vy zingnah a hnui lypaw le meh paleh meh pathae sahlo, zetih tai maw naaning khatah ka ung a? Zetih tai maw ka lung ka ca pasua pá he a? Na sawtei cawh ma lehei a vong khui tua,” tatah a palei.
\p 
\v 42 Nyhehpaw cawh a va sei leimeining takhei hmai khachia taco alui letah paliahly ka, a hruipakingsah. Canghrasala Zisu tah thlawpaw pialuipaw cawh a hrangso ka, nyhehpaw cawh dangsah ka, a paw khakhei a peh kaw.
\v 43 Taico aaning vytei cawh Khazing a rungnaw zia khah aa khuarawh a haa.
\p Ming vytei cawh Zisu a tuapaw hming kong letah khuarawha tah aa ung thlang ning taco Zisu tah a hningzuitu sahlo cawh,
\v 44 “Naaning ka ca ching lepaw he bia heh achaw teitah nawthlia tua o. Cawngsaw Sawcapaw heh cawngsaw sahlo kih letah luithae a cang myca a,” a tah he.
\v 45 Canghrasala, a hningzuitu sahlo taco a rei dupaw khah hnih thai bei he. A silang khah nokhai aa cangnah cawtah khei tle khy be ca he ka, hae hri ngang bei he.
\s1 Ahomaw alaicai a?
\r (Mt 18:1-5; Mk 9:33-40)
\p 
\v 46 A hningzuitu sahlo cawh aa hrong letah ahomaw alai caipaw a cang a tahpaw bia khah a ei hrang aa patho.
\v 47 Aa rawhnah cawh Zisu tah hnih ka, nyhehpaw tei khah law ka, a kae letah a dawsah.
\v 48 Mataico aa hai letah, “Ahohmai Kama ka ming tah ma hapaw nyhehtei heh a cyhlangpaw cawh Kama a pa cyhlangpaw cang ka, Kama a pa cyhlangpaw cawh a pa tawtupaw a cyhlangpaw a cang. Naa hrong letei a chia caipaw heh alaicaipaw cawh a cang a,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 49 Johan taco, “Hruitupaw, cawngsaw pakheh tah na ming tah khachia a papia leimeipaw hmuh he peh ka, kaa bu cawngsaw a cang lynah cawtah kaa thly,” a tah.
\p 
\v 50 Zisu tah, “Thly khe o, a ma cakhae lypaw maikaw cawh naa cawngsaw a cang he,” a tah.
\s1 Samaria khua cawngsaw tah Zisu aa daichua
\p 
\v 51 Vaicung lang lahchy a cang nápaw cai khah a nenah cawtah khei, Zisu cawh Jerusalem lang sei pawtah a pachia.
\v 52 Mataico zuaky sahlo khah hmelang a seisah hlang he. Aaning cawh a cawtah hming pachiapaning hlang rua pawtah Samaria cawngsaw aa khua lang khah a nae he.
\v 53 Canghrasala Zisu cawh Jerusalem lang sei a tingnah cawtah khei ma khua letei cawngsaw sahlo taco pasungpanaw bei he.
\v 54 Ma cawh a hningzuitu Johan le Jeims tah aa hmuh tihtah a hai letah, “Abuipaw aaning sahlo a kangseh ruapaw he tahei avai taitah me za tlahsah peh seh la, tahpaw na ma dukhui maw?” tatah aa tah.
\v 55 Canghrasala Zisu cawh a hui ka, aaning sahlo cawh a raw he.
\v 56 Taico aaning sahlo cawh khua hring lang aa sei.
\s1 Zisu zuilainah a mai
\r (Mt 8:19-22)
\p 
\v 57 Langpui letah aa seilai leimeining taco cawngsaw pakheh tah, “Na seinah maikaw lang ka ca zui a,” a tah.
\p 
\v 58 Zisu tah, “Sihatei sahlo tah kua hnui he ka, pavaw sahlo zong tah bu aa hnui. Canghrasala Cawngsaw Sawcapaw cawh a lu pahnia nápaw hminghmaw hmai hnui be,” tatah a palei.
\p 
\v 59 Cawngsaw hringpaw pakheh cawh, “Va pa zui law,” a tah.
\p Canghrasala ma cawngsaw taco, “Abuipaw, va seí neh ka, ka paw ka va phung taw a,” tatah a palei.
\p 
\v 60 Zisu tah a hai letah, “A thipaw cawh mehthi tah phung thlang he seh, nama duitei cawh sei la, Khazing painah raang thawngchawbia va rei my lo,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 61 Cawngsaw pakheh a vong vy hui ka, “Abuipaw, na seinah maikaw letah ka ca zui a. Canghrasala, kaw kaw taw neh ka, ka sawny aa kih ka tlesi taw he a,” a tah.
\p 
\v 62 Zisu tah, “Ahohmai alui paleh patho tlung katei, a hninglang a hui kaw leimeipaw cawh Khazing painah raang letah rai a hre tlangpaw cang bei he,” tatah a palei.
\c 10
\s1 Zisu tah a hningzuitu songsarih le pahning a taw he
\p 
\v 1 Ma khy taico Abuipaw tah a hningzuitu ahringpaw songsarih le pahning khah thing he ka, pahning longmang tah Ama a sei nápaw khua maikaw le hminghmaw maikaw lang khah hmelang a thlaw hlang he.
\v 2 Aa hai leco, “Saze hre ruapaw hlu ngetei ka, canghrasala a hretu cawh a cawngtei he. Macawtaco saze lui a hnuitu Abuipaw cawh raihretu sahlo khah saze lui lang taw rua pawtah hae my lo.
\v 3 Sei tua o, naaning sahlo cawh chahnia hrong letei tuu teitei sahlo hratah ka ca taw he.
\v 4 Tangkabawng cang seh, sahre cang seh, phepakong cang seh a cakai khe la, lang letah ahohmai aa kih tle khe lo.
\p 
\v 5 Ing na nae tih he ceh tah ahmasaw cai tah, ‘Ma ing lehei denah ung ky seh,’ tah my lo.
\v 6 Ma cawngsaw cawh denah sawtei a cang caco, naa reipaw denah cawh a cung letah a tlung a, ma hratei a cang ly caco naaning naa cung lang a va kaw kaw a.
\v 7 Ma ing leco ung la, aa ca pehpaw he maikaw khah e la, ding thlang my lo. Raihretu cawh a raihrenah mai hmuh rua tah a tlah. Ingkheh hning ingkheh a palong lai khe lo.
\p 
\v 8 Khuachung lang a nae he ceh ka, ingtlung aa ca pa-awng tih he tah aa ca pehpaw he maikaw khah e thlang my lo.
\v 9 A dang lypaw sahlo khah dang sá la, Khazing painah raang tah a ca ne my ca he, tatah ching my lo.
\v 10 Canghrasala, khuachung a nae he ceh ka, ingtlung aa ca pa-awng ly caco he, langlaipui sahlo lekhei sei la, ma hrahei tah my lo,
\v 11 ‘Naa khua luipadih kaa phe letei a kapaw hmai kaa cathingthlah hi, ma duitei cawh ma heh hnih my lo. Khazing painah raang cawh a ne myca,’ tatah tah my lo.
\v 12 Ma heh ka ca ching he, biacenah ning taco ma khua navy co Sodom khua tai-ingnah hmai khah a zia a ung vy a.
\p 
\v 13 Vy Korazin khua na cing a ping! Vy Bethsaida khua na cing a ping! Naaning letei tuapaw ningang chuipaw hming khah Tair le Sidon khua letah tuapaw cang he seh la, buri pai a buh a tah mecang letah a ty a he ka, a ngepachih syly tha he a.
\v 14 Canghrasala, biacenah ning leco Tair le Sidon khua tei aa ingpaw cawh naaning navy tah a zia a ung vy tae a.
\v 15 Taico, nama Kapernaum khua, avai tai kheh calia na cang maw? Cang bei ceh. Hraihming lang na tlahthlah a.
\p 
\v 16 Naa rei a ca ngepaw maikaw he cawh kama ka rei a pa ngepaw a cang he. Naaning a ca hlawhpaw maikaw he cawh kama a pa hlawh paw a cang he. Canghrasala kama a pa hlawhpaw maikaw he cawh a pa tawtu a hlawhpaw a cang he,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 17 Songsarih le pahning tlaw he khah lunglawng teitah va tlung kaw he ka, “Abuipaw, khachia vanghru sahlo zong tahmai na ming tah kaa rei aa ma nge,” tatah aa ching.
\p 
\v 18 Zisu tah, “Setan khah lailaw hratah vaicung taitei a za tlahthlahpaw ka hmuh.
\v 19 Pari sahlo le tlangcekawng sahlo zong tlaipabainah naw le naa caraepaw te khynah naw ca pei he neh ka, zetahmai a ca sawsah khy bei he.
\v 20 Ma duitei cawh thlawpaw pialuipaw zong tah naa rei aa ca nge caw he tah a lawng khe o. Canghrasala vaicung letah naa ming cia a cangnah cawtah a lawng hri my lo,” tatah a palei he.
\p 
\v 21 Ma ningcai leco Zisu cawh Thlawpaw Pathai thongtah a lawng ngetei ka, “Ka Paw, alui le avai Buipaw, ka ca reithai, mehthai mehsing sahlo caw taco, ma hming sahlo heh nawh ceh ka, nyheh hapaw sahlo khatah na palang. A cang, ka Paw, ma cawh nama na lawngnah cawh a cang,” a tah.
\p 
\v 22 Zisu cawh ma hratei thlaw a chang khy taico zawpui sahlo lang cawh ma hrahei bia rei ka, “Hming vytei heh ka Paw tah a pa peh thlu thah he. Paw tah ly co Sawcapaw heh ahomaw a cang tahpaw ahotahmai hnih bei he. Taico, Sawcapaw le Sawcapaw tei hnisah rua pawtah a thingpaw he tah ly co Paw cawh ahomaw a cang tahpaw ahotahmai hnih bei he,” a tah.
\p 
\v 23 Mataico, a hningzuitu sahlo lang khah a hui ka, aaning ei teitah ching he ka, “Naa hmuhpaw hming a hmuhpaw mehkho sahlo cawh bonghnang aa ting.
\v 24 Biahmuisui ka ca ching he, Khazing khuavang le abui sahlo mehlupui tah naa hmuhpaw heh hmuh aa du ngetei cy hrah naná teitah hmuh bei he. Naa thuipaw heh thui aa du ngetei hrah naná teitah za thui bei he,” tatah a tah he.
\s1 Samaria mehchawpaw tawchingnah
\p 
\v 25 Uikheh cawh phungbia a thai ngeteipaw pakheh cawh Zisu pase du tah a daw ka, “Cawngpahtu, chaizaw hringnah ka hmuh khy nápawtah zemaw ka tua a?” tatah a hae.
\p 
\v 26 Zisu tah, “Khazing phungbia letah zemaw a cia? Zekhatamaw na hni?” tatah a hae hri kaw.
\p 
\v 27 Phungbia a thai ngeteipaw taco, “ ‘Abuipaw na Khazing khah na lungthing vytei, na hringnah vytei, na thawzaang vytei le na khuarawnah vytei tah do my lo.’\x + \xo 10:27 \xt Biary 6:5\x* Mataico, ‘Nama na dopaw hratah na ingpaw khah do my lo,’\x + \xo 10:27 \xt Tlangbui 19:18\x* tahpaw he a cang,” tatah a chai.
\p 
\v 28 Zisu tah, “Na pachaipaw ahmang ngetei, ma hraco va tua la, na hring a,” a tah.
\p 
\v 29 Canghrasala, ama teitah thai a cangsah khah a dunah cawtah, “Ka ingpaw cawh ahomaw a cang?” tatah a hae kaw.
\p 
\v 30 Zisu tah palei ka, “Cawngsaw pakheh Jerusalem khua taitah Jeriko khua lang a seithlah. Ma langpui leco damia sahlo tah hrawh he ka, a caise vytei pahlu pah thlu he ka, thi daimang tah aa dai khy taitah aa seisai.
\v 31 Tlangbui pakheh cawh ma lang a za sei hrah ning khatah a tong ka, damia sahlo tah aa daipaw cawngsaw khah a hmuh tihtah khungsai ka, lang kang rakheh lang tah a cahri.
\v 32 Ma paw hraco Levi mingphing pakhehpaw tah ma hminghmaw cawh va phah hrah ka, a hmuh tihtah khungsai ka, langkae lang co a cahri sai thlang hrah.
\v 33 Canghrasala, Samaria cawngsawpaw pakheh cawh khua tlawng hrah ka, damia sahlo tei aa daipaw cawngsawpaw ungnah khah va phah hrah ka, a hmuh cangkawleh ning a do ngetei.\f + \fr 10:33 \ft Juda cawngsaw le Samaria cawngsaw cawh a chethai bei he.\f*
\v 34 A vawhno ka, a hmaw vytei khah sathy le misurhang thupah ka, a tongchai pah khy taitah ama a kelaipaw, la cung lang cawh khing ka, khuabuh lang seikhui ka, ma leco a mingkai.
\v 35 A ningthlamongpaw leco, ngung tangka phaehning cawh chua ka, khuabuh a hnuitupaw cawh pei ka, ‘Ma cawngsaw heh achaw teitah mingkai la, ka va kaw kaw tihtah a hluipaw tei na changpaw maikaw cawh ka ca chang kaw thlu tae a,’ a tah.
\p 
\v 36 Ma tlaw pathung hrong lehei ahomaw damia sahlo tei aa hrawhpaw cawngsaw a ingpaw cawh a cang tatah na rawh?” tatah a hae.
\p 
\v 37 Phungbia a thaipaw taco, “A cung letei ningdonah a hnuipaw khah a cang a, tah ka rawh,” tatah a chai.
\p Zisu tah, “Sei la, ma hraco va tua hrah,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Mari le Martha ing letah
\p 
\v 38 Zisu le a hningzuitu sahlo khah khua aa tlawnglai ning tah khua khuakheh va phah he ka, ma leco canuno pakheh Martha aa tahpaw tah a ing letah a tlungsah he.
\v 39 Martha cawh Mari aa tahpaw chuahruino pakheh a hnui. Ama cawh Abuipaw phehrang letah a ty ka, a bia reipaw khah a nawthlia.
\v 40 Canghrasala, Martha cawh raihrepaw ahlunah cawtah a rai a hnawh ngetei. Zisu khatah a vong ka, “Abuipaw, ka nyteino tei rai kama longtei a pa váso thlangpaw heh a pui tah bei ceh maw? Kama baw rua pawtah pa chingpah law,” a tah.
\p 
\v 41 Abuipaw taco, “Martha, Martha, hming hlupui cawtah lung reithui tah na ung,
\v 42 canghrasala hming sangkheh suipaw a hia. Mari tah achaw vypaw a thingpaw heh ama taitah lah pápaw cang be,” a tah.
\c 11
\s1 Thlawchangnah kong Zisu cawngpahnah
\r (Mt 6:9-13; 7:7-11)
\p 
\v 1 Ningkheh cawh Zisu cawh hminghmaw sangkheh letah thlaw a chang leimei. Thlaw a chang khy taico a hningzuitu pakheh tah a hai letah, “Abuipaw, Johan tah a hningzuitu sahlo a cawngpah pawhe hrakhei thlawchang ma cawngpah hrah,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 2 Zisu tah, “Thlaw naa chang tihtah ma hrahei chang my lo.
\q1 ‘Vy kaa Paw, na ming cawh cizaw tah ung seh.
\q1 Na painah tlung ky seh.
\q1 
\v 3 Ning ting kaa hiapaw batui ma pei my lo.
\q1 
\v 4 Kaa cung letei suanah a tuapaw kaa ngethai pawhe hrakhei
\q2 kaa suanah ma ngethai hrah my lo.
\q1 Tuhsonah lang a ma chui kheh lo,’ ”
\m tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 5 Taico Zisu tah ma hrahei a tah he, “A bianapaw tah naa hrong letah pakheh cawh vesaw pakheh hnui ka, ama khaco zaicing tah a vaw ka, ‘Ka dua, very tlangthung tah pa cui theh,
\v 6 zecawtamaw tatah khua a tlawngpaw ka vesawpaw va tlung ka, zehmai peh ruapaw hnui bei neh,’ tatah a va tah.
\p 
\v 7 Taico ing chung letei a ungpaw taco, ‘Hna pa hnawh tua kheh, ingkaw zong ka hrai thlu thah, ka sawtei leh zong kama khatah a ih thlu myca he, tho tah zehmai ca pei khy bei neh,’ tatah a chai.
\v 8 Ka ca ching he a, vesaw chaw a cangnah cawtah tho lytah le very khah peh lytah ung hmai seh la, a hae lawnglia caco tho ka, a dunah zé tah a peh thlang a.
\p 
\v 9 Macawtaco ka ca ching he a, hae la, peh na cang a he ceh, hui la, naa hmuh a, khong la, ingkaw hong pah na cang a he ceh.
\v 10 Ahohmai a haepaw cawh peh a cang he a, a huipaw taco hmuh a ka, ingkaw a khawngpaw cawh hongpah a cang a.
\p 
\v 11 Naaning paw a cangpaw sahlo, naa sawtei leh tah ngaw ca hae my he seh la, pari naa pae he maw?
\v 12 Aatui ca hae he seh la, tlangcekawng naa pae he maw?
\v 13 Naaning mehchahly tahmai naa sawtei leh hmingchaw peh zia naa hni caco, vaicung letei naa Paw taco Thlawpaw Pathai a haepaw sahlo khah ze tlua tamaw a peh vy chichi he a!” a tah he.
\s1 Zisu le Belzabub
\r (Mt 12:22-30, 43-45; Mk 3:20-27)
\p 
\v 14 Zisu tah a rei a thlaw thai lypaw chung taikhei khachia khah a tingchua. Khachia a piathlah tihtah a rei a thlaw thai lypaw cawngsaw cawh a rei ka thlaw ka, mingzawpui khah aa ning a ang thlang.
\v 15 Canghrasala aaning chung taitah thaikhehpaw taco, “Khachia sahlo buipaw Belzabub thongtah khachia sahlo a papia khy he,” tatah aa tah.
\v 16 Ahringpaw sahlo taco, Ama khah pase du tah vaicung lang tei ningang chuipaw paching pakhanah ma tuapah law, tatah aa tah.
\p 
\v 17 Zisu tah aa rawhnah khah hnih ka, aa hai letah, “Ze painah raang hmai, aaning le aaning aa dy caco he a rawh thlu he a. Taico ingchungkho khokheh zong a rai ly tei a chaichy caco he a rawh hrá he a.
\v 18 Setan zong ama le ama a dy caco, zekhatamaw a painah raang cawh a daw khy a? Ma bia heh Belzabub thongtah khachia sahlo a papia he naa tah cawtah ka reipaw a cang hi.
\v 19 Atoheh kama tah Belzabub thongtah khachia khah ka papia pawtei a cang caco, naaning a ca zuipaw sahlo he takhei saw aho thong tamaw aa papia? Macawtaco aaning cawh naaning bia a ca cepahtu a cang he a.
\v 20 Canghrasala, khachia sahlo khah Khazing hmingtuakhynah thongtah ka papia pawtei he a cang caco, Khazing painah raang cawh naaning khatah a tlung thah tahnah a cang.
\p 
\v 21 Mehthawtlung pakheh tah hrainang a hlupui khatah a ing khah a vai thlang chung taco a hnuichia vytei a bing.
\v 22 Canghrasala ama navy tah a thawtlung vypaw tah dy katei, a pahneh tih taco, a paichaipaw hrainang vytei khah lah pah ka, a hringpaw a lahpaw hming vytei khah a rai thlu he.
\p 
\v 23 Ahohmai kama lang a bai lypaw cawh a pa caraepaw a cang, kama a pa pahmo khui lypaw cawh a papaipaw a cang.
\p 
\v 24 Thlawpaw pialuipaw cawh cawngsawpaw chung taitah a ka piathlah tihtah raangcaa raangro lekhei a hianah hminghmaw hui tah a khiakaly ka, hmuh be. Mataico, ‘Ka piasaipaw ing lang khah ka pange kaw thlang a,’ tatah a tah.
\v 25 Ing cawh a va phah tihtah longkarong tah ung ka, pathai pahling teitah chiapaw a cangpaw khah a hmuh.
\v 26 Taico sei ka, ama navy tah a sua vypaw he ahringpaw thlawpaw pialuipaw pasarih a va chui he ka, ma ing cawh aa pahrang. Taico ma cawngsawpaw cawh athoning tei navy khei, a hning tei a dawhming cawh a pazua vy syly,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 27 Zisu tah ma hming vytei heh a rei leimeining taco, zawpui hrong taikhei canu pakheh cawh ka y chua ka, “Nama a ca sahtu le hnabae tui tei a ca cawngtu cawh bonghnang a ting caimang,” a tah.
\p 
\v 28 Zisu taco, “Canghrasala, Khazing bia khah thui tei, a bia a zuipaw he cawh bonghnang aa ting vypaw a cang he,” tatah a chai.
\s1 Jonah paching pakhanah
\r (Mt 12:38-42; Mk 8:12)
\p 
\v 29 Cawngsaw rungpui aa va hlu vy leimeining takhei Zisu taco, “Atochai cawngsaw heh a chah ly caimang he. Ningang chuipaw paching pakhanah aa hae, canghrasala Khazing khuavang Jonah paching pakhanah khah tah cy ly co zehmai peh cang a bei he.
\v 30 Nineve khua cawngsaw cawtah Jonah cawh paching pakhanah a cangpaw hrakhei Cawngsaw Sawcapaw zong heh atochai cawngsaw cawtah paching pakhanah a cang hrah.
\v 31 Biacenah ning leco thuilang Abuino Shiba cawh a daw a ka, ato chai cawngsaw sahlo heh thaily a cang sá he a. Zecawtamaw tatah ama cawh Solomon a singnah bia nge rua pawtah alui a changnah taitah va sei ka, canghrasala atoheh Solomon navy tah a lai vypaw ma lehei a ung thlang.
\v 32 Biacenah ning leco Nineve khua cawngsaw sahlo cawh atochai cawngsaw khahei a daw hrui he ka, sua aa phosah tae he a, zecawtamaw tatah ma tlaw taco Jonah a bia reipaw rawng tah angepachihnah aa hnui, taico atoheh ma lehei Jonah navy tah a rungnaw vypaw a ung thlang.
\s1 Pungsaw me-ing
\r (Mt 5:15; 6:22-23)
\p 
\v 33 Ahotahmai me-ing aa vang tihtah a langlynah hminghmaw letah maw, tongbai rai letah maw chia bang bei he. Ing chunglang a naepaw tah a khaipaw aa hmuh khy nápawtah me-ing tung letah me-ing khah a chia tei.
\v 34 Na meh heh na pung cawtah me-ing a cang. Na meh a chah caco, na pungpaluh zong khah khainá tah a chih. Canghrasala na meh a chah ly caco, na pung zong muiná tah a chih.
\v 35 A raering my lo, naa chung letei a ungpaw khainah cawh muinah cang be kho.
\v 36 Macawtaco na pungpaluh cawh khai ná tah a chi tei, na pungsaw a zehapaw letah hmai muinah a ung ly caco, me-ing a khainah tei a ca khaisopaw hrakhei na pung cawh a khai a,” a tah.
\s1 Cingpingnah sangruh
\r (Mt 23:1-36; Mk 12:38-40; Luk 20:45-47)
\p 
\v 37 Bia a rei khy taico Zisu cawh Farasi pakheh tah batui e hrui pawtah a hrui. Macawtaco va sei ka, a ty ka, cabuai khah a hia thlang.
\v 38 Canghrasala, Zisu cawh Farasi phung a cangpaw e hlai tah kih si khah tua be ca ka, Farasipaw tah a kih a si lypaw khah a hmuh tihtah a khuarawh a haa.
\p 
\v 39 Mataico Abuipaw tah a hai leco, “Naaning Farasi cawngsaw taco ny le pakang sahlo alailang khah pathaisah he ceh ka, canghrasala, naa chunglang cawh chahlynah le dusawnah long teitah a chih.
\v 40 Naaning mehruh sahlo, alailang a tuatu Khazing takhei a chunglang zong tua hrah bei maw?
\v 41 Canghrasala naa pakang le naa ny chung letei a ungpaw khah mehsisah va pei la, naa cawtah zezongpui a pathai thlang a.
\p 
\v 42 Naaning Farasi sahlo, naa cing a ping, zecawtamaw tatah naa buichung taitei a chuhpaw hmekhuh, hanghui le aihnaw sihnaw taikhah chyhraw chykheh khah Khazing naa peh naná teitah dingnah le Khazing do khah naa thlawdaw. A hmetaw teipaw heh dethlang lytah ahning teipaw zong heh naa tua ruapaw a cang.
\p 
\v 43 Farasi sahlo, naa cing a ping, zecawtamaw tatah synagog letah achaw caipaw dyching letah a ty du he ceh ka, chodo tlaang letah cizaw hmo tah bia a ching khah naa du.
\p 
\v 44 Naa cing a ping, zecawtamaw tatah naaning cawh ngianah a ung lypaw athlai, ahotahmai hni ly tei aa tlaichai teipaw hratah na cang he ceh,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 45 Phungbia a thai ngeteipaw hrong letei pakheh tah, “Cawngpahtu, ma vytei hming na rei tih lehei kaaning zong na ma zongte hrah,” tatah a chai.
\p 
\v 46 Zisu tah, “Naaning phungbia a thai ngeteipaw sahlo naa cing a ping, zecawtamaw tatah cawngsaw khah aa pho khy lypaw behnah phung hmingrih khing he ceh ka, naa vuhsah he. Naaning duiteisai cawh aaning baw rua pawtah naa kihdong hmai calia du bei he ceh.
\p 
\v 47 Naa cing a ping, zecawtamaw tatah naa pupaw sahlo tei aa za nongpaw he Khazing khuavang sahlo caw takhei thlailung sahlo naa bing he.
\v 48 Macawtaco naa pupaw sahlo aa tuasanah khah naa naw a tlah khui hrah he tahnah a cang, aaning tah Khazing khuavang sahlo khah aa nong he, naaning tah aa thlailung naa bing.
\v 49 Macawtaco Khazing singnah tei a reipaw cawh, ‘Khazing khuavang le apostol sahlo khah aaning khatah thlaw he neh ka, thaikheh khah theh a he ka, thaikhehpaw khah aa hrae he a,’ a tah.
\v 50 Macawtaco atochai cawngsaw sahlo cung lehei khazaw hrangthonah taitei aa thawpaw he Khazing khuavang vytei aa thisai rawng tah dangtahnah a tlung tae a.
\v 51 Abel thisai taitah dangnah siasang le behnah ing pathai kaa letah aa thawpaw Zakaria thisai tai a cang a. A cang, ka ca ching he, ma vytei cawtah hei atochai cawngsaw sahlo heh dangtah a cang tae he a.
\p 
\v 52 Naaning phungbia a thai ngeteipaw sahlo, naa cing a ping, zecawtamaw tatah hninah ingkaw cabi khah law he ceh ka, naa seikhui. Naaning duiteisai cawh a nae bei he ceh, taico a nae dupaw khah naa pakhang tlung he,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 53 Ma hminghmaw taico Zisu cawh a piathlah tihtah Farasi le phungbia cawngpahtu sahlo tah thaw tah cakhae he ka, hming a hlupui kong khah hae cakhia he ka,
\v 54 ma pawsui co a reichiapaw bia khei aa tle khy a.
\c 12
\s1 Raering pehnah le thawzaang pehnah
\r (Mt 10:28-33; 12:32)
\p 
\v 1 Ma cai leco cawngsaw thonghlupui a pahmo caw he tah pakheh le pakheh a tlaichai pai leimei he ka, Zisu tah ahmasaw cai tah a hningzuitu sahlo hai letah ma hrahei a rei. “Cungmai raipha a cangpaw Farasi sahlo raangri khah a raering my lo.
\v 2 No thlangpaw hming maikaw palang cang a he ka, biaparuh zong phy a cang he a.
\v 3 A muinah letah naa reipaw zong a khainah letah thui cang a ka, inah khang letei naa reipaw biaparuh zong khah ing tlungkhu taitah phy a cang he a.
\p 
\v 4 Ka huivesaw sahlo, ka ca ching he, pungsaw a theh khypaw sahlo khah ahohmai ci khe lo. Aa thaw khy taikhei zehmai tua khy khawh bei he.
\v 5 Canghrasala ahomaw naa ci ruapaw a cang takhah ka ca hmuh sá he a. Pungsaw zong thaw khy taitei hraihming lang zong thlah khynah naw a hnuipaw Khazing khah ci hri my lo. A cang, ka ca ching he, Ama cawh ci my lo.
\v 6 Baibaw pavaw sangpangaw khah tangka phaesai phaehning tah zua bei he maw? Canghrasala, sangkheh tei hmai khah Khazing tah monghly be.
\v 7 Ahmangpaw tei co, naa lu letei sangbu sahlo hmai rei thlu a cang he. Zehmai ci khe o. Naaning cawh baibaw pavaw sahlo navy tah na sungnaw vy he ceh.
\p 
\v 8 Cawngsaw hmekung letei Kama a pacang khuipaw cawh Cawngsaw Sawcapaw tah Khazing vaiming sahlo hme letah ka cangkhui hrá a.
\v 9 Canghrasala, ahohmai cawngsaw hrong letah Kama a pa paphahsaipaw cawh Khazing vaiming sahlo hme letah ka paphah sai hrá a.
\v 10 Taico ahohmai Cawngsaw Sawcapaw a reipachiapaw maikaw cawh ngethai khy cang thlang he ka, Thlawpaw Pathai a reipachiapaw maikaw cawh ngethai khy cang a bei he.
\p 
\v 11 Synagog sahlo le uhtu bui sahlo le nawhnuitu sahlo aa hme letah chuakhui naa cang tihtah zekhatamaw a reicakai neh ka, zemaw ka rei a tahpaw khah naa thlawzawng kheh seh.
\v 12 Zecawtamaw tatah ma cai letei naa rei ruapaw khah Thlawpaw Pathai tah a ca ching tae he a,” tatah a tah.
\s1 A hruhpaw mehrung tawchingnah
\p 
\v 13 Zawpui hrong taitah cawngsaw pakheh tah Zisu hai letah, “Cawngpahtu, ka unypaw khah ry chaichy pawtah pa chingpah law,” a tah.
\p 
\v 14 Zisu taco, “Cawngsawpaw, naa pahning kaa letah biacetu le ry chytu tah ahomaw naw hnuinah a pa pei?” tatah a chai.
\v 15 Mataico aa zongmingtei hai letah, “A raering teitah ung my lo! Du hlui hnuinah a phingphing khah a raering my lo. Cawngsaw hringnah heh a hnuipaw rungnah letah a pahnia be,” a tah.
\p 
\v 16 Mataico aa hai letah ma tawchingnah bia heh a ching he, “Mehrungpaw pakheh a ly cawh kungvui a chah ngetei.
\v 17 Ama le ama cawh, ‘Zekhatamaw tua neh seh la, a chah a? Ka saze chia nápaw hminghmaw hmai a ung khawh tlung be,’ a tah.
\p 
\v 18 Taico a reipaw cawh, ‘Ma hrahei ka tua a. Ka sachai heh chehthlah a neh ka, alai vypaw ka sá a, ma leco ka saze vytei le ka hmingbo sahlo ka chia a.
\v 19 Taico kama le kama khah, “Kung hlupui cawtah hmingchaw a hlupui hnui ceh ka, a nawng teitah ung la, e la, ding la, a nawng my lo,” tatah ka tah a,’ tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 20 Canghrasala Khazing tah, ‘Mehruhpaw! Ato zai hrahring lehei na thi a. Macawtaco na cawtah na pacungpaw hming vytei cawh aho tamaw a lah a?’ tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 21 Ama a caw suipaw tah hming pacung katei, Khazing letah a rung lypaw cawngsaw maikaw cawh ma hraco a cang a,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Naa thlawzawng kheh seh
\r (Mt 6:25-34)
\p 
\v 22 Mataico Zisu tah a hningzuitu sahlo hai letah, “Macawtaco ka ca ching he, naa hringnah cawtah zemaw kaa e a, a cang ly leh naa pung cawtah a buh a sai ruapaw kong letah naa lung reithui kheh seh.
\v 23 Hringnah heh e le ba navy tah sungnaw vy ka, pung heh chaichi navy tah a sungnaw vy.
\v 24 Ra-aw khah pacang tua hmai, thleci cing be ca he ka saze zong hre bei he, sachai zong hnui bei he, a cang naná teitah Khazing tah a cong thlang he. Naaning cawh pavaw navy tah a sungnaw vypaw cang bei he ceh maw!
\v 25 Naa hrong letah ahomaw a lungreithuinah rawng tah a hringnah cai suimehlang pakheh chang a chahchi khy?
\v 26 Ma hratei hming a chia pawtei hmai naa tua khy tlung lypaw tah zecawtamaw a hringpaw hming cawtah lungreithui tah naa ung?
\p 
\v 27 Lili pangpa sahlo khah zekhatamaw aa ka cy tahpaw pacang tua o. Rai hre bei he, chaichi a taw bei he. Canghrasala ma heh ka ca ching he, siangpahrang Solomon hmai khah ma tlua khei a laisui thlang naná teitah ma pangpa sahlo letei kung kheh tlua khei hmai pasang cang be.
\v 28 Vy naaning zingnah a cawngpaw sahlo, alui letah atoning ka cy katei, ningthlamong me lang aa bo thlangpaw araang hmai a pasangpaw Khazing taco naaning cawh a ca pasang vy chichi he a.
\v 29 Macawtaco, naa ding naa e ruapaw kong pacang tah lung reithui tah ung khe lo.
\v 30 Zecawtamaw tatah ma hapaw hming sahlo cawh lawki cawngsaw sahlo zong tah aa hui teipaw cang hrah ka, naa Paw vaicung leteipaw tah naa hiapaw khah a hni thlang.
\v 31 Canghrasala a painah raang khah hui la, ma hming vytei zong heh peh na cang thlang a he ceh.
\p 
\v 32 Phu cawngtei sahlo, ci khe lo. Zecawtamaw tatah naa Paw tah a painah raang a ca pehpaw he khah a lung a lawngpaw a cang.
\v 33 Naa hnuichia sahlo khah zua la, mehsisah sahlo khah pei my lo. A cai thai lypaw tangkabawng khah a zaa la, mehru tei aa ruh khylynah le luichaw tei aa e khylynah hming, vaicung letah aa chang khaw lypaw chosung sahlo cawh pacung my lo.
\v 34 Zecawtamaw tatah naa chosung a ungnah letah naa lungthing cawh a ung hrá a.
\s1 A mai pacia my lo
\r (Mt 24:45-51)
\p 
\v 35 Rai hre pawtah caise a tua pacia tah ung la, me-ing vang cia tah chia my lo.
\v 36 Nupui chui kongchuanah hming taitah a va tlung kawpaw aa buipaw cawh a va chua cangkawleh ingkaw a khong tihtah rairang teitah hongpah rua pawtah a heh thlangpaw a saecapaw sahlo hratah ung my lo.
\v 37 Aa buipaw tah a hraw hmotei a heh thlangpaw he sae sahlo, a va chuahnopaw sahlo he cawh meh vaichaw a cang he. Biahmuisui ka ca ching he, ama cawh raihrenah caise a tua ka, cabuai cadung sá he ka, ama hrahring tah a tuitang he a.
\v 38 Zaicing tamaw a cang ly leh ma navy co a haa vy tah a va tlung tih letah hmai a mai pacia teitah aa za haw thlangpaw khah aa buipaw tah a hmuh caco he, ma sae sahlo cawh meh vaichaw a cang he a.
\v 39 Canghrasala ma heh hnih my lo. Ing hnuitu tah mehru cawh ze cai letah maw a va chua a takhah hnih thah my seh la, a ing cawh hrawh sá a be.
\v 40 Macawtaco a mai pacia tah ung my lo, zecawtamaw tatah Cawngsaw Sawcapaw cawh naa rawh lypaw cai lekhei a vong a,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 41 Piter taco, “Abuipaw, ma tawchingnah bia heh kaaning longtei maw na ma ching, a cang ly leh ming vytei caw tamaw?” tatah a hae.
\p 
\v 42 Abuipaw taco, “Aho khah maw zing a chuipaw le a singpaw, a ingchungkho sae sahlo khah a cai naning teitah batui peh rua pawtah a buipaw tah rai a pehpaw mingkaitu cawh a cang?
\v 43 Aa buipaw a va tlung kaw tihtah ma hratei a tuapaw a hmuhpaw sae cawh meh vaichaw a cang.
\v 44 Biahmuisui ka ca ching he, ma paw cawh a hnuichia vytei a mingkaitu takhei a tua a.
\v 45 Canghrasala a bianapaw tah a saecapaw taco ama le ama khah, ‘Ka buipaw cawh a va tlung nápaw a ne be,’ tatah tah ka, zuding saw e tah ung ka, ahringpaw sae canu le sae capaw sahlo khah a dai he.
\v 46 Ma saecapaw a buipaw cawh a rawh lypaw ning le a pacang lypaw cai letah va tlung a ka, a buipaw tah ma sae capaw cawh caiping caimang tah taichung a ka, a zing lypaw sahlo ungnah lekhei a ungsah hrah a.
\p 
\v 47 A buipaw dunah hni thlang tei, rai hre pawtah a mai pacia tei a ung lypaw le a buipaw dupaw a tua lypaw sae cawh ui hlupui tah chei a cang a.
\v 48 Canghrasala, a buipaw dunah hni ly hmotei dangtah tlang a cangpaw suanah a tuapaw cawh a cawng vy tah chei a cang a. A hlupui peh a cangpaw cawh a hlupui hae kaw a cang a. A hlupui kai sahpaw cawh a hlu vy tah hae kaw a cang he a,” a tah.
\s1 Denah cang lytah pachainah
\r (Mt 10:34-36)
\p 
\v 49 Ma hrahei a rei vy, “Alui heh me tah ro rua pawtah pui ka vong. Kang myca seh la, tah ka du caimang!
\v 50 Canghrasala baptisma cang nátah tai-ingpaw hnui neh ka, ma ka patlung ka patlia hlai cawh ka lung rei a thui caimang.\f + \fr 12:50 \ft Baptisma tahpaw heh Khri a tai-ing nápaw le a thih nápaw khah a cang.\f*
\v 51 Aluicung lehei denah chuasah rua pawtah a vong tatah maw naa parawh? Cang be, pachai pawtah a cang hri.
\v 52 Atotei ri hei co ingchungkho ingkheh letah a ungpaw cawngsaw papangaw hrong letah a pachai he ka, pathungpaw tah pahningpaw khah dy he ka, pahningpaw tah pathungpaw khah aa dy tae he a.
\v 53 Paw leh tah aa sawtei leh khah dy a he ka, sawtei leh tah aa paw leh khah aa dy he a. No leh tah aa sawcanu leh khah dy a he ka, sawcanu letah aa no leh khah aa dy he a. Sawcapaw no leh tah myno leh khah dy a he ka, myno leh tah aa pasaepaw no leh khah aa dy tae he a,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Khuacai hninah
\r (Mt 16:2-3; 5:25-26)
\p 
\v 54 Zisu taco mingzawpui hai letah, “Nitlah lang tah meding a ka chuhpaw naa hmuh tihtah sungkheh tah, ‘Khua a so a!’ tah he ceh ka, ma hraco a so tahtah.
\v 55 Thuilang tah thli a hrang tihtah, ‘Ning a paling tae a!’ tah he ceh ka, a paling tahtah.
\v 56 Cungmai raipha sahlo! Alui le avai ming he ceh ka, ningkhua zemaw a lo a tah cawh naa hni. Zekhatah zia tamaw atochai hming ung zia a silang heh naa ching pase thai be?
\p 
\v 57 Zecawtamaw naaning teitah zemaw ahmang tah cawh naa pacang thai be?
\v 58 Naa caraepaw khatah biacetu hme letah chua pawtah naa sei tihtah langpui letah a rai khy nápaw khah a zawng my lo. Ma hratei na tua ly caco biacetu hme letah ca chuakhui ka, biacetu tah nawhnuitu kih letah ca hlai sua a ka, taico thong letah thlah na cang sua a.
\v 59 Ka ca ching, tangka lia ruapaw na lia thlu hlai vytei cawh thong taitah chuh khy khaw bei ceh,” tatah a tah.
\c 13
\s1 A ngepachinah maw lydenah
\p 
\v 1 Ma ningcai taco ma letei a ungpaw cawngsaw thaikheh taco Zisu hai letah raang uhbui Pilat tei Galili cawngsaw thuihlainah aa tua leimei ning tah a thaw sahpaw he kong khah aa ching.
\v 2 Zisu tah, “Ma hratei thihnah a ingpaw Galili cawngsaw sahlo he khah ahringpaw Galili cawngsaw sahlo navy tah aa sua vy rawng tah a cang tatah maw naa rawh?
\v 3 Cang be tah ka ca ching he! Naaning zong na ngepachih ly caco he ceh na lyde hra he ceh.
\v 4 A cang ly leh Siloam ing a sangpaw a cing ning tah a naiseh pawhe cawngsaw pahrawhluireh khah Jerusalem khuapui chung letei a ungpaw a hringpaw cawngsaw sahlo navy tah aa sua vy cawtah a cang naa tah maw?
\v 5 Cang be tah ka ca ching he! Naaning zong na ngepachih ly caco he ceh na lyde hra he ceh,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 6 Taico Zisu tah ma tawchingnah bia heh ching he ka, “Cawngsawpaw tah a buichung letah thuiku kung kung kheh cing ka, a thui maw thui ly tatah a va ming tihtah zehmai hmuh be.
\v 7 Macawtaco buichung a mingkaipaw hai letah, ‘Ma thuiku kung heh a thui maw, thui ly tatah kung thung chung mingkai neh ka, zehmai hmuh bei neh. Hyhly! Cholui chang a pahry,’ tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 8 Buichung a mingkaipaw taco, ‘Abuipaw, ato kung kung kheh chung tei heh cawh ming cawng tua, a kaekang heh thlo pá neh ka, alui achawpaw ka bia a.
\v 9 Hangkung lang a thui caco chah thlang ka, ma hratah cang ly tei a thui ly caco, hyhly thlang lepui ceh,’ a tah,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Kai king no Sabat ning tah a dangsah
\p 
\v 10 Sabat ning tah Zisu tah synagog sangkheh letah a cawngpah leimeining he takhei,
\v 11 kung hrawhluireh chung khachia tah a tlepaw canuno a za ung. A kai a king thlu thah ka, a pathlang khy bingbi lytah a ung myca.
\v 12 Zisu tah ma no cawh a hmuh tihtah a hmelang va chuh law tatah y ka, “Cawngsawno, nama cawh na ciacung lynah taco a ca thlaw myca,” a tah.
\v 13 Taico a cung letah a kih pahnia ka, sungkheh teitah canuno cawh a ka pathlang khy ka, Khazing khah a reithai.
\p 
\v 14 Sabat ning tah Zisu tah cawngsaw a dangsah cawtah synagog a uhtu cawh a thingae ka, zawpuipaw khah, “Raihrenah ning ningruh a ung, Sabat ning rei lytah ma ningruh chung leco a vong tah na dangsah bei he ceh,” tatah a tah he.
\p 
\v 15 Abuipaw tah a hai letah, “Naaning cungmai raipha sahlo! Ahotahmai Sabat ning tah a co cang seh, a la cang seh, naa ing taitah thlaw he ceh ka, tui ding sá pawtah seikhui thlang bei he ceh maw?
\v 16 A cang caco Abraham pathlah a cangpaw, Setan tei kung hrawhluireh chung hrai katei a sahpaw heh Sabat ning zong tah dangsah pápaw cang bei maw?” a tah he.
\p 
\v 17 Ma hratei bia a palei tih he taco Ama a caraepaw vytei khah aaning a zeh. Canghrasala zawpuipaw taco a tuapaw hming ningang chuipaw vytei cawtah khei aa thaw a chah ngetei.
\s1 Aihrang ci le raangri tawchingnah bia
\r (Mt 13:31-33; Mk 4:30-32)
\p 
\v 18 Zisu tah, “Khazing painah raang cawh zekhatamaw a lo? Zekhatamaw kaa tawching a?
\v 19 Cawngsawpaw pakheh tah a ly chung letah a lingpaw aihrang ci khatah a lo. Aihrang ci cawh ka chang ka, thingkung tah a ka tua ka, pavaw sahlo tah a cai sahlo letah a cawng tei he,” a tah.
\p 
\v 20 Taico Zisu tah a tah vypaw cawh, “Khazing painah raang cawh zekhatamaw kaa tawching a?
\v 21 Canuno tah vedi hongkheh lekhei raangri pahlawh ka, a nong chi. Ma raangri taco vedi cawh a tho sahpaw hratah a cang,” a tah.
\s1 Ingkaw a bawpaw
\r (Mt 7:13-14, 21-23)
\p 
\v 22 Taico Zisu cawh Jerusalem lang a seinah langpui letah khuapui zong khuatei zong pae pai lai ka, a cawngpah lai he.
\v 23 Cawngsaw thaikheh tah, “Abuipaw, meh cawngtei long maw pachah a cang he a?” tatah aa hae.
\p 
\v 24 Zisu taco, ma hrahei a tah he, “Ingkaw a bawpaw lang tah a nae pawtah thaw tah a zong my lo, zecawtamaw tatah ka ca ching he, cawngsaw a hlupui tah a nae zaa he ka, a nae khy bei he.
\v 25 Ing hnuitu khah tho ka, a ingkaw khah a kha tae a. Taico naaning cawh ingkaw khungthing lang tah ingkaw khah khong he ceh ka, ‘Abuipaw ingkaw ma hong ky law,’ tatah naa ta a.
\p Canghrasala ama taco, ‘Ze taitah maw naa va chua? Naaning cawh ca hnih bei he neh,’ tatah a ca tah tae he a.
\p 
\v 26 Mataico naaning tah, ‘Nama khatah kaa e hrui, kaa ding hrui tei kha, kaa khuatlang letah na ma cawngpah tei kha saw,’ naa tah a.
\p 
\v 27 Canghrasala ama taco, ‘Naaning zong ca hnih bei he neh, zelang tamaw naa va chua tahpaw hnih bei neh. Naaning hming chahly a tuapaw vytei ka kae taitah seihly o!’ a ca tah tae he a.
\p 
\v 28 Naaning vytei cawh alailang letah vathlang cang he ceh ka, Abraham le Isak le Jakob le Khazing khuavang vytei cawh Khazing painah raang chung lekhei naa hmuh tae he a. Ma tih taco cá he ceh ka, naa haw naa ria tae a.
\v 29 Cawngsaw cawh nichua, nitlah, thuilang, tlanglang tah a vong a he ka, Khazing painah raang lawhdangnah hming lekhei a ty he a.
\v 30 Ma tih taco ato letei a hningcaipaw zong heh a hme a sahpaw cang he ka, ato letei a hme a sahpaw zong heh a hningcaipaw a cang tae he a,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Jerusalem cawtah Zisu a nge a chia
\r (Mt 23:37-39)
\p 
\v 31 Ma ning taco Farasi thaikhehpaw tah Zisu kha a vong he ka a hai letah, “Ma hminghmaw taihei piathlah la, hmingkheh kheh lang sei. Herod tah thaw a ca du,” tatah aa ching.
\p 
\v 32 Zisu tah, “Va sei la, ma sihatei khah va ching o, ‘Atoning zong, ningthlamong zong, khachia sahlo tingchua he neh ka, a dang lypaw ka dang sá he a. A ningthung ning tah ka rai cawh ka paling a.’
\v 33 Zekhatah a cang zong tah atoning, ningthlaw le hazaining tai cawh ka sei longmang thlang a. Zecawtamaw tatah Khazing khuavang cawh Jerusalem khuapui khungthing lang letah thih phung cang be!
\p 
\v 34 Vy Jerusalem! Jerusalem! Khazing khuavang sahlo khah za theh he ceh ka, Khazing tah naaning khatah a tawpaw he a cawngsaw sahlo khah alung tah naa vaseh tei he. Aa puino tah a sawtei leh a mathlaw rai letah a bakhupaw he hratah naa cawngsaw cawh uikhazeh uilui maw pakhawng du he neh ka, canghrasala du bei he ceh!
\v 35 Mingtua hmai o, naa ing cawh a ching myca. Ka ca ching he, ‘Abuipaw ming tah a vongpaw cawh bonghnang song cang ky seh,’\x + \xo 13:35 \xt Hlaw 118:26\x* tatah naa tah hlai vytei cawh pa hmuh kaw khaw bei ceh,” tatah a tah.
\c 14
\s1 Farasi ing letah Zisu
\p 
\v 1 Sabat ning leco Zisu cawh Farasi sahlo letei hruitu pakheh ing lang khah batui hrong pawtah a sei tihtah Ama cawh achaw teitah aa ngia lai.
\v 2 Ma leco a hmekaw letah cawngsawpaw pakheh thlingnah hri a ingpaw a ung.
\v 3 Zisu tah Farasi sahlo le phungbia a thai ngeteipaw sahlo cawh, “Sabat ning letah dangsah heh a phung a cang maw cang ly?” tatah a tah he.
\v 4 Canghrasala a cali thlang he. Macawtaco cawngsawpaw cawh va hre ka, dangsah ka, a seisah.
\p 
\v 5 Mataico aa hai letah, “Naaning hrong letah pakheh tah Sabat ning letah a sawtei pakheh a cang ly leh a co tungpaw sangkheh khobatlung lang tlah my seh la, rairang tah chuahly a bei maw?” tatah a tah he.
\v 6 Maco, a rei nápaw hnih bei he.
\p 
\v 7 Hruipaw cawngsaw sahlo tah cabuai letah a tynah achawpaw a thingpaw he khah Zisu tah a hmuh tihtah aaning cawh ma tawchingnah bia heh a ching he.
\v 8 “Pakheh kheh tah nupui chuinah letah a ca hrui tih he tah a tynah achawpaw lekhei a ty khe lo. Nama navy tah a puimaw vypaw cawngsaw pakheh zong a hrui mai a.
\v 9 Ma hratei a cang caco, naa pahning tah a ca hruipaw he kong a chuatupaw a vong ka, ‘Na tynah khah ama heh tlui,’ a ca tah a. Mataico ningzaw tah a chawly caipaw hming lekhei na ty a.
\v 10 Canghrasala aa ca hrui tih he tah a nai caipaw hming lekhei a ty o. Maco a ca hruitupaw he a vong tihtah ama taco, ‘Ka dua, achaw vypaw hming lang a palong,’ a ca tah a. Ma tih taco male hme letah upanah na hmuh a.
\v 11 Ahohmai ama le ama a pasangpaw cawh nytaw tah ung ka, ama le ama a panaipaw cawh pasang a cang a,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 12 Mataico, Zisu tah kong a chuatupaw cawh, “Ching batui a cang ly leh zairia na tua tihtah na vesaw sahlo, na uny sahlo, naa sawny sahlo, a cang ly leh naa ingpaw mehrung sahlo khah hrui khe lo. Na hrui caco he aaning tah nama khah ca hrui kaw hrá he ka, chang kaw na cang tha a.
\v 13 Canghrasala lawhdangnah na tua tihtah dawngchiapaw, ciacung lypaw, a phe a cabepaw le a mehcopaw khah hrui hri la, bonghnang song na cang a.
\v 14 Aaning tah aa ca chang khy ly tahmai mehding thokawnah letah chang kaw na cang a,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Lawhdangnah rungnawpaw tawchingnah
\r (Mt 22:1-10)
\p 
\v 15 Aaning hrong letei pakheh ama kha cabuai a cadung hruipaw taco a thui tihtah Zisu cawh, “Khazing painah raang letei lawhdangnah letah batui a epaw cawngsaw cawh meh vaichaw a cang a,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 16 Zisu taco, “Pakhehpaw cawh kongchuanah rungnawpaw pachia ka, cawngsaw hlupui a hrui he.
\v 17 Kongchuanah cai a zaw tihtah aa hruipaw he khah, ‘A vong myca o, zezong a tlang a tling thlu myca,’ tatah ching pawtah a sae khah a taw.
\p 
\v 18 Canghrasala aa zongmingtei khei biasi aa phe thlu. A pakhehnahpaw taco, ‘Atotei khah alui co neh ka, va ming pawtah sei ka du. Pa ngethai ky,’ a tah.
\p 
\v 19 Ahringpaw taco, ‘Atotei khah co tungpaw ching pangaw co neh ka, aaning khah hnehsá pawtah seipaw ka cang. Pa ngethai ky,’ a tah.
\p 
\v 20 Ahringpaw vy taco, ‘Atotei khah nupui chui neh ka, macawtaco a vong thai bei neh,’ a tah.
\p 
\v 21 A sae cawh a vong kaw ka, ma bia cawh a buipaw khah a ching. Mataico ing a hnuitupaw cawh a thingae ka a sae cawh, ‘Khuapui letei langpui sahlo le ing kaa leh ing kaa letei lang sahlo lang rairang tah va sei la, a dawngchiapaw, a ciacung lypaw, a mehcopaw le a phesongpaw khah va chuakhui o,’ a tah.
\p 
\v 22 A sae taco, ‘Abuipaw, na pa chingpaw hrakhei tua neh ka, canghrasala ing chung letah chih balang bei he,’ tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 23 Taico, a buipaw tah a sae cawh, ‘Langpui sahlo lang le arangchung lang va sei la, ka ing chih ky tah cawngsaw chuasah my lo.
\v 24 Ka ca ching, ka hruipaw sahlo he takhei co, ka lawhdangnah batui heh pateh khy bei he,’ a tah,” tatah a tah.
\s1 A hningzuitu cangnah mai
\r (Mt 10:37-38)
\p 
\v 25 Zawpuipaw cawh Zisu khatah khua tlawnglai he ka, Zisu tah aaning lang cawh a hui ka,
\v 26 “Ahohmai kama kha a vong katei a no le a paw, a nupui le a saw sahlo, a uny sahlo le a satei sahlo le ama a hringnah hmai khah kama navy tah a do vypaw cawh ka hningzuitu cang khy be.
\v 27 Taico, ma leh khraws a puá tah a pa zui lypaw cawh ka hningzuitu cang khy be.
\p 
\v 28 Naaning hrong letah aho tamaw ingsang sah du seh la, a hnuipaw tangka tah a palingnah tai a zy maw tahpaw hni rua tah patih patong taw a bei maw?
\v 29 A hrang patho thah katei, a paling khy lypaw tei a cang caco, aa hmuhpaw maikaw tah ama cawh aa hnuiso a.
\v 30 ‘Ma cawngsawpaw tahei ingsah patho ka, paling khy khawh be,’ aa tah a.
\p 
\v 31 A cang ly leh abui pakheh cawh abui hringpaw dy rua pawtah sei seh la, ama dy rua pawtah mehnung thongki khatah a va seipaw pakheh khah mehnung thonghraw khatah a te khy a maw tahpaw cawh pacang taw a bei maw?
\v 32 Te khy bei neh takhah a hni caco, a caraepaw langhlaw letah a ung chung takhei ai-awhtu sahlo thlaw tah arainah a hae a.
\v 33 Ma hraco naaning zong naa hnuipaw maikaw naa seisai ly caco, ka hningzuitu cang khy bei he ceh.
\p 
\v 34 Paci cawh a chah, canghrasala a aenah a ly caco zekhatamaw aa aesah kaw khy a?
\v 35 Alui a chah sápaw cawtah chah be ca ka, ingding tah tua rua tah zong chah be, vathlang ruapaw suipaw a cang thlang a.
\p Thuinah nawkho a hnuipaw maikaw taco, ma bia heh thui he seh,” tatah a tah.
\c 15
\s1 Tu a lypaw tawchingnah
\r (Mt 18:12-14)
\p 
\v 1 Taico ngungkhui kheitu sahlo le ahringpaw mehsua sahlo cawh Zisu a bia nge rua pawtah aa dawngkasawny teitah a pahmo he.
\v 2 Canghrasala Farasi le phungbia cawngpahtu sahlo taco, “Ma cawngsawpaw tahei mehsua sahlo achaw teitah chai he ka, aaning khatah batui a e thlang dei e,” tatah a phing he.
\p 
\v 3 Mataico Zisu tah aaning cawh ma tawchingnah bia heh a ching he.
\v 4 “Naaning hrong letah pakheh tah a hnuipaw tuu zakheh lekhei sangkheh ly seh la, songkua sangkuapaw khah arangchung letah seisai tah a lypaw tuu khah seihno tah a hmuh kaw hlai vytei hui bei maw?
\v 5 Taico, a lypaw tuu khah a hmuh kaw tihtah lunglawng teitah a saitlang letah khing ka, ing lang a tlung.
\v 6 Mataico a vesaw sahlo le a ingpaw sahlo khah y he ka, ‘A pa lawng khui law, ka tuu a lypaw ka hmuh kaw thah e,’ a tah he.
\v 7 Ka ca ching he, ma hraco mehding a ngepachih a hia lypaw songkua pakua navy co, a ngepachihpaw mehsua pakheh cung lekhei vaicung letah alawngnah a hlu vy.
\s1 Tangka a lypaw tawchingnah
\p 
\v 8 A cang ly leh canuno pakheh tah ngung tangka phaehraw hnui seh la, phaekheh hly tua seh. Ma no taco me-ing vang tah ing phih a ka, a hmuh hlai tai achaw teitah hui a bei maw?
\v 9 Ma no taco ma tangka cawh a hmuh tihtah a vesaw sahlo le a ingpaw sahlo khah y pakhong he ka, ‘A pa lawng khui law, a lypaw tangka khah ka hmuh thah e,’ tatah a tah he.
\v 10 Ma hraco ka ca ching he, angepachihpaw mehsua pakheh cung lehei Khazing a vaiming sahlo hme letah alawngnah a ung,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Sawcapaw a lypaw tawchingnah
\p 
\v 11 Zisu tah a bia cawh reipazo ka, “Cawngsawpaw pakheh ung ka, sawcapaw pahning a hnui.
\v 12 A nyheh vypaw tah a paw cawh, ‘Apaw, ka ting vypaw ry pa pei law,’ tah ka, macawtaco a paw tah a hnuipaw khah aaning cawh a chaichy he.
\p 
\v 13 Khua sy a ry hlai tah a sawcapaw a nyheh vypaw taco a hnuipaw vytei cawh pakhong ka, langhlaw pui raang lang seihly ka, ma leco a tangka vytei cawh a nawngnangnah letah a hmang thlu.
\v 14 A hnuipaw vytei a hmang thlu khy taikhei ma raang chung vytei leco cakaang a thaw tah tlung ka, ama cawh a phahlah pawngchang tah a ung myca.
\v 15 Mataico ma raang letei cawngsawpaw pakheh khatah a vaw ka, a hlofa. Ma cawngsawpaw taco voh lawh a pei ruapaw tah ly lang a taw.
\v 16 A ngai a di tu cawtah voh lawh khah hmai e du ngetei ka, canghrasala e ruapaw ahohmai a peipaw ung bei he.
\p 
\v 17 A lung ka sing ka, ama tei co, ‘Ka paw ing letei a hlofapaw sahlo tahmai e ruapaw a hlupui hnui he ka, kama cawh ma lehei ngaidi tah ka thi daimang myca!
\v 18 Tho a neh ka, ka paw kha ka sei a. Taico, “Ka paw, Khazing hme le na hme letah ka sua myca.
\v 19 Na sawtei tah tlang hmai a tlah khawh bei neh, canghrasala, na raihrepaw sahlo letei pakheh hratah pa tua ky law,” tatah ka tah a,’ a tah.
\v 20 Macawtaco tho ka, a paw khaco a sei.
\p Canghrasala langhlaw pui letah a va sei leimeining takhei a paw taco va hmuh ka, ning a do ngetei. Va saihno ka, a pongchai ka, a hnang.
\p 
\v 21 A sawcapaw taco, ‘Apaw, Khazing hme le na hme letah ka sua myca. Kama cawh na sawcapaw tah tlang hmai a tlah khawh bei neh,’ tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 22 Canghrasala a paw taco a sae sahlo cawh, ‘Pai achaw caipaw khah rairang tah va tle la, a buh sá o. A kihdong lekhei kihsapadi a hro sá la, a phe lekhei phepakong a pakong sá o.
\v 23 A thy caipaw co tungnypaw khah va hrui la, theh my lo. Kongchuanah tuá tah a nawng he peh.
\v 24 Ma ka sawcapaw heh thi ka, a kahring kaw, ama cawh ly ka, ka hmuh kawpaw a cang,’ tatah a tah. Mataico lawhdangnah cawh aa tua.
\p 
\v 25 Ma chung cawh a sawcapaw uthuipaw cawh ly letah a ung thlang. Ing lang ka tlung ka, ing kae a va phah tihtah hlaw o le aa langpaw py khah a thui.
\v 26 Macawtaco sae pakheh khah y ka, ‘Zemaw naa tua?’ tatah a hae.
\v 27 Ma saecapaw taco, ‘Na nyteipaw va kaw kaw ka, a bing teitah a va kaw kaw cawtah na paw tah a thy caipaw co tungnypaw khah a thaw,’ tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 28 Uthuipaw cawh a thingae ka, ing chunglang a nae du khawh be. Macawtaco a paw cawh piathlah ka, a va naw.
\v 29 Canghrasala a paw hai leco, ‘Rawh tua hmai! Kung ma vytei heh sae hratah ca hrepah neh ka, na reipaw zong nge lytah ung bang bei neh. Ma naná co hmai ka vesaw sahlo kha a nawng nápaw cawtah mei teitei hmai pa pei bang bei ceh.
\v 30 Canghrasala ma na sawcapaw tahei na tangka vytei khah hlohlang no khatah hly thlu ka, ing lang a va kaw kaw tihtah a caw taco a thy caipaw co na thawpah!’ tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 31 A paw taco, ‘Ka sawcapaw, nama cawh kama khatah ung leimei thlang ceh ka, ka hnuipaw vytei heh na tei a cang.
\v 32 Canghrasala a lawngnah dy tua tah kaa lawngpaw he peh a cang, zemaw tah pawco ma na nyteipaw heh thi ka, a ka hring kaw, ama cawh ly ka, hmuh kawpaw a cang,’ tatah a palei,” tatah Zisu tah a tah.
\c 16
\s1 Hming a mingkaitu mehdihly
\p 
\v 1 Zisu tah a hningzuitu sahlo cawh, “Mehrung pakheh ung ka, hming a mingkaitu pakheh a hnui. Hming a mingkaitu taco mehrungpaw a cho le pe sahlo cawh a longdepaw tah a tua tatah pu a cang.
\v 2 Macawtaco ama cawh mehrungpaw tah y ka, ‘Na kong ka thuipaw heh zekhatamaw a cang? Rai na hrepaw cazing papei, zecawtamaw tatah ka hming mingkaitu cang khy khawh bei ceh,’ a tah.
\p 
\v 3 Hming a mingkaitu taco ama le ama cawh, ‘Zemaw ka tua a? Ka buipaw tah ka rai a pa lah pah thah. Alui che pawtah thawzaang hnui tlung be ca neh ka, kih do pawtah ka ning a zeh tlung.
\v 4 A cang caco, zemaw ka tua a tahpaw ka hni myca! Ma hratei ka tua caco, ka rai a chang tihtah cawngsaw tah aa ing letah aa pa tlungsah du a,’ tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 5 Maco a buipaw khatei luibah a hnuipaw sahlo khah pakheh cy tah y he ka, a pakhehnah khah, ‘Ka buipaw cawh khazeh maw na bah?’ tatah a hae.
\p 
\v 6 ‘Oliv sathy galon pung zareh,’ tatah a palei.
\p Hming a mingkaitu taco, ‘Na cazing law la, rairang tah a ty la, galon pung zapali tatah cia,’ tatah a ching.
\p 
\v 7 Mataico a pahningnah cawh, ‘Nama saw khazeh maw na bah?’ tatah a hae.
\p ‘Changvuh bai thongkheh,’ tatah a palei.
\p Ma cawngsawpaw zong cawh, ‘Na cazing law la, zareh tatah cia,’ tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 8 Ma hming a mingkaitu mehdih lypaw tei singthai tei hming a tuapaw cawh a buipaw tah a pachaw ngetei. A hmang, khazaw cawngsaw heh aaning aa mehnung hui khatei aa cawtah aa tuanah kong leco Khazing a khainah letei a ungpaw cawngsaw navy tah a sing vy he.
\v 9 Ka ca ching he, khazaw cho le pe heh vesaw hnui nápawtah hmang o. Ma hratei naa tua caco, naa cho a chang tihtah chaizaw ing letah naa ung he ceh.
\p 
\v 10 Ahohmai a chia pawtei letah zingchui pawtah a ungpaw cawh alaipaw zong letah zingchuipaw cang tei ka, ahohmai a chia pawtei letah zing a chui lypaw cawh alaipaw zong letah zing chui hrah be.
\v 11 Macawtaco, khazaw hnuirungnah letah zingchuipaw naa cang ly caco, rungnah hmuisuipaw letah ahomaw a ca zing he a?
\v 12 Taico, cawngsaw hringpaw hnuicho letah zingchuipaw naa cang ly caco ahomaw naa tei rua pawtah hming a ca pei he a?
\p 
\v 13 Aho sae tahmai abui pahning aa rai hre khy be. Pakheh a hua ka, pakheh a do a, a cang ly leh pakheh cung letah zingchuipaw tah ung a ka, pakheh khah ze tah rei a be. Khazing rai kha, tangka rai kha hre pakong khy bei ceh,” tatah a ching he.
\p 
\v 14 Tangka a dupaw Farasi sahlo tah ma bia cawh thui he ka, Zisu cawh aa hmo aa miaso.
\v 15 Zisu tah aaning cawh, “Cawngsaw mehmuh letah thai a cangsah he ceh ka, canghrasala naa lungthing cawh Khazing tah a hni. Cawngsaw tah a sungsah ngeteipaw heh Khazing mehmuh leco pasih a chuipaw a cang.
\s1 Cawngpahnah chahchipaw
\r (Mt 11:12-13; 5:31-32; Mk 10:11-12)
\p 
\v 16 Moses phungbia le Khazing khuavang bia sahlo cawh baptisma peitu Johan chai tai khah a cang he. Ma cai ri taico Khazing painah raang thawngchawbia cawh rei leimei tah cang ka, ming hlupui cawh ma langpui chunglang khah a chuchei tah a nae he.
\v 17 Khazing phungbia cabu chung letei a chia caipaw, casung tei deipaw tei hmai heh lahly navy co, alui le avai a lypaw hmai heh a neh vy syly a.
\p 
\v 18 A nupui mah katei ahringpaw canu a chuipaw cawh a pheipaw a cang. Mah ciapaw canu a chuipaw capaw cawh a pheipaw a cang,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Mehrungpaw le Lazaru
\p 
\v 19 A rei vypaw cawh, “Mehrungpaw pakheh, saidungpaw paithladih anaipaw a tua katei, ning tating tei a nawng teitah khua a sahpaw a ung.
\v 20 Kih dopaw, a ming Lazaru aa tahpaw, hmawchia tei a pahlong thlangpaw khah a hawkaw letah chia he ka,
\v 21 mehrungpaw a cabuai taitah didang a tlahpaw khah e rua pawtah a du ngetei. Ui sahlo taco a vong he ka, a hmaw khah aa liapah tei.
\p 
\v 22 Kih dopaw cawh a thihnah cai a va phah tihtah vaiming tah ama cawh Abraham kae letah aa seikhui. Mehrungpaw zong cawh thi hrah ka, aa phung.
\v 23 Vaisang ngetei tei a ungnah hraihming taikhei, a cung lang cawh a kahui ka, langhlaw pui lekhei Abraham le a kae letei Lazaru khah a hmuh he.
\v 24 Taico Abraham cawh y ka, ‘Ka paw Abraham, ning pa do la, Lazaru khah taw la, a kih dong khah tui letah nong seh la, ka lui a cakaw nápawtah za pa thlah so ky seh, zecawtamaw tatah ma me lehei ka tai tu myca,’ tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 25 Canghrasala Abraham taco, ‘Ka sawtei, na hring chung tei hming chawpaw na cypaw vytei khah a thui thlang bei ceh maw? Ma ning lekhei Lazaru taco hmingchahly a cy kho. Canghrasala, atoheh cawh ama cawh ma lehei a hnaw pangang he ka, nama cawh taisai na tai myca.
\v 26 Ma hlui co, na kaa le kaa kaa lehei khobatlung a thuh ngeteipaw ung ka, macawtaco ma taihei nama kha a va sei dupaw sahlo aa va sei khy lypaw hratah ma taikhei kaaning khatah ahohmai va cakang khy hrá bei he,’ tatah a palei.
\p 
\v 27 Mataico mehrungpaw taco, ‘Ka ca naw, ka paw! Lazaru khah ka paw ing lang taw la,
\v 28 uny papangaw hnui he neh ka, aaning cawh a raeringnah va pei he seh la, ma tai-ingnah hming lang heh aa va sei ly nápawtah,’ tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 29 Abraham taco, ‘Moses le Khazing khuavang sahlo hnui thlang he ka, aaning aa bia cawh nge thlang he seh,’ tatah a palei.
\p 
\v 30 Mehrungpaw taco, ‘Cang be, ka paw Abraham, a thi ciapaw tah aaning kha aa va sei caco, aa ngepachih thlang he a,’ tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 31 Canghrasala Abraham taco, ‘Moses le Khazing khuavang sahlo aa bia aa nge ly caco, thihnah taitah a thokawpaw aa ung tahmai tah aa bia zong nge hlui a bei he,’ tatah a palei,” tatah Zisu tah a tah.
\c 17
\s1 Suanah, zingnah le hre ruapaw rai
\r (Mt 18:6-7, 21-22; Mk 9:42)
\p 
\v 1 Zisu tah a hningzuitu sahlo hai leco, “Cawngsaw a suasahpaw hming sahlo a ung paria thlang he a. Canghrasala suanah a chuakhuipaw mehnung cawh a cing a ping.
\v 2 Ma nyhehtei sahlo lehei pakheh hmai heh a suasahpaw cawh a hirong letah saangrianah lung pathle tah rili lang thlah he seh la, a cawtah a chah vy a.
\v 3 Macawtaco a singkang my lo.
\p Na unypaw tah suanah a tua caco, chinghring la, a ngepachih caco ngethai my lo.
\v 4 Ning kheh tah uisarih na cung letah sua katei, uisarih nama kha a vong tah, ‘Ka ngepachih,’ a ca tah caco ngethai my lo,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 5 Apostol sahlo tah Abuipaw cawh, “Kaa zingnah heh changchysah vy law!” tatah aa tah.
\p 
\v 6 Zisu taco, “Aihrang hmu tia tei chang zingnah naa hnui caco, ma siasahming kung heh, ‘A phehly la, rili letah va cy law,’ tah khy he ceh ka, naa bia a ca nge thlang he a.
\p 
\v 7 Naaning hrong letah pakheh tah alui a paleh ruapaw tamaw, tuu a king ruapaw tamaw sae pakheh hnui seh la, arangchung lang tah a va tlung tihtah, ‘A vong la, a ty la batui e,’ naa tah a maw?
\v 8 Ma hraco tah lytah, ‘Batui pa tuapah, a pachia la, ka ding ka e chung vytei heh pa ungpai thlang, ma khy taico na ding na e tae hra a,’ tah hri bei maw?
\v 9 Ma a saecapaw tah a chingpaw hratah a tua cawtah a buipaw tah a cung letah a lawng hlui be.
\v 10 Ma hraco naaning khatah chingpaw vytei heh naa tua thlu khy taitah hmai, ‘A chahnai lypaw sae kaa cang he peh, kaa hre ruapaw rai pui kaa hre hi,’ tah my lo,” a tah he.
\s1 Thinghmuihri a ingpaw pahraw dangsahnah
\p 
\v 11 Zisu cawh Jerusalem lang a seining takhei, Samaria le Galili raangri khei a sei lai.
\v 12 Khua khuakheh chunglang a nae ka, thinghmuihri a ingpaw pahraw cawh Ama khatah a tong he. Langhlaw pui khei a daw he ka,
\v 13 a thangpui tah, “Zisu, Abuipaw, ning ma do ky law!” tatah a y he.
\p 
\v 14 Aaning cawh a hmuh tih he tah Zisu taco, “Sei la, tlangbui sahlo khah a va hmuhsah my lo,” a tah he. Taico, aa seining tah langpui letah a dang he.
\p 
\v 15 Aaning chung taitah pakhehpaw cawh ka dang tahpaw khah a hni tihtah Khazing khah a thangpui tah reithai hmo khei a va kaw kaw.
\v 16 Zisu a phehrang lekhei a bawh ka, alawngnah bia a rei. Ma cawngsaw cawh Samaria\f + \fr 17:16 \ft Juda cawngsaw le Samaria cawngsaw cawh pakheh le pakheh a nytaw he.\f* mingphing a cang.
\p 
\v 17 Zisu tah, “Dang sahpaw khah pahraw cang bei he maw? Pakuapaw saw zeletamaw aa ung?
\v 18 Ma mingphing hringpaw rei ly hei a vong tah Khazing reithainah a hlaipaw pakheh chang ung be dei he?” tatah a tah.
\v 19 Mataico Samaria cawngsawpaw hai leco, “Tho la sei, na zingnah tah a ca dangsah,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Khazing painah raang a vongnah
\r (Mt 24:23-28, 37-41)
\p 
\v 20 Uikheh cawh, Farasi sahlo tah zening tamaw Khazing painah raang cawh a va tlung a tatah aa haepaw khah, Zisu tah, “Khazing painah raang cawh naa hmuh khy pawtah va tlung a be.
\v 21 Cawngsaw tah, ‘Ma lehei a ung, a cang ly leh ma lekhei a ung,’ tah khy bei he, zecawtamaw tatah Khazing painah raang cawh naa chung letah a ungnah cawtah a cang,” tatah a palei he.
\p 
\v 22 Mataico a hningzuitu sahlo hai leco, “Cawngsaw Sawcapaw heh ningkheh tachang hmuh naa du ngetei nápaw ning le cai khah a va tlung tae a, canghrasala hmuh khy a bei ceh.
\v 23 Cawngsaw hlupui tah, ‘Ama cawh ma lekhei a ung khi, a cang ly leh ma lehei a ung hi,’ tatah aa ca tah he a. Ama cawh hui pawtah piahly khe lo.
\v 24 Cawngsaw Sawcapaw a vongnah ning leco lailaw ky katei, avai a ki rakheh taitah a ki rakheh lang a khaipalehpaw hratah a cang tae a.
\v 25 Canghrasala a hmasaw letaco hming a hlupui khah tai-ing taw a ka, atochai cawngsaw tahei aa hlawh tae a.
\p 
\v 26 Noah a chai ning leteipaw hrakhei Cawngsaw Sawcapaw a vongnah cawh a cang tae a.
\v 27 Cawngsaw sahlo cawh Noah tuilawng chunglang a naenah ning tai lekhei e he ka, ding he ka, a chuihae he ka, a hnui he. Mataico tuipa-ia cawh tlung ka, aaning vytei cawh aa dawngkasawny tah a hlyde thlu he.
\p 
\v 28 Ma heh Lot a chai ning teipaw khakhei a lo. Cawngsaw sahlo cawh e he ka, ding he ka, co he ka, zua he ka, cing he ka, ing aa sah.
\v 29 Canghrasala Lot tah Sodom khua a piasaining tah me le me a epaw kaa cawh avai taitah za so ka, aaning cawh aa dawngkasawny tah a ro cehceh he.
\p 
\v 30 Ma tei hraco Cawngsaw Sawcapaw a vong kaw ning taco a cang hra a.
\v 31 Ma ning leco ing cung letei a ungpaw cawh ing chung letei a hmingbo lá pawtah a nae kheh seh. Ma hraco ly letah a ungpaw ahohmai hming sangkheh kheh lá pawtah ing lang kawkaw kheh seh.
\v 32 Lot a nupuino khah a thui thlang my lo.
\v 33 A hringnah pachah a pachiapaw taco sung a ka, a hringnah a sungpaw taco a pachah a.
\v 34 Ka ca ching he, ma zai leco lakhing sangkheh letah a ih hruipaw cawngsaw pahning chung taikhei pakheh cawh lah cang ka, pakheh cawh seisai a cang a.
\v 35 Canu pahning tah saang suh hrui a he ka, pakheh cawh lah cang a ka, pakheh cawh seisai a cang a.
\v 36 Cawngsaw pahning ly chung letah ung he ka, pakheh cawh lah cang a ka, pakheh cawh seisai a cang a,”\f + \fr 17:36 \ft Kih cia thaikheh leco cai 36 heh ung be.\f* tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 37 “Abuipaw, zeletamaw ma hming cawh a tlung a?” tatah aa hae.
\p Zisu taco, “Sarawh a ungnah hming leco langtaw pavaw cawh a pahmo tei he,” tatah a palei he.
\c 18
\s1 Tai lytah a haepaw lahmeno tawchingnah
\p 
\v 1 Mataico Zisu tah lungdong lytah thlaw aa chang paria nápawtah cawngpahnah cawtah tawchingnah bia khah a hningzuitu sahlo a ching he.
\v 2 Aa hai letaco, “Khuapui khua kheh letah Khazing a ci lypaw le cawngsaw zetah a rei lypaw biacetu pakheh a ung.
\v 3 Taico ma khuapui letei a ungpaw lahme no pakheh taco ama khatah a vaw ka, ‘Ka caraepaw cung letah a dihpaw teitah bia pa cepah ky law,’ tatah a naw cakhawng leimei thlang.
\p 
\v 4 Ma biacetupaw taco uihlupui a bia cawh a ei. Canghrasala, a changnah leco ama le ama cawh, ‘Khazing ci ly le cawngsaw zetah rei lytah ung hmai my neh seh la,
\v 5 ma lahmeno heh cawh hna a pa hnawh leimeinah cawtah a bia cawh ka cepah thlang a. Ma pawsui co, a vong khaw be ca ka, ka rei pa pathui khaw be,’ a tah,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 6 Taico Abuipaw taco, “Mehding lypaw biacetu tei a reipaw heh nawthlia tua o!
\v 7 Khazing tah Ama a thingpaw cawngsaw, ching le zai tei ama khatah a y leimeipaw sahlo aa cai tah a dingpaw biacenah cawh tuapah lytah a ung a maw? Aaning bawkhang paw taco a hongsang a beh.
\v 8 Ka ca ching he, a dingpaw biacenah cawh rairang tah a tuapah he a. Ma duitei cawh Cawngsaw Sawcapaw a vongkaw tihtah alui lehei zingnah a hnuipaw he hmuh siama he maw?” tatah a tah.
\s1 Farasi le ngungkhui kheitu tawchingnah
\p 
\v 9 Thaikheh aaning le aaning mehding a tah ngetei he katei, cawngsaw maikaw a minghnawh pawhe sahlo khah Zisu tah ma tawchingnah bia heh a ching he.
\v 10 “Cawngsaw pahning cawh behnah ing lang thlawchang rua pawtah sei he ka, pakheh cawh Farasi cang ka, pakhehpaw cawh ngungkhui kheitu a cang.
\v 11 Farasipaw cawh a daw ka, ama a kong thlaw a changpaw cawh, ‘Vy Khazing, cawngsaw hringpaw, damia sahlo, chahlynah a tuapaw sahlo, a pheilaipaw sahlo, a cang ly leh ma ngungkhui kheitu hrahei ka cang lynah cawtah ka ca long.
\v 12 Zaa kheh letah ning hning batui cahe tei neh ka, ka hmuhpaw vytei taitah chyhraw chykheh ka peh tei,’ tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 13 Canghrasala ngungkhui kheitu cawh langhlaw pui lekhei a daw ka, avai lang hmai a y ngang lytah a cacanghnaw khah a cung ka, ‘Vy Khazing, mehsuapaw kama heh ning pa do ky law,’ a tah.
\p 
\v 14 Ka ca ching he, Farasipaw khah cang lytah ma ngungkhui a kheitupaw khah Khazing hme letah thaicangsah cang tah ing lang a dihpaw cawh a cang. Ahohmai ama le ama a pasangpaw cawh panai cang ka, ama le ama a panaipaw cawh pasang a cang a,” a tah.
\s1 Zisu le nyheh sahlo
\r (Mt 19:13-15; Mk 10:13-16)
\p 
\v 15 Zisu tah tong he seh la, bonghnang song he seh tah du tah hasaitei sahlo khah aa va chua khui he. Ma cawh a hningzuitu sahlo tah hmuh he ka, aa raw he.
\v 16 Canghrasala Zisu tah nyheh sahlo cawh Ama kha y he ka, “Nyheh sahlo cawh Kama khatah a vong he seh, pakhang khe o! Zecawtamaw tatah Khazing painah raang cawh ma hapaw sahlo aa tei khah a cang.
\v 17 Biahmuisui ka ca ching he, Khazing painah raang cawh nyheh hratei a cyhlang lypaw taco a chunglang a nae by a bei he,” a tah.
\s1 Uhtu mehrung
\r (Mt 19:16-30; Mk 10:17-31)
\p 
\v 18 Uhtu a cangpaw pakheh tah Zisu cawh, “Cawngpahtu chaw, chaizaw hringnah ka hmuh khy nápawtah zemaw ka tua a?” tatah a hae.
\p 
\v 19 “Zecawtamaw a chawpaw na pa tah? Khazing tah cy ly co ahohmai achawpaw ung bei he.
\v 20 Biapeh sahlo cawh na hni thlang, ‘A phei kheh, lenong kheh, ru kheh, ahmang lypaw bia hnikhuitu cang kheh, na no le na paw cizaw my lo,’\x + \xo 18:20 \xt Piachua 20:12-16; Biary 5:16-20\x* tahpaw khah,” tatah Zisu tah a chai.
\p 
\v 21 Uhtu paw tah, “Ma vytei heh cawh ka nyheh ning taitah ka zui ciapaw long tei a cang,” a tah.
\p 
\v 22 Ma cawh Zisu tah a thui tihtah a hai leco, “Hming sangkheh naa by ning thlang. Na hnuipaw vytei zua la, mehsisah khah tangka va pei la, vaicung letah chosung na hnui a. Mataico a vong la, pa zui,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 23 Ma bia cawh a thui tihtah a nge a chia ngetei, zecawtamaw tatah ama cawh mehrung a cangnah cawtah a cang.
\v 24 Zisu tah ama cawh ming ka, a hai leco, “Mehrung cai taco Khazing painah raang letah a nae heh cawh a ru caimang!
\v 25 Hmuisui tei co, mehrungpaw tei Khazing painah raang letah a nae navy co, ceiphing kho letah sahisy a nae heh a neh vy a,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 26 Ma bia a thuipaw sahlo taco, “Ma hratei a cang caco ahomaw pachah a cang khy a?” tatah aa hae.
\p 
\v 27 Zisu tah, “Cawngsaw caw tei a cang khy lypaw heh Khazing caw taco a cang khy,” tatah a palei he.
\p 
\v 28 Piter tah a hai leco, “Kaa hnuipaw vytei seisai tah kaa ca zui hi,” a tah.
\p 
\v 29 Zisu tah aa hai leco, “Biahmuisui ka ca ching he, Khazing painah raang cawtah a ing cang seh, a nupui cang seh, a uny sahlo cang he seh, a no le a paw cang he seh, a sawtei leh cang he seh a seisaipaw taco,
\v 30 ato cai letei hmuh ruapaw a leh hlupui aa hmuh hlui tah a va chuh lepaw cai letah chaizaw hringnah zong aa hmuh a,” a tah he.
\s1 Zisu tah a thih nápaw a reihlang vy hui
\r (Mt 20:17-19; Mk 10:32-34)
\p 
\v 31 Zisu tah a hningzuitu hluihning cawh thokhui he ka, ma hrahei a ching he. “Jerusalem khuapui lang seichy he peh ka, Khazing khuavang sahlo tei Cawngsaw Sawcapaw kong aa ciapaw vytei khah a tling a.
\v 32 Ama cawh Gental cawngsaw sahlo kih letah peh a cang a. Aaning taco hnuiso he ka, pasipasa he ka, aa ci tah chawh he ka, basung tah chei a he ka, aa thaw a.
\v 33 Ningthung ning letah a thokaw a,” tatah a tah he.
\p 
\v 34 A hningzuitu sahlo tah ma bia cawh thuithai bingbi bei he. A silang khah nokhai aa cangnah cawtah a reipaw kong cawh zemaw a cang tah hnih bei he.
\s1 Kih a dopaw mehcopaw tah khua a hmuh khy
\r (Mt 20:29-34; Mk 10:46-52)
\p 
\v 35 Zisu cawh Jeriko khua a nae cai lekhei, mehcopaw pakheh cawh kih do pawtah langpui kae letah a ty thlang.
\v 36 Cawngsaw rungpui aa seipaw khah a thui tihtah zehming maw a tlung, tatah a hae he.
\v 37 “Nazaret Zisu a va sei!” tatah aa ching.
\p 
\v 38 Mehcopaw taco, “David Pathlah, Zisu, ning pa do ky law!” tatah a y.
\p 
\v 39 Langhme a chuipaw sahlo taco raw he ka, de law aa tah. Canghrasala ma cawngsawpaw cawh, “David Pathlah, ning pa do ky law!” tatah a y tima.
\p 
\v 40 Zisu cawh a daw ka, ma cawngsawpaw cawh kama khatah a vong khui law, a tah he. A kae a va phah tihtah Zisu taco ma cawngsawpaw cawh,
\v 41 “Na cawtah ze tuapah maw na du?” tatah a hae.
\p “Abuipaw, khuahmuh khy ka du,” tatah a palei.
\p 
\v 42 Zisu taco a hai letah, “Khuahmuh myca, na zingnah tah a ca dangsah thah,” tatah a tah.
\v 43 Ma cangkaw leco, khuahmuh khy ka, Khazing khah reithai ka, Zisu cawh a zui lai. Ma cawh cawngsaw vytei tah aa hmuh tihtah Khazing khah aa reithai hrah.
\c 19
\s1 Ngungkhui kheitupaw Zakia
\p 
\v 1 Zisu cawh Jeriko khua lang a nae ka, khua chung cawh a cahrong.
\v 2 Ma khua leco cawngsaw pakheh a ming Zakia aa tahpaw ung ka, ngungkhui kheitu bui pakheh cang ka, a dong a chah ngetei.
\v 3 Ama taco Zisu cawh ahomaw a cang tahpaw khah hmuh du ngetei ka, canghrasala a ding a nai tunah cawtah cawngsaw rungpui tah pakhang he ka, hmuh khy be.
\v 4 Macawtaco a hmelang va sai ka, Zisu hmuh du taco a va sei nápaw langpui letei saikamur thuiku kung cawh a ke.
\p 
\v 5 Zisu tah ma hminghmaw cawh va phah ka, a kahui ka, a hai leco, “Zakia, rairang tah za cung. Atoning heh na ing letah ka tlung a,” tatah a tah.
\v 6 Mataico rairang tah za cung ka, Zisu cawh a lawng ngetei tah a cyhlang.
\p 
\v 7 Cawngsaw vytei tah ma cawh hmuh he ka, “Mehsuapaw khuatlung cang rua pawtah a sei thlang,” tatah a phing tlungmang he.
\p 
\v 8 Canghrasala, Zakia cawh a daw ka, Abuipaw hai leco, “Mingtua! Abuipaw, ato hrahring heh ka cho a chy cawh mehsisah pei he neh ka, ahohmai ka dungkhei pawhe aa ung caco, a leh pali tah ka chang kaw he a,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 9 Zisu taco a hai letah, “Atoning heh ma ing lehei pachahnah a va tlung myca, zecawtamaw tatah ma cawngsaw zong heh Abraham pathlah a cang hrah.
\v 10 Cawngsaw Sawcapaw cawh a lydepaw sahlo hui rua pawtah le pachá pawtah a vongpaw a cang,” a tah.
\s1 Mina tangka phaehraw tawchingnah
\r (Mt 25:14-30)
\p 
\v 11 Ma bia aa nge leimeining taco tawchingnah bia sangkheh khah a ching vy he. Zecawtamaw tatah Jerusalem khua khah phah daimang tei ca ka, cawngsaw vytei tah Khazing painah raang cawh a va lang palang a tatah aa rawh.
\v 12 Zisu taco, “Abui hring a cangpaw pakheh cawh siangpahrang cangnah lah rua pawtah le va kaw kaw rua pawtah raang langhlaw pui lang a sei.
\v 13 A sei hlai tah a sae pahraw khah y he ka, mina\f + \fr 19:13 \ft Mina tangka phaekheh cawh thlah thung kuli mai khatah a khing.\f* tangka phaehraw khah a peh he. ‘Ka va tlung hlai vytei ma tangka hei cho paleh naw my lo,’ a tah he.
\p 
\v 14 Canghrasala, a khuasaw tah aa huanah cawtah a hninglang tah cawngsaw khah taw he ka, ‘Ma cawngsaw heh kaa siangpahrang rua tah du bei peh,’ tatah aa va chingsah he.
\p 
\v 15 Canghrasala ama cawh siangpahrang tah tua thah he ka, ing lang cawh a va tlung kaw. Mataico tangka a peh sipaw a sae sahlo khah khazeh cy maw a miasah he tah hni du takhei a ysah he.
\p 
\v 16 A pakhehnah cawh a vong ka a hai leco, ‘Abuipaw, na mina tangka khah phaehraw ka miasah,’ tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 17 A buipaw tah, ‘Na tua thai caimang, ka sae chaw! Hming a chia pawtei letah zingchui pawtah na ungnah cawtah hei khuapui khua hraw a uhtu na cang a,’ tatah a palei.
\p 
\v 18 A pahningnah cawh a vong ka, ‘Abuipaw, mina tangka khah phaepangaw ka miasah,’ a tah.
\p 
\v 19 A buipaw taco, ‘Nama zong khuapui khua pangaw a uhtu na cang a,’ a tah.
\p 
\v 20 Mataico, a sae hringpaw a vong ka, ‘Abuipaw, na mina tangka phaekheh cawh ma heh a cang, pai tah pahlong neh ka, achaw teitah ka chia thlang.
\v 21 Nama cawh mehcicia cang ceh ka, ka ca ci. Na chiapaw a cang lypaw zong law ceh ka, na cingpaw a cang lypaw zong na hre tei,’ tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 22 A buipaw taco, ‘Sae chah ly, nama na bia tei hratah bia ka ca cepah a. Kama cawh mehcicia, ka chia lypaw zong law neh ka, ka cing lypaw zong ka hrepaw cawh na hni, cang maw?
\v 23 A cang caco, zecawtamaw ka tangka cawh amia a ungnah letah na chia be? Chia la caw, ka va tlung tihtah a mia ka hmuh a,’ tatah a palei.
\p 
\v 24 Mataico a kae letei a dawpaw sahlo khah, ‘Ma cawngsawpaw a mina tangka heh chu la, mina tangka phaehraw a hnuipaw khah pei o,’ a tah he.
\p 
\v 25 Aaning taco, ‘Abuipaw, ama cawh mina tangka phaehraw a hnui thah!’ aa tah.
\p 
\v 26 Aa hai leco, ‘Ka ca ching he, ahohmai a hnuipaw cawh peh chi vy a cang a. Canghrasala, zehmai a hnui lypaw cawh a hnuitlakangpaw tei hmai khah lah pah a cang a.
\v 27 Macawtaco, aa siangpahrang caw tei a pa du lypaw he le ka carae a cangpaw sahlo khah ma lehei va chua khui la, ka hmekaw lehei thae o,’ tatah a palei he,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Tenah khatah a naenah
\r (Mt 21:1-11; Mk 11:1-11; Jh 12:12-19)
\p 
\v 28 Zisu cawh ma bia a rei khy taico Jerusalem lang sei pawtah hme lang a sei.
\v 29 Oliv tlaang aa tahpaw letei a ungpaw Bethfes le Bethani khua khah aa phah daimang ning tah a hningzuitu pahning khah a seisah hlang he.
\v 30 “Naa hme khua lekhei va sei la, khuachung naa nae tih he ceh tah ahotahmai aa ke bang lypaw la teitei a hrai thlangpaw naa hmuh a. A rui khah thlang he ceh ka, ma lang heh naa va hrui a.
\v 31 Pakheh kheh tah, ‘Zecawtamaw ma a rui khah naa thlang?’ tatah ca tah my he seh la, ‘Abuipaw tah a hia,’ tah my lo,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 32 A taw hlangpaw cawngsaw sahlo cawh va sei he ka, Zisu tei a ching pawtei he hrakhei aa va hmuh.
\v 33 La teitei cawh a rui aa thlang leimeining tah a hnuitupaw sahlo takhei aaning cawh, “Zecawtamaw naa thlang?” tatah aa hae he.
\p 
\v 34 Aaning taco, “Abuipaw tah a hia,” tatah aa palei he.
\p 
\v 35 La teitei cawh Zisu khatah va chuakhui he ka, a kai letah aa pai sahlo dae he ka, Zisu cawh aa kesah.
\v 36 A sei nápaw langpui lekhei cawngsaw taco aa pai sahlo cawh aa phaw.
\p 
\v 37 Oliv tlaang lang tah a za cung chuhpaw langpui kae a va phah tihtah a hninglang tah aa zuipaw ming rungpui cawh aa hmuhpaw ningang chuipaw vytei rawng takhei a lawng ngetei he ka, o thangpui khei Khazing cawh aa reithai.
\q1 
\v 38 “Abuipaw ming tah a vongpaw siangpahrang cawh bonghnang song tah ung ky seh!\x + \xo 19:38 \xt Hlaw 118:26\x*
\q1 Vaicung letah denah ung seh la, Cungnungcai lekhei rungnawnah ung ky seh,” aa tah.
\p 
\v 39 Zawpui hrong letah a ungpaw Farasi thaikheh taco Zisu cawh, “Cawngpahtu, na hningzuitu sahlo heh raw tua o,” tatah aa tah.
\p 
\v 40 Zisu taco, “Ka ca ching he, aaning heh aa de tahmai tah alung sahlo heh a y chua he a,” tatah a palei he.
\p 
\v 41 Jerusalem cawh phah daimang myca he ka, khuapui cawh hmuh ka, a cawkhui.
\v 42 “Ze tamaw denah heh nama khatah a chuakhui a taheh atoning heh hnih tua la, taheh ka du caimang, canghrasala atoheh cawh na hmuh ly rua pawtah nokhai na cang myca.
\v 43 Na carae sahlo tah nama tuh nápawtah raetuhnah ing ca sahso he ka, ca cadung he ka, a kawkih tah a ca dawkhai he ka, khunglai hmai na piathlah khylynah cai a phah tae a.
\v 44 Nama le na hawkaw chung letei a ungpaw sahlo cawh alui letah aa ca nangpabai thlu he a. Khazing nama khatei a vongnah cai khah a hnih lypaw hratah na tuanah cawtah na chung letei alung sangkheh tei hmai palehly lytah aa seisaipaw ung a be,” tatah a tah.
\s1 Behnah ingdung chung letah Zisu
\r (Mt 21:12-17; Mk 11:15-19; Jh 2:13-22)
\p 
\v 45 Mataico Zisu cawh behnah ingdung chunglang a nae ka, hming a zua leimeipaw sahlo khah a tingchua he.
\v 46 Aa hai leco, “Capathai letah ma hrahei cia a cang, ‘Ka ing cawh thlawchangnah ing tah a cang a,’\x + \xo 19:46 \xt Isai 56:7\x* canghrasala naaning taco, ‘Mehru kua,’\x + \xo 19:46 \xt Jere 7:11\x* tah naa tua,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 47 Ning tating tah behnah ing leco cawngpah he ka, canghrasala tlangbui macang sahlo le phungbia cawngpahtu sahlo le zawpui hrong letei hruitu sahlo taco, Ama cawh thaw pawtah khua aa khang leimei thlang.
\v 48 Cawngsaw vytei cawh a bia reipaw khah aa lung a cang tu thah cawtah zekhatamaw kaa tua a, tahpaw khah hnih khy bei he.
\c 20
\s1 Zisu a nawhnuinah aa cakhia
\r (Mt 21:23-27; Mk 11:27-33)
\p 
\v 1 Ning kheh cawh Zisu tah zawpui khah behnah ingdung chung letah cawngpah he ka, thawngchawbia a ching leimeining he takhei, tlangbui macang sahlo le phungbia cawngpahtu sahlo cawh macang sahlo khakhei Ama khatah a vong he ka,
\v 2 “Ze nawhnuinah tamaw ma hming sahlo heh na tua? Ma nawhnuinah heh ahomaw a ca pei? Ma ching tua,” tatah aa tah.
\p 
\v 3 Zisu taco, “Bia sangkheh ka ca hae tua hrá he a.
\v 4 Johan tah baptisma pehnah naw a hnuipaw khah vaicung taitah maw, cawngsaw taitah maw?” tatah a palei he.
\p 
\v 5 Reisia he ka, “ ‘Khazing taitah,’ tah my peh seh la, ‘Zemaw Johan cawh naa zing be?’ a ma tah a.
\v 6 Canghrasala, ‘Cawngsaw taitah,’ tah my peh seh la, zawpuipaw tahei alung tah aa ma vaseh a, zecawtamaw tatah aaning tahei Johan cawh Khazing khuavang a cang tah tlung he ka,” aa tah.
\p 
\v 7 Macawtaco, “Ze taitah maw tahpaw hnih bei peh,” tatah aa chai.
\p 
\v 8 Zisu taco, “Kama zong tah ma hming sahlo heh ze hapaw nawhnuiná tamaw ka tua tahpaw ca ching hrá bei neh,” tatah a tah he.
\s1 Buichung a hlangpaw sahlo tawchingnah
\r (Mt 21:3-46; Mk 12:1-12)
\p 
\v 9 Zisu taco ma tawchingnah bia heh zawpuipaw khah a ching he. “Cawngsawpaw tah misur buichung tua ka, male khah hlei he ka, a sypui ry pawtah khua a tlong.
\v 10 Hre cai a cang tihtah a sae pakheh khah ama a ting hangpaw pakhong pawtah ly a hlangpaw sahlo khaco a taw. Canghrasala ly a hlangpaw sahlo taco a sae cawh dai he ka, kih longpaw tah aa kawsah kaw.
\v 11 A sae hringpaw khah taw kaw ka, canghrasala ma paw zong cawh dai he ka, ningzaw chuipaw tah tua he ka, zehmai peh lytah aa kawsah hrah.
\v 12 A pathungnah a va taw vy tihtah ma paw zong cawh hmaw phosah he ka, khungthing lang aa vathlang.
\p 
\v 13 Mataico misur buichung a hnuitupaw taco, ‘Zekhatamaw ka tua a? Ka dopaw ka sawcapaw heh ka taw a. Ama heh cawh aa cizaw phung thlang pui ta,’ a tah.
\p 
\v 14 Canghrasala ly a hlangpaw sahlo taco ama cawh aa hmuh tihtah, ‘Ma cawngsaw heh ry cytu a cang, thé he peh ka, a ry a lah ná peh seh,’ aa tah.
\v 15 Macawtaco ama cawh misur buichung alailang khah piakhui he ka, aa thaw.
\p Ma tih taco misur buichung a hnuitupaw takhei aaning sahlo cawh zekhatamaw a tua he a?
\v 16 Va seí ka, ly a hlangpaw sahlo khah thé he ka, misur buichung khah ahringpaw khah a hlei he a,” a tah he.
\p Ma bia cawh zawpui tah aa thui tihtah, “Ma hraco cang thai by be!” aa tah.
\p 
\v 17 Zisu tah aaning cawh mingpai he ka, “A cang caco, Capathai letei aa ciapaw heh zemaw a silang a cang?
\q1 ‘Ing a sahtu sahlo tei aa hlawhpaw alung cawh,
\q2 a biapui caipaw alung tah a cang,’\x + \xo 20:17 \xt Hlaw 118:22\x*
\m tahpaw heh.
\v 18 Ahohmai ma alung cung letei a tlahpaw cawngsaw cawh kuichy thlu he ka, ma alung tei a tlahsopaw cawngsaw heh cawh a mang cici he a,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 19 Phungbia cawngpahtu sahlo le tlangbui macang sahlo tah ma tawchingnah bia a reipaw cawh aaning a rei hnopaw he a cang takhah hnih he ka, Ama tle nápaw langpui khah aa hui. Canghrasala zawpui khah aa ci he.
\s1 Sizar kha ngungkhui pehnah
\r (Mt 22:15-22; Mk 12:13-17)
\p 
\v 20 Zisu cawh tai lytah ngia thlang he ka, mehding hratah a tua pakheipaw he cawngsaw a ngiatu sahlo khah aa taw he. Rom raang uhtu bui a hmingtuakhynah le a nawhnuinah chung letah Zisu khah aa hlai khy nápaw cawtah a reipaw bia khei Zisu khah tle pawtah a pachia he.
\v 21 Macawtaco male a ngialaipaw sahlo tah Zisu cawh, “Cawngpahtu na reipaw le na cawngpahnah heh ahmangpaw cang ka, aho hme hmai ming lytah Khazing langpui khah biahmuisui a cang naning teitah na cawngpah he tahpaw kaa hni.
\v 22 Macawtaco kaa cawtah Sizar letah ngungkhui peh heh ahmang maw hmang ly?” tatah aa tah.
\p 
\v 23 Zisu tah a zia aa thaipaw khah hnih ka, aa hai leco,
\v 24 “Denari tangka phae pa hmusah tua o. Aho lingthlaw le cakhai maw a cia?” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 25 Aaning taco, “Sizar a lingthlaw le cakhai,” tatah aa palei.
\p Zisu taco aa hai letah, “Sizar a tei cawh Sizar pei la, Khazing a tei cawh Khazing pei my lo,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 26 Ma zawpui hme letei a reipaw bia lekhei a suanah cawh tle khy bei he. Taico a biachainah khah aa ningang ka, a de thlang he.
\s1 Thokawnah le a chuihaenah
\r (Mt 22:23-33; Mk 12:18-27)
\p 
\v 27 Mehthi thokawnah ung be a tahpaw Sadusi thaikheh cawh Zisu kha a vong he ka bia aa hae.
\v 28 “Cawngpahtu, Moses phungbia letah cawngsawpaw cawh sawtei sah lytah a nupui a thih sai caco, a unypaw takhei lahmeno cawh nupui tah chui kaw seh la, a thipaw caw takhei sawtei sah pápaw a cang, a tah.
\v 29 Uikheh cawh uny pasarih a ung he. A uthui caipaw tah nupui chui ka, sawtei sah lytah a thi.
\v 30 Mataico, a pahningnahpaw tah lahmeno cawh chui kaw ka, a thih sai hui.
\v 31 A uny a pathungnah a cangpaw taco chui vy ka, a thih sai hrah. Aa pasarih co, ma canuno cawh chui cy he ka, sawteisah lytah a thi thlu he.
\v 32 A hning cai tah ma canuno zong cawh a thi hrah.
\v 33 Macawtaco thokawnah letah ma canuno cawh aho a nupui maw a cang a? Aa pasarih tah ma canuno khah aa chui tlung,” aa tah.
\p 
\v 34 Zisu taco, “Khazaw cawngsaw heh aa chui aa hae he.
\v 35 Canghrasala, mehthi sahlo patho kaw a cang tihtah ma cai letei a ung tlang pawtei rawhpaw cawngsaw sahlo aa cai leco a chuihae cawh ung khaw a be.
\v 36 Vaiming hratah cang he ka, thi khy khaw bei he. A thokawpaw sawtei sahlo aa cangnah cawtah aaning cawh Khazing sawtei a cang myca he.
\v 37 Canghrasala chingbu me tei a kangpaw phungpaw lekhei Moses tahmai tah mehthi sahlo aa thokawpaw khah palang ka, Abuipaw cawh ‘Abraham Khazing, Isak Khazing, Jakob Khazing’\x + \xo 20:37 \xt Piachua 3:6\x* a cang a tah.
\v 38 Ama cawh mehthi aa Khazing cang be, canghrasala mehring aa Khazing a cang. Zemaw tah pawco ma cawngsaw vytei cawh Khazing mehmuh letaco a hring he,” tatah a palei he.
\p 
\v 39 Phungbia cawngpahtu thaikheh tah, “Cawngpahtu, bia na paleipaw he a chah caimang,” tatah aa chai.
\v 40 Taico ahotahmai bia hringpaw hae ngang khawh bei he.
\s1 Khri cawh aho sawcapaw maw?
\r (Mt 22:41—23:36; Mk 12:35-40)
\p 
\v 41 Taico, Zisu tah aa hai leco, “Ze silang tamaw Khri cawh David pathlah aa tah?
\v 42-43 David ama ceingei tei a reipaw cawh,
\q1 ‘Abuipaw tah ka Buipaw cawh,
\q2 na carae sahlo khah na phe rai letah
\q1 ka chia hlai vytei he cawh,
\q2 ka cacang lang letah a ty my lo a tah,’\x + \xo 20:42-43 \xt Hlaw 110:1\x*
\m tatah a tahpaw khah Reithainah Hlaw cabu letah a cia.
\v 44 David tah Khri cawh, ‘Abuipaw,’ a tah tlung, zekhatamaw David a sawcapaw cawh a cang thai a?” a tah he.
\p 
\v 45 Zawpuipaw tah aa nge thlang chung takhei Zisu tah a hningzuitu sahlo cawh,
\v 46 “Phungbia cawngpahtu sahlo khah a raering my lo. Aaning cawh a ngepaw angki a pasuapaw a hrei tah a khia lai du he ka, chodo tlaang lekhei cizaw hmotah bia a ching khah aa du hlui tah synagog letah a chaw caipaw dyching letah a ty du he ka, kawngchuanah letah achaw caipaw hminghmaw khah aa du.
\v 47 Lahme sahlo aa ing khah chu he ka, male hmuh ruapaw tah thlaw a sypui tah aa chang. Ma hapaw cawngsaw sahlo cawh a sah caipaw dangtahnah aa ing tae a,” tatah a tah he.
\c 21
\s1 Lahmeno a tholong
\r (Mk 12:41-44)
\p 
\v 1 Zisu cawh a kahui ka, mehrung sahlo tei behnah ing tholong thingkawng chunglang aa tholong aa thlah leimeipaw khah a hmuh.
\v 2 Mehsisah lahmeno tei phaesai phaehning a thlah hrahpaw zong khah a hmuh.
\v 3 “Biahmuisui ka ca ching he, ma mehsisah lahmeno tahei aho navy zong tah a hlu cai tholong a thlah.
\v 4 Ma sahlo vytei tahei co aa hnuipaw a hluipaipaw chung taikhei aa peh. Canghrasala ma lahmeno tahei co a dongchia hmo tah a hringnah caw tei a hnuipaw vytei a peh thlu hi,” a tah he.
\s1 Cai le ning changnah paching pakhanah
\r (Mt 24:1-35; Mk 13:1-31)
\p 
\v 5 A hningzuitu thaikheh taco behnah ing khah a hmui a ngepaw alung sahlo tah le Khazing letei hlaipaw cho le pe sahlo tei aa pasangpaw kong cawh aa rei leimei. Canghrasala Zisu tah,
\v 6 “Ma lehei naa hmuhpaw vytei he alung phaekheh hmai heh palehly lypaw a ung lynah cai a va chuh tae a. Aa zongmingtei hei va hly thlu a cang tae he a,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 7 Aaning sahlo taco, “Cawngpahtu, ma hming sahlo cawh zening tamaw a cang a? Taico ze hapaw paching pakhanah maw a ung a?” tatah aa hae.
\p 
\v 8 Zisu taco, “Aho tahmai aa ca dungkhei ly nápaw he tah a raering my lo. Ka ming tah cawngsaw hlupui va chua he ka, ‘Kama heh Ama cawh ka cang, cai a ne myca,’ aa tah tae a. Ma sahlo cawh zui khe lo.
\v 9 Raetuhnah le raang chung letah rae a dynah thongpang naa thui tihtah a pahly khe lo. Ma hming sahlo heh a tlung taw ruapaw a cang, canghrasala a changnah cang balang be,” tatah a palei he.
\p 
\v 10 Mataico aa hai letah, “Raang kheh le raang kheh a dy a he ka, painah le painah a dy he a.
\v 11 Aling a sah pui tah a hrui a, hming hlupui letah cakaang le ngae-y asawnah a tlung a. Mataico, cichuipaw hming sahlo le paching pakhanah a rungnawpaw sahlo avai taitah a lang a.
\p 
\v 12 Canghrasala, ma vytei hlai tahei ca tle he ka, aa ca hrai he a. Synagog sahlo lang ca seikhui he ka, thong aa ca thla he a. Siangpahrang sahlo le uhtubui sahlo hme letah ca chuakhui he ka, ma vytei heh naa pa zuinah rawng tah a cang a.
\v 13 Ma heh naa cawtah ka kong reinah caichaw a cang a.
\v 14 Naaning a rungvai nápaw cawtah zekhatamaw bia kaa rei a tatah lung reithui tah naa ung ly nápawtah naa thinglung a pacy pacia my lo.
\v 15 Naa carae ahohmai tah aa ca te khy ly nápaw he tah le aa ca ei khy ly nápaw he tah bia sahlo le singnah ka ca pae he a.
\v 16 Naa no sahlo le naa paw sahlo, naa uny sahlo, naa sawny sahlo le naa huivesaw sahlo tahmai tah ca luithae a he ka, meh thaikheh cawh aa ca thaw he a.
\v 17 Kama ka rawng tah cawngsaw vytei tah aa ca hua he a.
\v 18 Canghrasala, naa lu cung letei sangbu bukheh hmai lyde a be.
\v 19 Cy ky tah a daw la, hringnah naa cy a.
\p 
\v 20 Raekeh sahlo tah Jerusalem khuapui aa cadungpaw naa hmuh tihtah a ry hlai tah a rawh a, tah cawh naa hni a.
\v 21 Mataico Judia raang letei a ungpaw cawngsaw sahlo cawh tlaang cung lang sai he seh la, khuapui leteipaw sahlo cawh pia he seh. Taico khuapui alailang leteipaw sahlo cawh khuapui chunglang a nae kheh he seh.
\v 22 Ma heh cawh dangtah nápaw cai, Khazing bia letei a ciasipaw vytei a tling nápaw khah a cang.
\v 23 Ma ning cawh sawtei a phopaw canu sahlo le nysai a tlepaw no sahlo aa caw taco zetlua tamaw ningping a chui a! Raang chung letah rorangnah alaipaw pui tlung ka, Khazing thingaenah tah ma mingphing heh a carae he a.
\v 24 Aaning cawh zyzi tah thaw cang he ka, thaikheh cawh raang ting letah sae tah seikhui a cang he a. Khazing tah Gental cawngsaw sahlo cawtah a pachiapaw cai a tlingnah tai Jerusalem cawh Gental cawngsaw sahlo taco aa phe tah aa tlaichai a.
\p 
\v 25 Ning, thlawpaw le esi sahlo letah paching pakhanah a ung he a. Rili tuileh a thopaw le a pyraw rawng tah aluicung raang sahlo cawh thlawzawng le ningping tah a ung he a.
\v 26 Khazaw letei hming a va tlung lepaw khah aa hninah cawtah le avai hmingtuakhynah sahlo zong cahneh aa cang a cawtah mehnung cawh ci tu he ka, a cathing he a.
\v 27 Ma cai leco aaning tah Cawngsaw Sawcapaw khah hmingtuakhynah le rungnawnah khatah meding hrong letah a vongpaw khah aa hmuh a.
\v 28 Ma hming sahlo cang hrang a pathoning tahei a daw la, a huichy my lo, zecawtamaw tatah naaning tlang nápaw cai cawh a ne myca,” tatah a tah he.
\p 
\v 29 Ma khy taico Zisu tah aaning cawh ma tawchingnah bia heh a ching he. “Ma thuiku kung le thingkung ahringpaw vytei sahlo heh mingtua hmai o!
\v 30 A chawng a ka thopaw naa hmuh tihtah nipui ning a ne myca tahpaw naa hni.
\v 31 Ma hraco ma hming sahlo heh a cang leimeipaw naa hmuh tihtah Khazing painah raang cawh a ne myca tah hnih my lo.
\p 
\v 32 Biahmuisui ka ca ching he, ma hming vytei heh a tlung hlai vytei cawh atochai cawngsaw sahlo heh thi thlu balang bei he.
\v 33 Alui le avai cawh a rawh a, canghrasala ka bia cawh a rawh by a be.
\p 
\v 34 A raering my lo, ma tei a cang ly caco a nawngsenah, zu ruinah le tungtuh khuasahnah lungreithuinah takhei ca nai a he ka, ma ning takhei ahui hratah rawh ly pui tah a ca o pang he a.
\v 35 Ma ning cawh aluicung pungpaluh letei a ungpaw cawngsaw vytei cung letah a tlung a.
\v 36 A va chuh lepaw vytei taitah naa lua khy nápawtah le Cawngsaw Sawcapaw hme letah na daw pacy khy nápaw he ceh tah a mai pacia tah ung paria thlang la, thlawchang my lo,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 37 Ning tating tah Zisu taco behnah ing letah cawngpah he ka, zailang maikaw cawh Oliv tlaang aa tahpaw letah zai hmang rua pawtah a piathlah tei.
\v 38 Taico ming vytei cawh a bia nge rua pawtah mongdi tah behnah ing leco a va chuh tei he.
\c 22
\s1 Zisu lui rua pawtah Judas Iskariot a naw a tlah
\r (Mt 26:1-5, 14-16; Mk 14:1-2, 10-11; Jh 11:45-53)
\p 
\v 1 Raangri phi lypaw Very Panawnah le Khungsai Panawnah aa tahpaw a ne myca ka,
\v 2 tlangbui macang sahlo le phungbia cawngpahtu sahlo tah Zisu thaw khy nápaw lang le si khah aparuh teitah aa hui, zecawtamaw tatah zawpuipaw khah aa ci he.
\v 3 Mataico, a hningzuitu hluihning letei pakheh a cangpaw Iskariot aa tahpaw Judas chung letah Setan cawh a nae.
\v 4 Taico Judas cawh tlangbui macang sahlo le behnah ing a mingkaitu abui sahlo khatah sei ka, zekhatamaw Zisu a luithae a tahpaw kong khah aa reisia.
\v 5 Aa thawchah ngetei ka, tangka peh rua pawtah aa naw a tlah.
\v 6 Judas zong cawh a lungtling ka, zawpui aa ung ly kaa tah aa kih letah Zisu hlai khy nápaw caichaw khah a haw thlang.
\s1 Zairia a hningcaipaw
\r (Mt 26:17-35; Mk 14:12-31; Jh 13:21-30)
\p 
\v 7 Mataico Khungsai Panawnah cawtah tuu teitei tah thuihlainah ning a cangpaw raangri phi lypaw Very Panawnah ning cawh a va phah.
\v 8 Zisu tah Piter le Johan cawh taw he ka, “Sei la, kaa cawtah Khungsai Panawnah zairia enah cawh va pachia tua o,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 9 Aaning taco, “Zeletamaw va pachia he seh tah na du?” tatah hae he ka,
\v 10 Zisu taco, “Khuapui chung a va nae la, beirai tah tui a cui laipaw capaw pakheh tah a ca tong he a. Ama a naenah ing lang va zui he ceh ka,
\v 11 ing a hnuitupaw khah, ‘Cawngpahtu tah ka hningzuitu sahlo khatah Khungsai Panawnah zairia ka e nápaw mehlai khang zeletamaw a ung, a tah,’ tatah naa hae a.
\v 12 Ama taco a cung khang a kypaw pui, tingtua cia tei a cangpaw khah a ca hmuh sá he a. Ma leco va pachia my lo,” tatah a palei he.
\p 
\v 13 Piter le Johan cawh seithlah he ka, Zisu tah a chingpaw he hrakhei hming sahlo cawh aa va hmuh. Ma leco Khungsai Panawnah zairia cawh aa pachia.
\p 
\v 14 A cai a va tling tihtah Zisu le Ama apostol sahlo taco cabuai cawh aa cadung.
\v 15 Taico Zisu tah aa hai letah, “Kama cawh ruhanah ka ing hlai tahei naaning khatah ma Khungsai Panawnah zairia e hrui heh ka du ngetei.
\v 16 Macawtaco ka ca ching he, Khazing painah raang letah ma Khungsai Panawnah tlingnah cai a tlung hlai vytei ma zaibatui heh e kaw khaw bei neh,” tatah a tah he.
\p 
\v 17 Taico ny khah law ka, Khazing letah alawngnah bia hlai ka, “Ma misurhang ny heh law la, a hlai pachaw my lo.
\v 18 Ka ca ching he, Khazing painah raang a va chuanah tai ma misurhang heh ding kaw khaw bei neh,” tatah a tah he.
\p 
\v 19 Taico very cawh law ka, Khazing khatah lawngbia a hlai khy taitah kychy ka, aaning cawh pei he ka, “Ma heh naa cawtah ka pehpaw ka pung cawh a cang hi. Kama monghly ly nápawtah tua tei my lo,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 20 Ma hraco zairia aa e khy taitah ny cawh law ka, “Ma ny heh naa caw tei a laipaw, ka thisai tei tuapaw biahrai thapaw cawh a cang.
\v 21 Kama a pa lui a paw cawngsawpaw cawh ma lehei kama khatah cabuai letah a ung.
\v 22 Cawngsaw Sawcapaw cawh Khazing bia thlia ciapaw hratah a thi a. Ma duitei cawh Ama a luipaw cawngsaw cawh a cing a ping,” tatah a tah he.
\v 23 Aaning le aaning cawh ahomaw ma hming heh a tua a, tatah aa hae he.
\p 
\v 24 Aaning hrong letah ahomaw alaicai a, tahpaw bia a einah zong khah aa hrong letah a chuh.
\v 25 Zisu taco aa hai letah, “Gental cawngsaw sahlo cung letei abui sahlo cawh a buisah ngetei he ka, aa nawhnuinah aa hmangpaw cawh, ‘A ca bawngtu ka cang he peh,’ tatah aaning le aaning a tah he.
\v 26 Canghrasala naaning cawh aaning hratah ung khe lo! Naa hrong letei alaicaipaw cawh a chia caipaw hratah ung hri seh la, uhtu a cangpaw taco sae hratah ung hri seh.
\v 27 Ahomaw alai vy? Cabuai letei a typaw maw batui a peitu maw? Cabuai letei a typaw cawh lai vy bei maw? Canghrasala kama cawh male rai hrepah tu pakheh hratah naa hrong letah ka ung hi.
\v 28 Naaning cawh hanah ka ingpaw vytei letah a pa dawkhuitu na cang he ceh.
\v 29 Taico ka paw tah painah raang a pa pehpaw hratah naaning khah ca pei hrá he neh ka,
\v 30 macawtaco ka painah raang letei ka cabuai letah e he ceh ka, naa ding a. Abui dyching letah a ty he ceh ka, Israel phinghraw hluihning khah bia naa ce he a.
\p 
\v 31 Simon, Simon, lythlopaw tah sacang a vangpaw hratah Setan tah naaning khah hnehsah a pawtah nawhnuinah hmuh a du my ca.
\v 32 Canghrasala Simon, na zingnah cawh a po ly nápawtah na cawtah thlaw ka chang thah. Taico kama lang na va hui kaw tihtah na uny sahlo khah thawzaang pei my lo,” a tah.
\p 
\v 33 Canghrasala Piter taco, “Abuipaw, nama khatah thongtlá tah thihnah tai ka mai thlang,” tatah a palei.
\p 
\v 34 Zisu taco, “Ka ca ching, Piter, atoning aa a khawng hlai tahei na pa hninah lehei uithung tai na pa paphahsai a,” tatah a chai.
\p 
\v 35 Mataico, Zisu tah a hningzuitu sahlo cawh, “Tangka ly, sahre lytah le phepakong lytah ka ca taw tih he tah ze na phahlahnah he ceh a ung maw?” tatah a hae he.
\p Aaning sahlo taco, “Ung be,” tatah aa tah.
\p 
\v 36 Zisu tah aa hai leco, “Canghrasala atoheh cawh tangka naa hnui caco a kai la, sahre zong a kai la, taico zyzi naa hnui ly caco naa angki pasuapaw khah zua la, co my lo.
\v 37 Ma hrahei Capathai letah ciapaw a cang, ‘Taico ama cawh hmingsua a tuapaw sahlo khatah reipai a cang a.’\x + \xo 22:37 \xt Isai 53:12\x* Ma heh kama letah a tling ruapaw a cang tah ka ca ching he. A cang, ka kong a ciapaw heh a tlingnah cai a phah leimei myca,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 38 A hningzuitu sahlo taco, “Abuipaw, mingtua, zyzi sanghning a ung thlang hi,” tatah aa tah.
\p Zisu taco, “A zaw seh,” tatah a palei he.
\s1 Oliv Tlaang letah Zisu thlaw a chang
\r (Mt 26:36-46; Mk 14:32-42)
\p 
\v 39 Zisu cawh a tua teipaw hrakhei Oliv tlaang lang cawh sei ka, a hningzuitu sahlo tah Ama cawh aa zui.
\v 40 A hminghmaw cawh aa phah tihtah aa hai leco, “Tuhsonah chung lang naa tlah ly nápawtah thlawchang my lo,” a tah he.
\v 41 Ama cawh aaning khah a cawngpe va long he ka, a khuh panai ka, thlaw a chang.
\v 42 “Vy Ka paw, na naw a tlah pawtei a cang caco ma tai-ingnah ny heh kama taitah law hly thlang. Canghrasala kama ka dunah hratah cang lytah nama na dunah hratah cang ky seh,” a tah.
\v 43 Vaicung taitah vaiming pakheh cawh ama kha a za paly ka, thawzaang a peh.
\v 44 Taico a lung rei a thui tunah cawtah khei lungsaw chingching tah thlawchang vy hui ka, a mathlai cawh thi di hratah alui letah a tlah.
\p 
\v 45 A thlawchangnah taitah tho ka, a hningzuitu sahlo khakhei a vaw kaw tihtah aa ihningpaw khah hmuh ka, ngechia tah aa ung cawtah aa thaw a chang.
\v 46 “Zemaw naa ihning thlang? Tho la, tuhsonah chunglang naa tlah ly nápawtah thlawchang my lo,” tatah aaning cawh a tah he.
\s1 Zisu aa tle
\r (Mt 26:47-56; Mk 14:43-50; Jh 18:3-11)
\p 
\v 47 Ma hratei a rei leimeining taco cawngsaw rungpui va chuh he ka, aaning sahlo cawh a hningzuitu hluihning letei pakheh a cangpaw Judas aa tahpaw takhei a va seikhui he. Zisu cawh hnang rua pawtah khei a va ne.
\v 48 Canghrasala Zisu tah ama cawh, “Judas, Cawngsaw Sawcapaw heh hnang ceh ka maw, na luithae a?” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 49 Zisu a hningzuitu sahlo tah, hming a cang leimeipaw khah aa hmuh tihtah, “Abuipaw, kaa zyzi hei kaa tuh a he maw?” tatah aa tah.
\v 50 Taico aa hrong letei pakhehpaw tah tlangbui alaicaipaw a sae capaw khah tuh ka, a cacang lang tei a naw khah a pathai thlah.
\p 
\v 51 Canghrasala Zisu tah, “Ma khah a zaw myca,” tatah a tah. Taico cawngsawpaw a naw khah tong ka, a dangsah.
\p 
\v 52 Mataico Zisu tah Ama a va seihnopaw tlangbui macang sahlo le behnah ing a congpaw sahlo aa bui sahlo le macang sahlo he khah, “Zyzi le thingtai kha naa va seipaw heh kama cawh rae a thopaw he hotu tamaw ka cang?
\v 53 Ning tating tah naaning kha behnah ing letah ung tei neh ka, ka cung letah naa kih naa thlah tlung be. Canghrasala ato cai heh cawh muinah tei a uhpaw naaning naa cai a cang,” a tah he.
\s1 Piter tah Zisu a paphah sai
\r (Mt 26:57-58, 67-75; Mk 14:53-54, 66-72; Jh 18:12-18, 25-27)
\p 
\v 54 Mataico Zisu cawh tle he ka, seikhui longmang he ka, tlangbui alaicaipaw a ing chunglang taikhah a naekhui he. Piter tah langhlaw pui khei a zuilai.
\v 55 Canghrasala inghme a le lekhei me tua he ka, me a ai tah a ty cadungnah pawhe lekhei Piter cawh aaning sahlo khakhei hmingkheh tah a ty hrah.
\v 56 Saecanu pakheh tah Piter ma letei a typaw khah a hmuh. Ma no taco ama cawh va mingchai ka, “Ma cawngsawpaw heh Zisu kha a ungpaw a cang,” a tah.
\p 
\v 57 Canghrasala ma cawh a paphah ka, “Cawngsawno, Ama heh hnih bei neh,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 58 A cawngpe ung ka pakhehpaw tah Ama cawh hmuh ka, “Nama zong aa hrong letei pakheh na cang,” a tah.
\p Piter taco, “Cang bei neh,” tatah a palei.
\p 
\v 59 Suimehlang pakheh tluh lekhei ahringpaw pakheh tah, “Ma cawngsawpaw heh Galili cawngsaw a cangnah cawtah hei Zisu kha a ungpaw a cang hrahring,” a tah.
\p 
\v 60 Piter taco, “Na rei leimeipaw kong heh hnih bei neh,” tatah a palei. Ma hratei a tah leimeining taco aa cawh a khawng.
\v 61 Abuipaw cawh Piter lang cawh a hui ka, a va ming. Taico Piter cawh Abuipaw tei a hai letei a reipaw, “Atoning heh aa a khawng hlai tah uithung na pa paphah sai a,” a tahpaw khah a thui kaw.
\v 62 Taico alailang piathlah ka, o tlili tah a cah.
\s1 Raevai sahlo tah Zisu aa pasi aa pasa
\p 
\v 63 Zisu cawh a congpaw raevai sahlo takhei pasipasa he ka, aa cabai.
\v 64 Aaning sahlo taco a meh pamai he ka, “Ma ching tua, nama Khazing khuavang! Ahomaw a ca tuh?” aa tah.
\v 65 Taico ma sahlo taco Ama cawh aisainah bia a hlupui tah aa tah.
\s1 Pilat le Herod aa hme letah Zisu
\r (Mt 26:59—27:2, 11-26; Mk 14:55-15:15; Jh 18:19-19:16)
\p 
\v 66 Khua hme a se cangkawleh biacetu macang a cangpaw sahlo cawh tlangbui macang sahlo le phungbia cawngpahtu sahlo khakhei hmingkheh tah a tong he ka, Zisu cawh aa hme lekhei aa va chuakhui.
\v 67 “Khri cawh na cang maw? Ma ching tua,” aa tah.
\p Zisu tah, “Ka ca ching zong he tah pa zing bei ceh.
\v 68 Ka ca hae zong he tah pachai bei ceh.
\v 69 Canghrasala ma taihei co, Cawngsaw Sawcapaw heh Cungnungcai Khazing a cacang lang letah a ty myca a,” tatah a chai he.
\p 
\v 70 Aa zongmingtei co, “Khazing Sawcapaw cawh na cang maw?” tatah aa hae.
\p Zisu taco, “Khazing Sawcapaw na cang tatei naa reipaw cawh ahmang,” tatah a palei he.
\p 
\v 71 Mataico aaning taco, “Ze hringpaw biahninah maw kaa hia khawh? Ama a hmo taitah ma bia kaa thui thah taico,” tatah aa tah.
\c 23
\p 
\v 1 Mataico a pahmopaw vytei cawh tho he ka, Zisu cawh raang uhbui Pilat khatah aa seikhui.
\v 2 Taico, Ama cawh sua pu he ka, “Ma paw tahei kaa mingphing a pingpaly tah a hruipaw he kaa hmuh. Ama tahei Sizar khatah ngungkhui pei khe law tah ka, Khri a cangpaw siangpahrang ka cang a tah,” tatah aa tah.
\p 
\v 3 Macawtaco Pilat tah Zisu cawh, “Juda cawngsaw aa siangpahrang cawh na cang maw?” tatah a hae.
\p “A cang, na reipaw hraco a cang,” tatah Zisu tah a palei.
\p 
\v 4 Mataico, Pilat tah tlangbui macang sahlo le zawpuipaw cawh, “Ma paw sua pho rua pawtah hei a chahlynah zehmai hmuh bei neh,” tatah a thang he.
\p 
\v 5 Canghrasala aaning sahlo taco, “Ama tahei Judia raang pungpaluh letei cawngsaw sahlo cawh a cawngpah ná tah hnahnawhnah a chuasah. Galili taitah a patho ka, ma tai heh a va phahpaw a cang,” tatah thaw tah aa rei.
\p 
\v 6 Ma cawh a thui tihtah Pilat taco, “Ma paw heh Galili cawngsaw maw a cang?” a tah he.
\v 7 Zisu cawh Herod a uhnah rai letei a ungpaw Galili raang cawngsaw a cang tahpaw khah Pilat tah a hni tihtah ma ningcai letei Jerusalem letah a ung thlangpaw Herod khakhei a seisah khui he.
\p 
\v 8 Herod tah Zisu a hmuh tihtah a lung a lawng ngetei, zecawtamaw tatah cai sypui hmuh a za du ngetei cawtah a cang. Zisu a thong khah a za thui teinah cawtah ningang chuipaw hming sahlo a tuapaw khah ka hmuh myca a, tatah a hnabei a sui.
\v 9 Bia a hlupui hae cakhia ka, canghrasala Zisu tah zehmai chai be.
\v 10 Tlangbui macang le phungbia cawngpahtu sahlo cawh ma leco a daw thlang hrah he ka, Zisu cawh a sah pui tah sua aa pu leimei.
\v 11 Mataico, Herod le a raekeh sahlo tah Zisu cawh hnuiso he ka, aa pasi aa pasa. Pai achaw ngeteipaw a buhsah he ka, Pilat khatah aa seisah kaw.
\v 12 Ma ning taico Pilat le Herod cawh huivesaw a cang he. Ma hlai taco a za carae tei he.
\p 
\v 13 Pilat tah tlangbui macang sahlo le uhtu sahlo le zawpuipaw khah y pahmo he ka,
\v 14 aa hai letah, “Ma paw heh zawpui khah carae tah a thosah he tatei kama kha naa va chuakhuipaw khah a cang. Ama heh naa hmekaw letah haecakhia neh ka, reipachia tei sua naa pupaw heh a dongkhang be tatah ka hmuh.
\v 15 Herod zong tah, a suanah hmuh be ca ka, kaaning kha a va ma kua kawpaw a cang. Naa hmuh thlangpaw hratah thih tlang a tlahpaw hming zehmai tua be.
\v 16 Macawtaco chei sá he neh ka, mataico ka thlaw a,” tatah a tah he.
\v 17 Khungsai Panawnah ning maikaw letah Pilat tah thong a tlahpaw chung taitah pakheh khah a thlaw hrahring ruapaw a cang.\f + \fr 23:17 \ft Kih cia thaikheh leco cai 17 heh ung be.\f*
\p 
\v 18 Zawpui sahlo cawh hmokheh tah y hrui he ka, “Ama cawh theh thlang la, Baraba khah ma thlawpah hri,” tatah aa tah.
\v 19 Baraba cawh khuapui chung letah rae a tho sahpaw a cang rawng tah le lee a nongpaw rawng tah thong a tlahpaw a cang.
\p 
\v 20 Pilat tah Zisu cawh thlaw a dunah cawtah khei aaning cawh a hae hry he.
\v 21 Canghrasala aaning taco, “Khraws letah khaipai! Khraws letah khaipai!” tatah a y vy tima he.
\p 
\v 22 A uithungnah leco aaning cawh, “Ze rawng tamaw? Ma paw tahei ze suanah ky maw a tua? Thihnah tai dangtá pawtah a panah zehmai hmuh bei neh. Macawtaco chei sá he neh ka, ka thlaw a,” tatah a tah he.
\p 
\v 23 Canghrasala, Ama cawh khraws letah khaipai tatah tai lytah a thangpui tah y he ka, aa ypaw takhei Pilat khah a pahnei.
\v 24 Macawtaco Pilat tah aa haepaw khah peh a pawtah bia a chaw.
\v 25 Pilat taco hnahnawhnah le lenongnah rawng tei thong a tlahpaw, aa haepaw Baraba khah thlaw ka, aa dunah hrakhei tua rua pawtah Zisu cawh a hlai he.
\s1 Zisu cawh khraws letah aa khaipai
\r (Mt 27:31-44; Mk 15:21-32; Jh 19:17-27)
\p 
\v 26 Zisu cawh raekeh sahlo tah seikhui he ka, langpui letah khuatei lang tah khua a va tlongpaw Sairin khuapaw Simon khah tle he ka, khraws cawh a cung lekhei khing he ka, Zisu hninglang khei aa puhsah lai.
\v 27 Cawngsaw a rungpui takhei pazui he ka, a cawtah a ngechia katei, a cahpaw canu sahlo zong a ung hrah he.
\v 28 Zisu tah a paleh ka aa hai leco, “Jerusalem sawcanu sahlo pa cawkhui khe o, naaning naa cawtah le naa sawtei leh cawtah cah hri my lo,
\v 29 zemaw tah pawco, ‘A cingpaw canu sahlo, sawtei a pho bang lypaw chi le meimei zai bang lypaw hnabae sahlo cawh bonghnang a tingpaw a cang he,’ tatah naa tah nápaw cai a va chuh a!
\v 30 Mataico,
\q1 ‘aaning sahlo tah tlaang sahlo cawh, “Ma tlahso law,” tah he ka,
\q2 tlangby sahlo khah, “Ma vuh law,”\x + \xo 23:30 \xt Hose 10:8\x* aa tah he a.’
\m 
\v 31 Ma hming sahlo heh cawngsaw tah thingkung a hring thlang ningtah hmai aa tua caco, thingkung a ro tihtah co zemaw aa tua chichi a?” a tah he.
\p 
\v 32 Ahringpaw cawngsaw pahning, mehsua va vei khah Zisu khatah thaw hrui rua pawtah aa seikhui hrah he.
\v 33 Luru hming aa tahpaw hminghmaw aa va phah tih taco, ma leco Ama cawh damia sahlo khakhei pakheh khah a cacang lang letah pakheh khah a cavui lang letah aa khaipai he.
\v 34 Zisu taco, “Apaw, ngethai my lo, aa tua leimeipaw heh aa hnilynah cawtah hei,” tatah a tah. Taico raekeh sahlo taco basung phe he ka, a chaichi cawh a chaichy he.
\p 
\v 35 Zawpuipaw cawh ma lekhei a daw he ka, ming thlang he ka, uhtu sahlo tahmai tah aa hnuiso. “Cawngsaw ahringpaw cawh pachah he ka, Khazing a thingpaw, Khri a cang hmuisui caco, ato heh ama le ama cawh a pachah seh,” tatah aa tah.
\p 
\v 36 Raekeh sahlo zong taco a vong he ka, Ama cawh pasipasa he ka, misur zu a thobahlapaw khah aa hlai.
\v 37 “Juda cawngsaw aa siangpahrang na cang caco nama le nama a pachah ca,” tatah aa tah.
\p 
\v 38 A lu cung letei ca a ciapaw cawh, “MA HEH JUDA CAWNGSAW AA SIANGPAHRANG A CANG,” tah heh a cang.
\p 
\v 39 Ma letei aa pathle hrahpaw suanah a tuapaw pakhehpaw taco Ama cawh naisui hmo khei, “Khri cawh cang bei ceh maw? Nama a pachah la, kaaning zong ma pachah hrah tua!” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 40 Canghrasala, mehsua ahringpaw pakheh taco raw ka, “Khazing hmai heh ci bei ceh maw? Ama khatah a lopaw tah hreh na cangpaw heh!
\v 41 Kaaning cawh hreh tlang ka cang peh, kaa tuasanah khatah a tlahpaw kaa hmuh hi. Canghrasala ma cawngsaw heh cawh suanah zehmai tua be hi,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 42 Mataico ama taco, “Zisu, na painah raang na phah tihtah a pa thui thlang my lo,” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 43 Zisu taco ma cawngsawpaw cawh, “Biahmuisui ka ca ching, kama khatah Paradis letah atoning na ung hra a,” tatah a chai.
\s1 Zisu thihnah
\r (Mt 27:45-56; Mk 15:33-41; Jh 19:28-30)
\p 
\v 44 Ningching suimehlang hluihning hrong taitah zailang suimehlang pathung tai raang pungpaluh letah muinah a tlung,
\v 45 zecawtamaw tatah ning a khainah khah a calinah cawtah a cang. Taico, behnah ing letei pai pazypaw cawh pehning tah a hria chy.
\v 46 Zisu tah a thangpui tah, “Apaw, nama khatah ka thlawpaw ka chia,” tatah a y. Ma hraco a rei khy cangkawleh cawh a hu a ceh chung.
\p 
\v 47 Ma cawh raekeh zakheh buipaw tah a hmuh tihtah Khazing cawh reithai ka, “Ma cawngsaw heh mehding a cang hrahring thlang,” tatah a tah.
\v 48 Ma hming ungzia hnikhui rua pawtei a pahmopaw cawngsaw vytei tah ma hming khah aa hmuh tihtah ngechia tah aa cacanghnaw a cung he ka, a seihly thlu he.
\v 49 Canghrasala, Galili raang tai tei a va zuipaw canu sahlo reipai tah Ama a hnihpaw vytei taco a langpa khei a daw he ka, ma hming sahlo cawh aa cai thlang.
\s1 Zisu aa phungnah
\r (Mt 27:57-61; Mk 15:42-47; Jh 19:38-42)
\p 
\v 50 Ma leco Juda khongsil chung letah a taepaw mehchaw mehding a cangpaw Josef aa tahpaw ung ka,
\v 51 bia aa thliapaw le rai aa hrepaw cung letah a nawtlah beh. Ama cawh Judia raang, Arimathea khua taitah a vongpaw cang ka, Khazing painah raang a va tlungpaw a heh thlangpaw a cang.
\v 52 Pilat khaco va sei ka, Zisu a rawh cawh a va hae.
\v 53 Mataico a rawh cawh khraws taitah lawthlah ka, paithladih anaipaw tah pahlong ka, alung kho aa ruipaw thlai thapaw ahohmai aa phung bang lynah pawhe lekhei a isah.
\v 54 Ma cawh ningpangaw ning Sabat ning cawtah pachianah ning cang ka, Sabat ning cawh a patho daimang tei.
\p 
\v 55 Galili taitah Zisu khatei a va seipaw he canu sahlo takhei Josef cawh zui he ka, athlai le a chung letei rawh cawh zekhatamaw aa isah tahpaw khah aa hmuh.
\v 56 Mataico aaning cawh ing lang a dih he ka, a rawh cawtah ringthopaw sahlo le zihmui ringthopaw aa pachia. Canghrasala phungbia aa zuinah cawtah khei Sabat ning leco a hia he.
\c 24
\s1 Thokawnah
\r (Mt 28:1-10; Mk 16:1-8; Jh 20:1-10)
\p 
\v 1 Zaa kheh letei ning hmetaw caipaw mongdi letaco canu sahlo cawh aa pachiapaw sathy ringthopaw sahlo khah a tle he ka, thlai lang cawh aa va sei.
\v 2 Aaning sahlo taco thlai taitah alung a hneihlypaw cawh aa hmuh,
\v 3 canghrasala a chunglang a nae tih he tah Abuipaw Zisu a rawh cawh hmuh bei he.
\v 4 Ma leco lunghnahnawh tah aa ung thlang ning takhei, sungkheh teitah cawngsaw pahning, aa caise lailaw hratei a khai thai ngetei pawhe khah aa kae letah a va daw he.
\v 5 Canu sahlo cawh aa ci cawtah khei alui lang a bung he ka, canghrasala capaw pahning taco, “Zecawtamaw mehthi hrong letah mehring cawh naa hui?
\v 6 Ama cawh ma lehei ung khawh be, a thokaw thah! Galili raang letah naaning khatah a ungning tei a ca chingpaw he khah a thui thlang bei he ceh maw?
\v 7 ‘Cawngsaw Sawcapaw cawh mehsua sahlo kih letah peh a cang a, khraws letah khaipai he ka, ningthung ning letah a thokaw a,’ a tahpaw khah,” aa tah he.
\v 8 Mataico canu sahlo taco Zisu a bia khah a thui kaw he.
\p 
\v 9 Thlai lang tah a va dih kaw he ka, ma hming vytei khah a hningzuitu hluikhehpaw le ahringpaw sahlo cawh aa ching he.
\v 10 Aaning sahlo cawh Mari Makdalin, Joana, Jeims a no Mari le aaning khatei a ungpaw ahringpaw, ma kong apostol sahlo a chingpaw he khah a cang he.
\v 11 Canghrasala, aaning sahlo taco canu sahlo tei aa reipaw cawh bia tah sah be ca he ka, zing bei he.
\v 12 Ma duitei cawh Piter suipaw cawh tho ka, thlai lang khah a va sai. A bung ka, ming ka, thlai chung letei Zisu aa pahlongnahpaw paithladih cy khah a hmuh. Taico seithlah ka, hming a cangnah silang kong cawh a khuarawh a haa ngetei.
\s1 Emau khua langpui letah
\r (Mk 16:12-13)
\p 
\v 13 Ma ning lilaw leco Zisu a hningzuitu letah pahning cawh Jerusalem taitah khang sarih tluh a hlahpaw Emau khua lang cawh a sei he.
\v 14 Aaning cawh pakheh le pakheh khah a cangpaw hming vytei kong khah aa reihrui lai.
\v 15 Ma hming sahlo kong cawh reilai he katei, bia a rawh laining he takhei, Zisu cawh va chuh ka, aaning khaco a sei hrah,
\v 16 canghrasala aa bi khy nápawtah pakhang a cang he.
\p 
\v 17 Zisu taco aa hai letah, “Naa seipai tah ze bia maw na rawh lai he ceh?” tatah a tah he.
\p Aaning cawh a daw he ka, aa hme a chia thlang.
\v 18 Aa hrong letei pakhehpaw Kleopa aa tahpaw taco Zisu cawh, “Jerusalem khuapui a va tlongpaw letah nama cy heh ato cai letei hming a cangpaw sahlo heh a hnih lypaw cang ceh maw?” tatah a tah.
\p 
\v 19 Zisu taco, “Zehming maw?” tatah a hae.
\p “Nazaret Zisu kong samaw,” tatah a palei. “Ama cawh Khazing khuavang pakheh cang ka, ming hme le Khazing hme lekhei bia le tuanah letah hming tuakhynah a hnui.
\v 20 Tlangbui macang sahlo le a ma uhtu sahlo tah thaw rua pawtah nawhnuitu sahlo khatah bia pei he ka, khraws letah aa khaipai.
\v 21 Canghrasala Ama cawh Israel mingphing a tlang ruapaw he pakheh a cang, tatah kaa hnabei a suipaw khah a cang. Ma hlui co ma hratei hming a cangnah heh atoheh a ningthungnah a cang myca.
\v 22 Ma hlui co, kaa phu chung taitah canu thaikheh sahlo tah kaa ning aa ma angsah. Ato zamong mongdi khei thlai lang va sei he ka,
\v 23 canghrasala a rawh hmuh bei he. Kaaning khatah a vong he ka, Zisu cawh a hring thlang tatah a reipaw he vaiming sahlo a palypaw he khah kaa hmuh tatah aa ma ching.
\v 24 Mataico kaa vesaw thaikhehpaw tah thlai lang va sei he ka, canu sahlo tei aa reipaw hrakhei aa va hmuh, canghrasala ama cawh hmuh bei he,” aa tah.
\p 
\v 25 Zisu taco aaning cawh, “Na hruh caimang he ceh, Khazing khuavang sahlo tei aa za rei ciapaw vytei zing nápawtah naa lungthing a ku a chaw caimang!
\v 26 Khri tah ma hming sahlo heh a tai-ing ceingeipaw cang ka, taico a rungnawnah lang a naepaw cang bei maw?” a tah he.
\v 27 Aaning cawh Moses le Khazing khuavang sahlo vytei tei Ama a kong Capathai letei aa reipaw naning tei hrakhei a chingpase he.
\p 
\v 28 Aa va sei nápaw khua khah aa va phah daimang tihtah Zisu cawh langhlaw vy lang a sei ruapaw hrakhei a tua.
\v 29 Canghrasala aaning taco, “Kaaning kha a reh thlang. Zailang cang ca ka, ning a tlah daimang myca hi!” tatah hmuisui teitah aa thly. Macawtaco aaning khaco ria rua pawtah a sei.
\p 
\v 30 Aaning sahlo kha cabuai letah a ty thlangning tah very cawh law ka, alawngnah bia a hlai khy taitah kychy ka, aaning cawh a peh he.
\v 31 Taico Zisu hni khynah cawh peh cang he ka, ama cawh aa bi. Taico, ama cawh aa mehmuhnah taitah a ly thah.
\v 32 Pakheh le pakheh cawh, “Langpui letei kaaning kha bia reilai katei, Capathai a ma ching pase laining takhei kaa chung letah kaa lungthing khah me kangpaw hratah cang bei maw kha?” a tah he.
\p 
\v 33 Sungkheh tah tho he ka, Jerusalem lang cawh aa kawkaw. Ma leco a hningzuitu hluikheh le aaning khatah a ungpaw sahlo he a za pahmo thlang he katei,
\v 34 “Ma heh ahmangpaw a cang! Abuipaw cawh thokaw ka, Simon khatah a paly,” tatah a za rei leimeipaw he khah aa hmuh he.
\v 35 Mataico, ma tlaw pahning taco langpui letei hming a cangpaw le very a kychy ning tei Zisu aa binah kong khah aa ching he.
\s1 A hningzuitu sahlo khatah Zisu a paly
\r (Mt 28:16-20; Mk 16:14-18; Jh 20:19-23; Apos 1:6-8)
\p 
\v 36 Ma bia aa rei chung vytei cawh Zisu cawh aa hrong letah a daw thlang ka, aaning sahlo cawh, “Naaning khatah thlawlungnah ung ky seh,” a tah he.
\p 
\v 37 Aaning sahlo cawh a pahly he ka, aa ci ngetei. Athlaw kaa hmuh tatah aa rawh.
\v 38 Zisu tah aaning sahlo cawh, “Zecawtamaw naa lung reithui ka, lung langlo tah naa ung?
\v 39 Ka kih le ka phe heh mingtua hmai o, kama pui ka cang caw! Pa tong la, naa hni thlang a. Athlaw taco ka hnuipaw, naa hmuhpaw hapaw ru le ngaisaw cawh a hnui tlung be!” tatah a tah he.
\p 
\v 40 Ma bia a rei khy taikhei a kih le a phe cawh a hmuhsah he.
\v 41 Aa khuarawh a haa tu cawtah le aa lung a lawng tu cawtah khei zing khy thly be ca he ka, “Ma lehei epaw naa hnuipaw a ung maw?” tatah a hae he.
\v 42 Aaning taco ama cawh aa pakang ciapaw ngawsaw vy kheh khah pei he ka,
\v 43 ma ngaw cawh law ka, aa hmekaw leco a e.
\p 
\v 44 Aa hai leco, “Naaning khatah ka ung ning takhei ma heh ka ca chingpaw he khah a cang. Moses phungbia cabu le Khazing khuavang sahlo aa cabu le Reithainah Hlaw cabu chung letei Kama ka kong ciapaw vytei cawh patling a cang tae he a,” tatah a tah he.
\p 
\v 45 Mataico Khazing Capathai sahlo aa thui khy nápawtah aa thinglung ning a pavang he.
\v 46 Aa hai leco, “Ma heh Capathai letah ciapaw cawh a cang. Khri cawh reithui sisaw ing ka, ningthung ning tah thihnah taitah a tho kaw a,
\v 47 taico, Ama a ming tah angepachihnah le sua ngethainah kong cawh Jerusalem taitah patho he ka, mingphing vytei khatah rei a cang tae a.
\v 48 Naaning sahlo cawh ma hming sahlo heh a hnikhuitu na cang he ceh.
\v 49 Ka paw tei bia a kang ciapaw khah naaning khatah ka za taw a, canghrasala hmingtuakhynah vaicung taitah naa hmuh hlai vytei cawh Jerusalem khuapui chung lekhei ung thlang my lo,” a tah he.
\s1 Vaicung lang a kenah
\r (Mk 16:19-20; Apos 1:9-11)
\p 
\v 50 Aaning sahlo cawh Zisu tah piathlah khui he ka, Bethani khua kae aa phah tihtah a kih pazy ka, bonghnang a song he.
\v 51 Bonghnang a song leimei ning he taco, aaning sahlo cawh seisai he ka, vaicung lang lah chy tah a cang.
\v 52 Mataico aaning sahlo taco Ama cawh beh he ka, a lawng ngetei tah Jerusalem lang cawh aa kawkaw.
\v 53 Taico, Khazing reithai hmo khei behnah ing leco aa ung thlang tei.
